<doc id='voa_5284847' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/coronavirus-yahawe-irindi-zina--covid-19/5284847.html' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus Yahawe Irindi Zina- COVID 19
Umubare w’abantu bamaze kwicwa na virusi ya Corona mu gihugu cy’Ubushinwa umaze kugera ku 1,110.
Komisiyo ishinzwe iby’ubuzima mu ntara ya Hubei yatangaje ko yamenye ko abandi bantu 94 bishwe n’icyo cyorezo.
96 ku ijana ry’abamaze guhitanwa niyo ndwara ni abo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, umurwa mukuru w’intara ya Hubei, iyi virus yavukiye, nk’uko umuryango witwa American Medical Association (AMA) wabitangaje.
Abanduye virus ya Corona bararenga 43,000. Muri bo 30 ku ijana ni abaganga n’abaforomo. AMA isanga ibi biteye impungenge z’uko inzego z’ubuvuzi zose zishobora gusenyuka mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, ibitangazamakuru bya leta y’Ubushinwa bivuga ko abayobozi bakuru babili b’inzego z’ubuvuzi mu ntara ya Hubei birukanwe ku milimo yabo.
Kuri ubu, iyo virus yamaze guhabwa irindi zina n’ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima. Ubu yitwa COVID-19.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5291235' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5291235.html' term='COVID'>
Corona/COVID-19 Umaze Kwica Abashika 1800 mu Bushinwa
Ibitigiri vy’abanduye umugera wa Corona/COVID19 mu Bushinwa gushika kuri uyu wa mbere vyarenze 70000 mu gihe indege zibiri zuzuye abanyamerika bari bugaraniwe mu bwato mu Buyapani batahukanwa muri Amerika.
Mu ntara ya Hubei, aho uwo mugera watanguriye, abandi bantu 100 bavuzwe ko bapfuye, bica bishikana ku gitigiri c’abamaze gupfa cababa 1800 mu Bushinwa. Ariko ibi bitigiri bishobora kwiyongera umwanya n’umwanya.
Umuyobozi w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yashikirije ko bigoye kumenya inzira ico kiza kizofata.
OMS yashikirije kuri uyu w’Imana ko yahamagariye amareta kuza arashikiriza abanyagihugu babo ububi bw’uwo mugera ariko batabateye ubwoba.
Mu gihe Ubushinwa bwaheruka gushemagizwa ku kuntu buvyitwaramwo hamwe n’utwigoro two guhagarika ikwiragira ry’uwo mugera, OMS iracasaba amakuru y’ukuntu ico gihugu gisuzuma no kumenya abanduye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5327231' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5327231.html' term='COVID'>
Inama yAbakuru ba EAC Yasibijwe Kubera Ikiza ca COVID-19
U Rwanda rwatangaje kuri uyu wa kane ko inama y’abakuru b’ibihugu vy’akarere ka Afrika y’ubuseruko, EAC, yobaye mu mpera z’uku kwezi kwa 3 yasibijwe kubera ikiza c’umugera wa Corona (COVID-19) gihangayikishije isi yose.
U Rwanda ni rwo rurongoye inama y’abakuru b’ivyo bihugu muri iki kiringo. Umushikiranganji w’u Rwanda w’imigenderanire n’amakungu yandikiye ikete umunyamabanga mukuru wa EAC ko n’izindi nama zihuza abantu benshi zohagarikwa mu ntumbero yo kwirinda ico kiza.
Inkuru iramvuye twayiteguriwe n’umumenyeshamakuru w’Ijwi ry’Amerika i Kigali mu Rwanda Pierre Claver Niyonkuru.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5338076' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ibihano-ku-bigo-24-byazamuye-ibiciro-kubera-covid-19-mu-rwanda-/5338076.html' term='COVID'>
Ibihano ku Bigo 24 Byazamuye Ibiciro Kubera COVID-19 mu Rwanda
Ministeri y’ubucuruzi mu Rwanda yatangiye gufatira ibihano abacuruzi bitwikiliye icyorezo cya Virus ya Corona, bagatangira kuzamura ibiciro ku masoko.
Kuva iyi Ministeri yatangira ubugenzuzi, ibigo by’ubucuruzi 24 bimaze gufatirwa ibihano.
Inkuru yateguwe n'umumenyeshamakuru w'Ijwi ry'Amerika Assumpta Kaboyi
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5322978' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/vatikani-yafunze-urubuga-rwa-mutagatifu-petero-kubera-covid-19/5322978.html' term='COVID'>
Vatikani Yafunze Urubuga rwa Mutagatifu Petero Kubera COVID-19
Virusi ya Corona, COVID-19 imaze kugera mu bihugu 105. Abayanduye bose barenga ibihumbi 115. Naho abo imaze guhitana kugeza ubu ku isi bararenga ibihumbi bine.
Intara y’Ubushinwa ya Hubei, aho COVID-19 yabanje, yadohoye gato ibyo gukumira urujya n’uruza rw’abantu. Perezida Xi Jinping w’Ubushinwa uyu munsi yagiye gusura umujyi wa Wuhan, umurwa mukuru wa Hubei. Yavuze ko bamaze gutera intambwe ikomeye mu rwego rwo guhashya COVID-19.
Mu Butaliyani, guverinoma yategetse, ku buryo butarabaho ku isi, ko abaturage bose uko ari miliyoni 60 baguma mu ngo zabo guhera kuri uyu wa kabili. Ubutaliyani ni cyo gihugu cya kabiri cyashegeshwe ku isi nyuma y’Ubushinwa.
Vatikani yafunze urubuga rwitiriwe Mutagatifu Petero kugera ku itariki ya 3 y’ukwa kane. Imbaga y’abantu bahateranira buri wa gatatu kugirango babonane n’umushumba wa kiriziya gaturika, Papa Fransisko, ntibazongera kuhajya igihe cyose ruzaba rufunze. Vatikani kandi yafashe icyemezo ko nta mukerarugendo izakira kugera ku itariki ya 3 y’ukwa kane.
Muri Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika, abadepite bane n’umusenateri umwe bafashe icyemezo cyo kwiha akato ubwabo kubera impungenge ko bashobora kuba barahuye n’abanduye COVID-19. Mu Bufaransa, mu bayanduye harimo abadepite batanu na minisitiri w’umuco.
Ku mugabane w’Afrika, kugeza ubu abantu bagera kuri 40 ni bo bamaze kwandura virusi ya Corona.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5326263' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5326263.html' term='COVID'>
Inteko y'Umutekano ya ONU Yasubitse Urugendo rwo muri Afurika
Icyorezo COVID-19 cyatumye Inteko y’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ishinzwe umutekano ku isi isubika mu gihe kitagenwe urugendo yateganyaga kujyamo yose uko yakabaye mu kwezi kwa kane mu bihugu bya Mali na Nijeri muri Afurika y’uburengerazuba.
Mali na Nijeri ntibiravuga niba COVID-19 yarabigezemo. Ariko abadipolomate b’ibihugu 15 bigize Inteko y’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ishinzwe umutekano ku isi bagombaga kugerayo banyuze mu Bufaransa, nk’uko ikigo ntaramakuru AFP cyo mu Bufaransa cyabitangaje.
COVID-19 imaze kwica abantu barenga 33 mu Bufaransa. Ariko urugendo rwasubitswe mbere y’icyemezo Perezida Trump yafashe ejo nimugoroba cyo gukumira Abanyabulayi: ntibemerewe kwinjira muri Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika mu gihe cy’ukwezi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5292683' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5292683.html' term='COVID'>
Ubushinwa Bwemeza ko 11000 Bamaze Gukira Umugera wa Corona
Abategetsi b’Ubushinwa batangaje kuri uyu wa kabiri ibitigiri bemeza vy’abantu bamaze kwandura umugera wa Corona-Covid-19, birenga 71000, abamaze gupfa nabo barenga 1800.
Abashika 11000 nabo baramaze gukira. Ariko ibi bitigiri birashobora guhinduka umwanya n’umwanya.
Umuyobozi wa OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus avuga ko ivyo bitigiri vy’Ubushinwa vyerekana ko umurindi w’abandura ugabanuka ariko ko ibi bikwiye gufatwa mu bwitonzi ko bishobora guhinduka bivanye na bashasha bokwandura.
OMS ishikiriza ko umugwi w’abahinga mvamakungu 12 baza bari mu Bushinwa kandi bariko barakorana na bagenzi babo b’Ubushinwa mu guhangana n’uwo mugera.
Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika yashikirije kuri uyu wa mbere ko yatahukanye abanyagihugu bayo barenga 300 n’imiryango yabo ya hafi bari baragumijwe mu bwato bwitwa Diamond Princess mu Buyapani kuko bakekwa kuba baranduye.
14 muri bo berekanye ibimenyetso ko banduye kandi abo bose bakazomara iyindi misi 14 ahabonyene aho bashikijwe muri Amerika.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5288744' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/afurika-yoba-yiteguriye-guhangana-na-corona-/5288744.html' term='COVID'>
Afurika Yoba Yiteguriye Guhangana na Corona?
Ibihugu by’Afurika bikomeje gufata ingamba zikaze zijyanye no kwitegura guhangana na virusi ya Corona ubu izwi COVID-19, igihe yaba igeze kuri uwo mugabane.
Ikigo nyafurika gishizwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara Africa CDC kivuga ko iyo virusi niramuka igeze muri Afurika ishobora kuzahitana abantu benshi.
Mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru I Addis Ababa muri Etiyopiya, umuyobozi w’icyo kigo John Nkengasong yavuze ko ibihugu bitandukanye byafashe ingamba zirimo gupima abantu ku bibuga by’indege, kubaka za labaratoire zifite ubushobozi bwo gupima iyo ndwara no guhugura abakozi b’ubuzima.
Yavuze ko ibihugu 16 by’Afurika ubu bifite ubushobozi bwo gupima iyo ndwara. Yagaragaje ko bifuza ko mbere yuko uku kwezi kurangira, ibindi bihugu 20 bizaba bifite ubwo bushobozi.
Nubwo nta makuru afatika arabyemeza, bwana Nkengasong yavuze ko bishoboka ko iyo ndwara ishobora kuba yarageze ku mugabane w’Afurika.
Hari ibihugu bimaze gutangaza ko hari abantu bikeka ko banduye iyo ndwara ariko nyuma ibizami bikaragaza ko atari byo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5296208' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5296208.html' term='COVID'>
Babiri Bishwe n'umugera Corona muri Irani
Itororokanirizo ry’amakuru rya reta ya Irani ryashikirije ko abantu babiri bapfuye inyuma y’aho basuzumiwe bagasanga baranduye umugera wa Corona/Covid-19. Babaye aba mbere bishwe n’uwo mugera mur’ico gihugu.
Ico kinyamakuru cashikirije ko umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu yavuze ko abo bantu bapfuye bari abo mu gisagara ceranda ca Qom, mu bumanuko bw’umurwa mukuru Teherani.
Gushika ubu, abashika 75000 baramaze kwandura uwo mugera kw’isi hose, mu gihe abarenga 2000 bavugwa ko bamaze gupfa, benshi mu Bushinwa. Ariko ibi bitigiri bishobora guhinduka umwanya n’umwanya.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5311159' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5311159.html' term='COVID'>
Uwugira Kabiri Yahitanwe n'Umugera wa Corona muri Amerika
Abategetsi mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu muri reta ya Washington, Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika bashikirije ejo ku musi w’Imana ko umuntu agira kabiri yahitanwe n’umugera wa Corona/COVID 19. Abashakashatsi bavuze ko uwo mugera wari umaze indwi zitari nke ugendagenda mu micungararo y’igisagara ca Seattle.
Aya makuru yiyongereye ku bandi bakozi babiri mu vy’amagara y’abantu mu karere ka San Francisco muri Californiya basuzumwe ko banduye ejo kuw’Imana. Naho mu gisagara ca New York umugore w’imyaka iharurwa muri 30 yasuzumwe ko yanduye mu gihe yariko aja muri Irani. Reta ya Washington imaze kuronka abantu 12 banduye.
Inyuma y’aho Abategetsi mu mareta hamwe n’ibisagara vy'Amerika bafatiye ingingo yo gusuzuma iyo ngwara, ibiharuro vy’abanduye vyiyongereye mu gihugu. Hagaragaye bashasha banduye muri reta za California, Illinois, Rhode Island, New York na reta ya Washington.
Icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu, Mike Pence, yashikirije ejo kuw’Imana ko hazokorwa ibishoboka vyose kugira umugera wa Corona ntiwamamare hose mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5338480' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/uwa-kabiri-yahitanywe-na-covid-19-muri-afurika-yo-munsi-y-ubutayu-/5338480.html' term='COVID'>
Uwa Kabiri Yahitanywe na COVID-19 muri Afurika yo Munsi y’Ubutayu
Umurwayi wa mbere yahitanywe na virusi ya corona muri Gabon. Ni uwa kabiri iyitanye muri Afurika yo munsi y’Ubutayu bwa Sahara, nyuma ya Burukina Faso. Muri Gabon kugeza kuri uyu wa gatanu habarwaga abarwayi batatu gusa.
Yari afite imyaka 50 y’amavuko. Yitabye Imana saa mbiri n’iminota itanu azize inkurikizi za diabete, amaze no kugira ibibazo byo guhumeka. Uwo mugabo, ubwenegihugu bwe butatangajwe, yaherukaga mu Bufaransa aho yari yagiye kwisuzumisha.
Uretse uwo witabye Imana na batatu barwaye, nta wundi wari wagaragaraho virusi ya Corona muri Gabon.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5326254' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5326254.html' term='COVID'>
Minisitiri w'Intebe wa Canada Yishyize mu Kato Kubera Corona
Muri Canada, ikinyamakuru “The Canadian Press” cyatangaje ko minisitiri w’intebe, Justin Trudeau, n’umugore we bishyize mu kato ku bushake bwabo.
Nk’uko ibiro by’umukuru wa guverinoma byabisobanuye, babitewe n’uko madame Sophie Trudeau yari avuye mu rugendo mu Bwongereza afite ibimenyetso bijya gusa n’ibya COVID-19, birimo kugira umuriro. Yatanze ibizame mu baganga. Ategereje ibisubizo.
Nta bimenyetso bisa n’ibya COVID-19 bigaragara kuri minisitiri w’intebe Trudeau ku giti cye. Ariko, ati: “Ntawamenya. Ibyiza ni ugukorera imuhira kugera igihe ibizame bya madame we bizabonekera.”
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5330608' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/covid-19-imaze-guhomvya-u-rwanda-miliyoni-eshanu-z-amadorali/5330608.html' term='COVID'>
COVID 19 Imaze Guhomvya u Rwanda Miliyoni Eshanu z’Amadorali
Leta y’u Rwanda iravuga ko imaze guhomba miliyoni eshanu z’amadorali, ni kuvuga agera kuri miliyari 5 mu mafaranga y’u Rwanda, kubera inama nyinshi zagombaga kubera mu Rwanda zahagaritswe bitewe na virusi ya Corona.
Ministeri y’ubucuruzi isobanura ko ico cyorezo kimaze kuyogoza isi cyateye ihungabana mu bukungu bw'u Rwanda. Minisitiri Hakuziyaremye Soraya ushinzwe ubwo bushikiranganji asobanura ko Leta imaze guhagarika inama zigera kuri 6 zagombaga kubera mu gihugu zikaba zarakuruye igihombo.
Iki gihombo Leta ivuga ko yagize, ni nacyo kivugwa ku bacuruzi bajyaga barangurira ibicuruzwa byabo hanze y’u Rwanda. Abo bacuruzi bagiye kumara amezi asaga 3 batarangura cyane cyane abaranguriraga mu Bushinwa.
Leta ivuga ko kubera igihombo gikomeje kugaragara haba ku bacuruzi ndetse no ku gihugu muri rusange, igiye gukorera ubuvugizi abacuruzi bafite imyenda ya banki n’abishyura imisoro bashobora guhomba kubera Coronavirus.
Minisiteri w’Ubucuruzi n’inganda ashimangira ko Ministeri ayobora igiye gukorana n’inzego zirebwa n’iki kibazo, hakigwa uburyo abantu bishyura imisoro kimwe n’abafite imyenda muri banki bafashwa kuko bashobora kubura ubwishyu kubera ibura ry’abakiliya riturutse ku ifungwa ry’ibikorwa mu gukumira Coronavirus.
U Rwanda rwakajije ingamba mu gukumira ko virusi ya Corona imaze kuyogoza isi ndetse kikaba cyarageze no mu gihugu imbere, aho Ministeri y’ubuzima, imaze gutangaza abantu bagera kuri 5 bamaze kwandura iyo Virusi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5287163' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5287163.html' term='COVID'>
Virusi ya Corona/COVID 19 Imaze Guhitana Abarenga 1350 kw'Isi
Mu Bushinwa, leta yatangaje kuwa Kane ko abandi bantu 254 bahitanywe na virusi ya Corona. Abo imaze kwica bose hamwe bararenga 1350.
Leta yasobanuye ko yashyize uburyo bushyashya bwo gukora aya mabarura bwerekana ko ubwo yakoreshaga mbere buterekana neza uko ikibazo kiremereye cyane.
Leta y’Ubushinwa kandi yatangaje ko abantu 451,462 bafite aho bahuriye ha hafi cyane n’abantu banduye virusi ya Corona. Muri bo 185,037 barakurikiranirwa hafi n’inzego z’ubuvuzi. Byumvikana kandi ko imibare y'abapfuye, n'iy'abanduye ikomeza kugenda ihinduka bitewe n'uko imenyekanye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5264752' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5264752.html' term='SARS'>
Umugera Corona Umaze Kwica 132 mu Bushinwa
Igitigiri c’abamaze kwandura umugera Corona mu Bushinwa cashitse ku 5974 kuri uyu wa gatatu, barenze abafashwe n’umugera nk’uwo wiswe SARS wateye ico gihugu nyene mu myaka y’2002 n’2003.
Komisiyo y’igihugu y’amagara y’abantu mu Bushinwa yashikirije ko abashika 1400 bashasha babonetse kuri uyu wa gatatu, mu gihe abamaze gupfa bageze ku 132.
Ubuyapani na Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika kuri uyu wa kabiri bakuye abanyagihugu babo mu gisagara ca Wuhan, ahatanguriye uwo mugera.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5273328' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/chine-imyiyerekano-isaba-iyugarwa-ry-imipaka-ija-ahatanguiye-corona-/5273328.html' term='SARS'>
Chine: Imyiyerekano Isaba Iyugarwa ry'Imipaka Ija Ahatanguriye Corona
Abakozi bagera 2,000 bo mu bitaro bya Hong Kong bari mu myigarambyo yatangiye ku wa mbere basaba ko imipaka yose ijya mu mujyi wa Wuhan wo mu Bushinwa wabaye indiri ya Virus ya Corona ifungwa.
Kugeza ubu iyo virusi imaze guhitana abantu 425.
Twibutse ko Hong Kong yigeze kwibasirwa n’icyorezo gifata imyanya y’ubuhumekero cya SARS mu myaka ya za 2002-2003.
Abayobozi mu nzego z’ubuzima muri Hong Kong bavuze ko bamaze kubona umuntu umwe ushobora kuba yaranduye virus ya Corona nyuma y’uko asuye umujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho ubuyobozi bw’umujyi wa Macau nawo wo mu Bushinwa bwatangaje ko bugiye gufunga ahantu hose hakinirwa urusimbi izwi nka kasino mu gihe cy’iby’umweru bibiri mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwizwa rwa virus ya Corona.
Ubu umubare w'abamaze kwemezwa ko banduye iyi virusi mu Bushinwa urarenga 20000, mu gihe abagera ku 150 aribo bamaze kwandura mu bihugu 23.
Ubushakashatsi bumaze gukorwa n’abahanga bo muri Wuhan Institute Virology, bafite ubunararibonye mu ndwara za virusi bemeza ko iyi virusi ya Corana imeze nk'iyabonetse mu tunyoni twitwa uducurama mu ntara ya Yunnan ku kigero cya 96 ku ijana.
Ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS riravuga ko imibare y'abandura iyi virusi ikomeza kuzamuka ishingiye ku bisubizo by’ibizami bikorerwa abakekwaho kuyandura.
Umuvugizi wa guverinema mu Bushinwa Hua Chunying anenga Leta zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika ko ikwirakwiza ubwoba mu bantu aho kubafasha guhangana n’icyo cyorezo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5253740' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5253740.html' term='SARS'>
OMS: Umugera SARS Umaze Guhitana Batatu mu Bushinwa
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS, ryatangaje ko rigiye gutumako inama yihuta muri iyi ndwi yo kurabira hamwe umugera mushasha wadutse mu Bushinwa, inyuma yaho ushikiye mu bindi bihugu bitatu vyo muri Aziya.
Umugwi w’abahinga ba OMS uzohurira i Geneve mu Buswise kuri uyu wa gatatu kugira wemeze nimba uwo mugera ufatira mu bihimba vyo guhema wiswe Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome canke SARS mu mpfunyapfunyo y’icongereza wotangazwa ko ari ikiza ku magara y’abantu kw’isi.
Iyi ngingo ifashwe inyuma yaho umuhinga wa reta y’Ubushinwa ashikirije kuri uyu wa mbere ko uwo mugera wamuka ku bikoko kandi umaze guhitana ubuzima bw’abantu batatu, wandukirana hagati y’abantu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1263957' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/a-18-a-2003-05-06-3-1-93012539/1263957.html' term='SARS'>
Indwara ya SARS ngo Ishobora Gukumirwa - 2003-05-06
Agakoko gatera indwara ya SARS - Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome - ngo karacyakwirakwira vuba n’ubwo isi yose yagahagurukiye.  Ibyo byaraye bitangajwe n’umuyobozi w’ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Madamu Gro Harlem Brundtland. Yari mu nama i Buruseli n’abaminisitiri bashinzwe ubuzima mu bihugu bigize umuryango w’ubumwe bw’i Burayi.  Madamu Brundtland asanga agakoko ka SARS gashobora gukumirwa no kurandurwa burundu. Gusa ngo haracyari kare kugira ngo bamenye aho iyo ndwara izahagararira.  Brundtland avuga ko iyo ndwara imaze gucika muri Vietnam, ikaba iri no kugabanuka cyane muri Canada. Mu Bushinwa ho icyakora ngo ntiracogora.  Hagati aho, umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishyaka riri k’ubutegetsi muri Mozambique, Armando Guebuza, yashyizwe ukwa wenyine mu gihe cy’iminsi 10 kubera gutinya ko yaba abungukanye indwara ya SARS.  Armando Guebuza, hamwe na bagenzi be 5 bari kumwe, bakubutse m’urugendo mu Bushinwa. Abategetsi bo muri Mozambique basobanura ko kubashyira ukwabo bigamije gusa kubuza iyo ndwara kwinjira mu gihugu cyabo.  Umwe mu bandi bategetsi b’ishyaka FRELIMO Armando Guebuza ayobora avuga ko uwo Guebuza na bagenzi be nta gakoko ka SARS kabagaragayemo ubwo bavaga mu Bushinwa.  Ubu hirya no hino ku isi abantu bagera kuri 6500 bamaze kwandura indwara ya SARS. Hafi maganane na 80 imaze kubahitana. Abaheruka bavugwa mu Bushinwa, Hong Kong, Taiwan, na Singapore.    Shakira izindi nkuru z'Afurika hano. Saba amakuru muri email yawe  hano.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1263835' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/a-18-a-2003-06-20-2-1-93011314/1263835.html' term='SARS'>
OMS ngo Urukingo rwa SARS  Ruracyari Kure - 2003-06-20
.  Abashakashatsi bo muri Afurika y’Epfo bavuga ko bitegura kugerageza bwa mbere urukingo rw’ubwoko bwa SIDA bwibasira amajyepfo y’Afurika by’umwihariko.  Umuyobozi w’abo bashakashatsi, Glenda Gray, yaraye atangaje ko urwo rukingo ruzageragerezwa bwa mbere ku bantu 96 badafite agakoko ka SIDA bakomoka muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika no muri Afurika y’Epfo. Abo bantu ngo ni bo bemeye ku bwende bwabo kugeragerezwaho urwo rukingo.  Mu byumweru bikeya ngo ni bwo urwo rukingo ruzageragerezwa bwa mbere ku bari muri Amerika.  Igeragezwa ry’urwo rukingo nirigenda neza mu kiciro cya mbere, ngo hazabaho n’ibindi byiciro 2 byo kurugerageza.  Ibyo ayo magerageza azageraho ngo bitegerejwe mu gihe cy’imyaka 2. Bigenze neza kandi urukingo rwatangira gukoreshwa ku bantu benshi ngo rwazaba rubonetse mu gihe cy’imyaka 10.  Saba amakuru muri email yawe  hano.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5044821' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5044821.html' term='ebola'>
Indwara ya Ebola Yageze mu Ntara ya Kivu y'Epfo
Abategetsi muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo bemeje ko abantu babiri banduye indwara ya Ebola, umwe muri bo akaba yamaze kwicwa niyo ndwara mu ntara ya Kivu y’epfo. Ni ku nshuro ya mbere hagaragaye abantu banduye iyo ndwara muri iyo ntara.
Amakuru dukesha ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS avuga ko umugore w’imyaka 26 yapfuye azize Ebola mu gihe umwana we muto akomeje gukurikiranwa n’abaganga mu bitaro bya Mwenga mu burasirazuba bwa Kongo.
Ubuyobozi bw’intara ya Kivu y’epfo buvuga ko uko ari babiri baje muri iyo ntara bavuye mu ntara ya Ituri imaze iminsi ivugwamo iyo ndwara.
Kuva iyo ndwara yongeye kwigaragaza muri Kongo, imaze guhitana abantu barenga 1800. Ni ku nshuro ya 10 Ebola igaragara muri Kongo mu myaka 40 ishize. Cyokora kuri iyi nshuro nibwo ihitanye umubare munini w’abantu.
Mu mwaka wa 2014, iyo ndwara yahitanye abantu 11000 mu bihugu byo mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika. OMS ivuga ko abantu 175000 bamaze gukingirwa indwara ya Ebola nka kimwe mu buryo bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ryayo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4718786' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4718786.html' term='ebola'>
Dr Denis Mukwege Yatahutse muri RDC
Kuri uyu wa kane nibwo Dr. Denis Mukwege yagarutse mu gihugu, ni nyuma yo gushyikirizwa igihembo cyitiriwe Nobel cy’uwaharaniye amahoro; i Bukavu aho asanzwe akorera ibikorwa by’ubuvuzi yakiriwe n’imbaga y’abaturage babarirwa mu bihumbi ndetse n’abakuriye imiryango ya Sosiyete Sivili ikorera muri Kivu y’Amajyepfo.
Mu ijambo rye, Dr Mukwege yongeye gusaba ko abagore bafashwe ku ngufu n’imiryango yabo bahabwa indishyi kandi hagashyirwaho urukiko mpuzamahanga rwihariye ruburanisha abagize uruhare mu ntambara imaze imyaka irenga 20 iyogoza igihugu cye.
Dr. Mukwege yashyikijwe iki gihembo i Oslo muri Norvege mu ntangiriro z’uku kwezi. Ni igihembo yahawe kubw’uruhare rwe mu kurwanya ko ihohoterwa n’isambaywa ku gahato ry’abagore byakoreshwa nk’intwaro y’intambara, agihanwa n’umunyairakekazi Nadia Murad.
Agarutse mu gihugu mu gihe hari umwuka utari mwiza uturuka ku isubikwa ry’amatora ry’igihe kirekire muri bimwe mu bice by’intara ya Kivu y’amajyaruguru birimo na Teritwari ya Beni, aho abatora barenga miliyoni n’igice batazagira uruhare muri aya matora ateganijwe kuri iki cyumweru kije bakazategereza ukwezi kwa 3 k’umwaka utaha; ni ku mpamvu akanama gashinzwe amatora CENI kavuze ko zatewe n’icyorezo cya Ebola ndetse n’umutekano utifashe neza;
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2422937' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2422937.html' term='ebola'>
1350: Igitigiri c'Abantu bamaze Guhitanwa na Ebola
Ikiza ca Ebola, kigeramiye akarere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, cahitanye ubundi buzima bw’abantu ijana na batandatu, mu vyongereje igitigiri c’abamaze guhitanwa n’ico kiza, muri rusangi bagera ku bantu igihumbi n’amajana atatu na mirongo itanu.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, ryatangaje ivyo bihahuro bishasha, ku musi wa gatatu, mu gihe abategetsi mu gihugu ca Liberia, bategetse ikumirwa ry’abantu baba mu bice bibiri, biri ku nkengera z’umurwa mukuru, mu mwizero w’ukugabanya ikwiragira ry’ikiza ca Ebola.
Igipolisi cararashe insoro n’imyuka ibabaza mu maso, mu gice ca West Point, kugira gishwiragize abari mu myiyerekano, bariko batera amabuye, bari bashavujwe n’izibirwa ry’amabarabara yinjira, canke asohoka, mu bice babamwo.
Ivyabona bavuga kw'abantu bane, canke barenga, bakomeretse.
Mu gihugu ca Liberia, niho ibice mirongo icenda kw’ijana vy’abantu bashasha bahitanywe na Ebola, batangajwe n’ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S, ryatangaje kandi, abandi bantu bashasha amajana abiri na mirongo ibiri n’umwe bafise Ebola, mu vyatumye igitigiri c’abamaze kwandura Ebola, muri Liberia, Guinee, Nigeria, na Sierra Leone, baba gatoyi musi y’ibihumbi bibiri n’amajana atanu.
Mw’ijambo yashikirije abanyagihugu, mw’ijoro ryo ku musi wa kabiri, prezida wa Liberia, Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yavuzeko kwihoza impanuro, n’igabishwa bitangwa na Reta, biriko bituba ikiza ca Ebola ciyongera.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1532906' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/1532906.html' term='ebola'>
Uganda ihanganye na Virusi ya Marburg
Uganda ihagurukiye guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi ya Marburg nyuma y’icyumweru kimwe gusa icyorezo cya Ebola gihitanye abantu byibura 16.
Mu cyumweru gishize abategetsi bashinzwe ibyerekeye ubuzima muri Uganda batangaje icyorezo cya virusi ya Marburg itera kuvilirana nka Ebola. Kugeza ubu abantu batanu bamaze gupfa batandatu bashyizwe mu kato abandi barenga 150 barimo gucungirwa hafi kubera ibimenyetso bagaragaje. Umwe muribo arimo kuvulirwa mu murwa mukuru Kampala. Abantu babonetseho virusi ya Marburg bose baturutse mu ntara y’amajyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba ya Kabale yegereye u Rwanda.
Twifuje kumenya iby’iyi vurusi ku bireba u Rwanda igihugu gituranye na Uganda tubatumilira umuyobozi ushinzwe kurwanya indwara z’ibyorezo Docteur Thierry Nyatanyi.
Yatubwiye ko virusi ya Marburg ntayiraboneka mu Rwanda ariko ko hari ingamba zafashwe ku birebana n’iyi vurusi. Ibindi bisobanuro murabyumva muri iki kiganiro.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2538210' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2538210.html' term='ebola'>
Ibisubizo bya Ebola Bishobora Kujya Biboneka mu Minota 15
Prezida w’Ubufaransa Francois Hollande, ari mu ruzinduko mu gihugu cya Gineya cyibasiwe n’indwara ya Ebola. Abaye umuyobozi wa mbere wo mu burengerazuba bw’isi, usuye ibihugu byogogojwe n’icyorezo cya Ebola.
Perezida w’Ubufaransa arabonana n’abayobozi ba Gineya, agasura ibigo by’ubuvuzi no kuzavugana n’abakorana n’abarwayi ba Ebola.
Ubufaransa bwarahiriye kuzatanga miliyoni 125 z’amadolari, yo gukoresha mu bikorwa byo kurwanya Ebola bwibanda kuri Gineya, igihugu bwigeze gukoroniza.
Kuri uyu wa gatanu kandi umuryango ufasha mu byerekeye ubuzima mu rwego mpuzamahanga, The Wellcome Trust, wavuze ko uteganya kugerageza uburyo bushya bwo gusuzuma indwara ya Ebola muri Gineya. Iki gipimo gishobora kuba cyagaragaje igisubizo mu minota 15. Ubu buryo bwaba bwihuse ho incuro esheshatu zose, ugereranije n’uburyo bwo gupima Ebola bugeragezwa ubu.
Ubwo buryo bushya buramutse bukoze neza, bwafasha impuguke mu by’ubuvuzi kumenya umuntu urwaye Ebola hakiri kare. Bwatuma abarwayi batangira kuvurwa mbere kurusha uko byari byifashe. Impuguke zivuga ko, kuvurwa kare bigira uruhare runini mu gutuma umuntu akira indwara ya Ebola.
Gineya yapfushije abantu 1,200 bazize Ebola. Icyorezo cya Ebola, cyatwaye ubuzima bw’abantu 5,700 mu 16,000 banduye iyo ndwara. Abenshi ni abo muri Gineya, Liberiya na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4518306' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4518306.html' term='ebola'>
Abasirikare ba ADF Bagirizwa Kwica Abashika 14 muri Beni
Abagabo cumi hamwe n’abagore bane baranyurujwe n’abakekwa kuba abarwanyi b’Abaganda bahurikiye mu muhari ADF. Batowe ibiziga mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, nkuko amakuru ava mu gisirikare yabivuze ku musi wa gatatu.
Ivyo biziga vyatowe i Beni mu ntara ya Kivu y’uburaruko, ihana urubibe n’ibihugu vya Uganda n’u Rwanda, ahavugwa ikiza ca Ebola muri iki gihe.
Umuhari w’abarwanyi ADF washinzwe n’abarwanyi b’Abayisilamu barwanya perezida wa Uganda Yoweri Museveni.
Bari mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo kuva mu mwaka w’1995 kandi bagirizwa na reta ya Kongo hamwe na ONU kwica abanyagihugu baharurwa mu majana kuva mu mwaka wa 2014.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5010451' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/umushikiranganji-w-amagara-y-abantu-muri-kongo-yeguye-/5010451.html' term='ebola'>
Umushikiranganji w'Amagara y'Abantu muri Kongo Yeguye
Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Republika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kong, Oly Ilunga, kuri uno wa mbere yatanze imihoho.
Ilunga yari amaze imyaka ibiri aramutswa ubwo bushikiranganji yasiguye ko yeguye kubera ingingo ya Prezida Felix Tshisekedi yo gushira mu minwe y'ibiro vyiwe ikibazo co kurwanya Ebola.
Mw’ikete ryo gutanga imihoho yanditse Ilunga yumvikanishije ko ababajwe no kuba atashoboye gukorana na Prezida hamwe n’umushikiranganji wa mbere mu twigoro two kugwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
Prezida Tshisekedi aza yamaze kugena mu mabanga uwuzotwara umurwi w'igihugu mushasha ujejwe kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola muri Kongo. Ico kiza kibangamiye ubuseruko bwa Kongo kuva kicaduka kimaze guhitana abarenga 1600.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2424200' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2424200.html' term='ebola'>
Liberia Ibandanya Kugira Ibibazo, mu Rugamba rw'Ukurwanya Ebola
Umutekano uvurwa ko wagarutse, mu gice ca West Point, ku murwa mukuru w’igihugu ca Liberia, Monrovia, umusi umwe inyuma yuko igipolisi kirwanya imigumuko gitanye mu mitwe n’ababa mur’ico gice, bariko bagerageza kurwanya ikumirwa ryari ryagizwe, mu gice babamwo, mu gikoro k’ukurwanya ikwiragira ry’ikiza ca Ebola.
Abantu bane, canke barenga, barakomeretse, ku musi wa gatatu, igihe igipolisi carasa insoro, n’imyuka ibabaza mu maso, kugira gishwiragize abantu bari mu myiyerekano, bariko batera amabuye, bari bashavujwe n’iyugarwa ryabaye giturumbuka, ry’amabarabara yinjira n’ayasohoka, mu gice babamwo.
Muri ico gihe, abagira neza babiri b’Abanyamerika babiri, bari banduye umugera wa Ebola, mu gihugu ca Liberia, barakize, bakaba baravuye mu bitaro vyo mu gisagara ca Atlanta, mu bumanuko bwa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kenta Brantly, na Nancy Writebol, bavuriwe mu bitaro vyo kuri kaminuza ya Emory, n’imiti irimwo umuti ukiriko urageregezwa, uzwi kw’izina rya ZMapp.
Nibo bantu ba mbere bavuwe, hakoreshejwe uwo muti, abaganga bakaba batazi nimba warabafashije gukira.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, ryamenyesheje kw'abantu igihumbi n'amajana atatu na mirongo itanu bapfuye, bahitanywe n’ikiza ca Ebola, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, amajana atanu na mirongo irindwi na batandatu muribo, bakaba bava mu gihugu ca Liberia.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4972609' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4972609.html' term='ebola'>
Dikembe Mutombo Agiye Gufasha Kurwanya Ebola
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika bahisemwo umukinyi w’umupira w’amaboko yamuka muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, Dikembe Mutombo gufasha mu rugamba rwo kurwanya Ebola mu gihugu ciwe.
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Amerika bafashe ingingo yo kurondera Mutombo ngo afashe inyuma y’aho ubushikiranganji bw’Amerika bujejwe imigenderanire n’amakungu butegetse abahinga b’ikigo c’Amerika kijejwe kugenzura no gukinga ingwara, CDC kwigira kure uturere twafashwe kubw’umutekano wabo.
Mutombo yateye akamo asaba abanyagihugu mu turere ico kiza cateyemwo kwiyubara no kwitura abaganga.
Mutombo yashitse muri Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika mu myaka y’1980 aje gukurikirana ivyigwa vy’ubuvuzi ariko kandi abifatanya n’inkino, kandi azwi cane ku bikorwa afashisha igihugu ciwe c’amavuko.
Kimwe mu biza vyahitanye abatari bake muri kahise kimaze guhitana abashika 1,500 abandi 2,200 baramaze gufatwa kuva mu kwezi kw’umunani.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4389294' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4389294.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Abantu 17 Baramaze Kwicwa na Ebola
Ikiza ca Ebola muri Republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo carongeye guhitana uwundi muntu umwe, nk’uko vyatangajwe n’umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu, afise amakenga no ku bakozi bakora mu gisata c’ubuvuzi.
Umushikiranganji Dr Oly Ilunga, mw’itangazo yashikirije kuri uyu wa gatatu yavuze ko kuva kw’igenekerezo rya 8 ukwezi kwa gatanu, igihugu ca Kongo congeye guterwa na Ebola, gushika ubu abantu 11 bamaze gufatwa, umwe arapfa. Avuga ko igiteye amakenga ar’uko abakozi batatu bo mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu bari mu banduye, ari naco gituma hakwiye inyishu yihutirwa kuri ico kiza.
Uwo mushikiranganji yemeje ko yarungitse abahinga mu vy’ubuvuzi cumi na babiri i Mbandaka ku murwa mukuru w’intara ya Equateur.
Igihugu ca RDC catangaje ku musi wa kabiri ko cinjiranwe na Ebola ku ncuro y’icenda. Abantu 21 baramaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso vya Ebola kandi 17 baramaze gupfa.
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS ryasohoye umuliyoni w’amadolari y’Abanyamerika mu ntumbero yo guhagarika igwirirana ry’ico kiza.
Igihugu ca Nijeriya gihana urubibe na RDC, catangaje ku musi wa gatatu ko gihagaritswe umutima n’ico kiza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4419392' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/abanyekongo-barenga-700-bamaze-guhabwa-urukingo-rwa-ebola-/4419392.html' term='ebola'>
Abanyekongo Barenga 700 Bamaze Guhabwa Urukingo Rwa Ebola
Abantu bagera hafi kuri 700 bamaze guhabwa urukingo rw’indwara ya Ebola mu duce twagaragayemo iyo ndwara muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo.
Hagati aho inzego z’ubuvuzi zikomeje gushakisha abashobora kuba baranduye iyo ndwara kugirango bakingirwe.
Abantu barenga 25 nibo bamaze kwicwa niyo ndwara kuva yongeye kwaduka muri icyo gihugu. Ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS rivuga ko umubare w’abanduye ushobora kurenga 300 mu mezi ari imbere.
OMS ivuga ko uwo mubare ushobora kwikuba inshuro eshatu, iyo ndwara iramutse igeze mu mijyi.
Uwo muryango ukomeza uvuga ko nubwo iyo ndwara itarafatwa nk’icyorezo, ibyo bishobora guhinduka bigaragaye ko yiyongera cyangwa yarenze imbibe z’igihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5047867' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/drc-abantu-batatu-biciwe-mu-myigaragambyo/5047867.html' term='ebola'>
DRC: Abantu Batatu Biciwe mu Myigaragambyo
Abantu batatu bishwe kuri uyu wa mbere muri Repubulika Iharanira demokarasi ya Congo, ubwo polise yarasaga mu bigaragambyaga biturutse ku mutekano muke nk’uko umutegetsi wo mu karere yabibwiye ibiro ntaramakuru by’abafaransa AFP.
Dona Kibwana umuyobozi mu ntara ya Beni yagize ati: “Habaye imyigaragambyo yaguyemo abantu batatu- umugabo w’imyaka 25 yarashwe mu nda apfira mu bitaro, impunyu yarashwe yihise yitaba Imana, undi mwana warashwe nawe yarapfuye”.
Ibyo byabereye i Oicha umujyi uri mu bilometero hafi 30 uvuye mu mujyi wa Beni mu majyaruguru y’igihugu.
Noella Katongerwaki, uhagarariye imiryango gakondo mu ntara ya Beni, yavuze ko Polise yasandaje abigaragambyaga ibarasamo amasasu mazima n’ibyuka biryana mu maso.
Oicha, umurwa mukuru w’intara ya Kivu ya ruguru wabereyemo ubwicanyi, gutegekwa kwigura hamwe n’urundi urugomo rwawubayemo karande.
Ni akarere kugarijwe n’icyorezo cya Ebola, kari mu nzara z’abarwanyi, bishe abantu amagana mu myaka itanu ishize.
Imyigaragambyo Oicha yabaye nyuma y’umunsi umwe habaye igitero cyitiriwe abarwanyi b’abayisilamu bo muri Uganda, mu mutwe witwa Allied Democratic Forces. Ni imyigaragambyo yaguyemo abantu babiri. Abaturage barasaba abashinzwe umutekano gukora akazi kabo bakabarinda.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2499581' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2499581.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Umuforomokazi wa Kabiri Wanduye Ebola Yakize
Umuforomakazi wa kabiri wari waranduye indwara ya Ebola hano muri Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika yasezerewe amaze gukira.
Ibitaro bya Emory mu mujyi wa Atlanta aho Amber Vinson yavurirwaga byatangaje ko ibipimo byakozwe kuri uyu muforomokazi byemeza ko yakize burundu iyi ndwara imaze kuba icyorezo mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika.
Vinson yanduye Ebola ubwo yitaga ku munyaliberiya Eric Duncan, waje guhitanwa na Ebola. Mugenzi we Nina Pham, nawe wari waranduye iyi ndwara yasezerewe mu bitaro ku wa gatanu w’icyumweru gishize.
Ubwo yari amaze gusezererwa, Vinson w’imyaka 29 yatangaje ko yashimishijwe n'uko yakize.
Yagize ati “Ndashimira Imana kuba yarampaye icyizere n’imbaraga zo guhangana na Ebola.”
Kwandura kw’ababaforomokazi byateye abanyamerika ubwoba, benshi bagakeka ko icyo cyorezo kigiye gukwirakwira mu gihugu.
Hagati aho za leta zitandukanye hano muri Amerika zikomeje kugenda zishyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda Ebola. Muri izo zirimo gusaba abakozi bita ku barwayi bava mu bihugu bya Liberia, Guinea na Sierra Leone kutava mu ngo zabo igihe cy’iminsi 21.
Ariko iki cyemezo gikomeje guteza impaka hano muri Amerika. Ikigo gishinzwe gukumira no kurwanya indwara z’ibyorezo "Centers for Disease Control and Prevention" cyatangaje ko abo bakozi badakwiye gushyirwa mu kato, ko ahubwo igikenewe ari uko bakurikiranwa.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2414882' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-iravuduka-cyane/2414882.html' term='ebola'>
MSF: Hakenewe Amezi 6 yo Gukumira Icyorezo cya Ebola
WASHINGTON, DC —
Umuyobozi w’umuryango w’ubutabazi Medecins sans Frontieres avuga ko icyorezo cya Ebola muri Afurika y’uburengerazuba cyihuta cyane kurusha uko abakora ubutabazi bashobora kugikumira.
Perezida wa MSF Joanne Lui yavuze ko hakenewe uruhare rukomeye rwa OMS, ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima kw’isi, kugirango Ebola icururuke. Ibyo yabitangaje ageze I Geneve mu Busuwisi nyuma y’iminsi icumi yari amaze mu ruzinduko mu bihugu byagarijwe n’icyo cyorezo.
Madame Lui yatangaje ko bizafata amezi agera kuri atandatu kugirango Ebola ikumirwe. Taliki ya 14/08/2014, ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, ryaburiye abantu ko uburemere bwa Ebola busa nk’aho bwasuzuguwe.
OMS yatangaje ko abantu 1069 bamaze guhitanwa na Ebola uyu mwaka muri Guinea, Liberia na Sierra leone. Abamaze kwandura bagera hafi ku bihumbi 2000.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3864810' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3864810.html' term='ebola'>
OMS-RDC: Ibikorwa vyo Kurwanya Ebola Bigenda Neza
Umuyobozi w’igisata c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU cita ku magara y’abantu, OMS ku mugabane w’Afrika atangaza ko ibikorwa vyo kugenzura kugira ikiza ca Ebola nticandukire benshi muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo biriko bigenda neza.
Matshidiso Moeti, yabwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika ko atewe intege cane n’umwete hamwe n’ubwira reta ya Kongo, ifadikanije n'abayifasha mu gihugu ndetse n’abari mu makungu babikoranye kugira bahagarike ico kiza.
OMS yashikirije ibitigiri vy’abantu 29 bafashwe na Ebola, batatu yarabahitanye kuva aho igaragariye muri Kongo kw’italiki ya 22 z’ukwezi kwa kane guheze.
Umugera wa Ebola utera umururumbo, kuvirirana amaraso, kuyorwa hamwe n’ugucibwamwo. Ukwiragira mu mubiri ningoga ndetse ugashobora kwica 50 kw’ijana y’abo ufashe.
Bubaye ubugira umunani Ebola ivugwa muri Kongo kuva mu mwaka w’1976. Watanguye kwibonekeza ubwa mbere mu ntara ya Bas-Uele, mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko hafi y’igihugu ca Republika Centrafrika.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4436563' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4436563.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola Yaragwanijwe muri RDC Ariko nta Gusamara
Umuyobozi mukuru w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS, Tedros Adhanom kuri uyu wa kabiri yasavye ko hogenzurwa neza ivya Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, avuga ko naho ibitigiri vy’abandura vyagabanutse bidasigura ko hoca haba ugusamara. Ni mugihe yari arangije urugendo rw’imisi itatu yahoramwo muri ico gihugu.
Ico kiza ca Ebola cagaragaye kw’igenekerezo rya 8 z’ukwezi kwa gatanu kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw’abantu 27.
Tedros aremeza ko aravye ibitigiri uko bimeze, ibintu bimeze neza ariko avuga ko intambara na Ebola itararangira, bakwiye kuguma bagavye.
Uwo mutegetsi wa OMS avuga kandi ko abantu barenga ibihumbi bibiri bacandazwe mu ntara yabangamiwe n’ico kiza ya Equateur.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2620745' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2620745.html' term='ebola'>
Ishirahamwe rya Afrika Rirashigikiye Inteko 7,500 z'Ukurwanya Boko Haram
Ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika, ryarashigikiye imigambi yerekeye inteko zo mu karere, ibihumbi indwi n’amajana atanu, zijejwe kurwanya umurwi, Boko Haram.
Ivyerekeye iyo ngingo vyabaye, mu gihe ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika ryuguruye inama yaryo, yama iba uko umwaka utashe, ku murwa mukuru w’igihugu ca Ethiopia, Addis Abeba.
Ibihugu vya Nigeria, Cameroun, Chad, Niger na Benin, biherutse kwumvikana, ku vyerekeye gukorera hamwe, mu gikorwa c’ukurwanya umurwi, Boko Haram, wishe abasivile ibihumbi n’ibihumbi, muri iki gihe ukaba ufise ibice binini vy’intara ya Borno, ku mbibe y’ibihugu vya Cameroun, n’ikiyaga Chad.
Umutegetsi mukuru w’urwego rujejwe amahoro n’umutekano, rw’ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika, Smail Chergui, yatangaje kw’uwo mugambi uzoshikirizwa urwego rw’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu rujejwe umutekano kw’isi.
Ivyabona bavuga kw’inteko z’igihugu ca Chad, ziza zikorera mu gihugu ca Nigeria, zasubiye gufata, ku musi wa kane, imihana y’ahitwa, Malumfatori, yari mu minwe y’umurwi, Boko Haram.
Bitegekanijwe kw’ibibazo vyerekeye umurwi, Boko Haram, n’ikiza ca Ebola muri Afrika yo mu burengero, biza ubwa mbere, ku rutonde rw’ibibazo bizokwihwezwa n’ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika.
Muri ico gihe, abategetsi b’ibihugu vyvo muri Afrika bagenye prezida w’igihugu ca Zimbabwe, Robert Mugab,e kuyobora ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika.
Amashirahamwe adaharanira inyungu za politike yaranebaguye iyo ngingo, mu kuvuga ko kahise ka Mugabe, ku vyerekeye ityozwa ry’agateka ka muntu, vyotegerejwe gutuma ataba mu bashobora gushingwa ayo mabanga.
Prezida, Mugabe, muri iki gihe afise imyaka mirongo icenda, asubiriye prezida w’igihugu ca Mauritania, Mohamed Ould Abdel Aziz.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5167618' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-yoba-igiye-gutuzwa-muri-republika-ya-demokarasi-ya-kongo-/5167618.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yoba Igiye Gutuzwa muri Republika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo?
Perezida wa Republika ya demokarasi ya Kongo, Felix Tshisekedi yatangaje ko afise icizere ko ikiza ca Ebola kizoba carangiye mu gihugu ciwe mu ndwi ziri imbere.
Tshisekedi yemeje ko abantu bagifise Ebola bari ku rushi mu ntara ya Ituri iri mu buseruko bw’igihugu. Yamara yibaza ko bashobora guhagarika burundu ico kiza mu mpera z’uyu mwaka.
Abantu barenga 2000 barahitanywe na Ebola muri Kongo. Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU ryatangaje Ebola ko ari ikibazo cihutirwa mu makungu mu kwezi kw’indwi k’uyu mwaka w’i 2019. Igitigiri c’abantu banduye Ebola caragabanutse bikomeye kuva ico gihe.
Mu vyo yatangaje mu gisagara ca Berlin inyuma yuko abonanye na Chanceliere w’Ubudagi, Angela Merkel, Tshisekedi yatangaje ko yipfuza gukorana n’igihugu ico arico cose gishaka gucukura ubutare bukomeye butandukanye buri mu gihugu ciwe, harimwo Ubushinwa n’Uburusiya.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2567689' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2567689.html' term='ebola'>
Igitigiri c'Abitavye Amatora, muri Liberia, Cari Hasi, Kubera Ubwoba bwa Ebola
Abakozi bajejwe amagara y’abantu, bari bahagarikiye ibibanza vy’amatora, ku musi wa gatandatu, mu gihe abanya Liberia bariko batora aba senatari, mu matora yigijweyo incuro zibiri, kubera ikiza ca Ebola, muri Liberia.
Abategetsi bajejwe amatora, mu gihugu ca Liberia, bategetse kw’abantu bose basukura iminwe yabo, bakongera bagapimwa ubushuhe bw’umubiri, imbere yuko binjira ,mu bibanza vy’amatora, bakirinda n’ukwegerana, mu biri musi y’imetero.
Abanebagura kugirisha ayo matora, baribaza nimba vyari bikwiye kw’abantu, mu bishobora gutuma umugera wa Ebola ukwiragira, mu bantu batonze imirongo, mu bibanza vy’amatora.
Igitigiri c’abitavye amatora, mu gihugu cose, kivurwa ko cari hasi.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagaara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, ryatangaje mw’ijoro ryo ku musi wa gatanu, kw’abantu barenga ibihumbi indwi n’amajana ane, bapfuye bahitanywe na Ebola, mu bihugu vya Liberia, Guinee na Sierra Leone, ibihugu bitatu vyageramiwe bikomeye kurusha ibindi, n’ikiza ca Ebola.
Igihugu ca Liberia nico gihugu gifise igitigiri kinini cane c’abantu bapfuye, bahitanywe na Ebola, n’ukuvuga abantu barenga ibihumbi bitatu n’amajana atatu, naho igitigikri c’abantu bashasha bandura Ebola, gisa n’ikiriko kiragabanuka.
Igitigiri, muri rusangi, c’abantu bafise Ebola, muri Liberia,Guinee, na Sierra Leone, muri iki gihe, kigeze ku bihumbi cumi n’icenda na mirongo itatu n’umwe.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5118594' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/oms-yizera-ko-vuba-ebola-muri-kongo-izotuzwa-/5118594.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Yizera ko Vuba Ebola muri Kongo Izotuzwa
Ishami rya ONU ryitaho amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, ritangaza ko ikiza ca Ebola muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gisigaye gutuzwa mu karere gato ko mu buseruko bw’ico gihugu. Gusa, OMS ivuga ko ikiyihangayikishije ubu ari uko ako karere karangwamwo umutekano muke ubangamira ibikorwa vyo gukinga.
Mu kiganiro umukuru w’igisata kijejwe guhangana n’ibiza muri OMS, Michael Ryan, yahaye abamenyeshamakuru i Genève mu Buswisse inyuma y’urugendo yahoramwo muri Kongo, yavuze ko afise ivyizere vy’uko ico kiza vuba kizotuzwa burundu muri Kongo.
Michael Ryan yavuze kandi ko hagiye gutanguzwa urucanco rwa kabiri rwo gukinga Ebola. Urwo rucanco ruzotangwa mu burere ata Ebola ikivugwamwo nka Goma.
OMS itangaza ko kuva mu kwezi kw’umunani mu mwaka w’2018 abamaze guhitanwa na Ebola muri Kongo ari 2.144.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2551273' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2551273.html' term='ebola'>
Umwaka w'2014, Wabaye Umwaka Mubi Cane, ku Bana
Ishami ry’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryitaho abana, UNICEF, rimenyesha kw’umwaka w’2014 wabaye umwaka mubi cane ku bana, mu gihe abana imiliyoni n’imiliyoni bageramiwe bikomeye.
Umuyobozi w’ishirahamwe UNICEF, Anthony Lake, yatangaje, ku musi wa mbere, kw’abana biciwe mu bitanda vyabo, mu mashule, babaye impfuvyi, banyurujwe n’abasirikare, bafashwe bunyamaswa, bafashwe ku nguvu, baragurishwa kugira bagirwe abashumba.
Anthony Lake, avuga kw’abana batari bwakorerwe ubunyamaswa butagira uko buvurwa nkubwo, mu bihe vya vuba.
Anthony Lake, avuga kw’ingwano, n’ayandi mabi muri Centrafrique, Iraki, Syria, mu ntara z’abanya Palestina, Sudani yo mu bumanuko, na Ukraine, biri mu vyatumye abana bakorerwa ayo mabi.
Yongeye kandi avuga kw’ikiza ca Ebola muri Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone, ari ikintu gishasha gishobora kugeramira abana.
Yamara ishirahamwe UNICEF, rivuga ko kubera utwigoro twaryo, n’igikorwa c’ayandi mashirahamwe, habaye umwizero, ku bana muri uyu mwaka.
Harimwo gusubiza mu mashule, abana ibihumbi amajana n’amajana, muri Centrafrique, gukingira abana indwara y’ubukagwe, hakoreshejwe incandago, mu karere k’Abarabu, n’ukuvura ababa bafungura nabi cane, muri Afrika y’epfo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2573788' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2573788.html' term='ebola'>
Papa Faransisiko Arasengera Amahoro kw'Isi
Uyu munsi, abemera Krisitu biriwe mu minsi mikuru ya Noheli. Mu mujyi wa Betelehemu muri Palesitina, abakristu bateraniye mu kiliziya yubatse ahantu bemeza ko Yezu yavukiye. Umushumba wa Yerusalem, Arikiyepiskopi Fouad Twal nawe yasomeye misa abantu amagana.
Umushumba wa kiliziya gatulika y’isi yose, Papa Fransisko, nawe yasomeye misa abantu ibihumbi n’ibihumbi ku rubuga rwitiriwe mutagatifu Petero, i Vaticani. Yamaganye yivuye inyuma urugomo rwa kinyamaswa umutwe wa Etat Islamique ugirira abakristu mu karere wigaruriye muri Syria na Iraq.
Papa Fransisko yasabiye kandi amahoro ibihugu biri mu ntambara, nka Ukraine, Nigeria, na Republika ya Centrafrika. Yamaganye igitero cy’aba-Talibani cyahitanye abana b’abanyeshuli bagera ku 150 ku italiki ya 16 y’uku kwezi mu mujyi wa Peshawar muri Pakistani.
Yasabiye umugisha abaturage bugarijwe na Ebola n’abayirwanya, by’umwihariko muri Liberia, Sierra Leone na Guinea.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4409369' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4409369.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Umupadiri Yanduye Ebola i Mbandaka Yakuwe mu Bandi
Umupadiri Katolika yakuwe mu bandi ashirwa mu kibanza ca wenyene inyuma y’aho bigaragariye ko yanduye umugera Ebola i Mbandaka, mu buraruko bushira uburengero bwa Republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo ahabangamiye n’ico kiza, nkuko amakuru ava mu baganga abivuga.
Amakuru itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa, AFP ryakuye mu baganga avuga ko uwo mupadiri ari uwo muri diyoseze ya Mbandaka-Bikoro.
Ku musi wa gatatu, abategetsi ba Kongo bavuze ko abantu boza baritondera amakuru ashikirizwa ku bantu bavugwa ko banduye, bakarindira ayavuye mu bushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu.
Ikiza ca Ebola catanguye gutangazwa kw’itariki ya 8 z’ukwezi kwa gatanu mu gisagara ca Bikoro, kiri ku birometero 600 uva ku murwa mukuru Kinshasa, ku rubibe n’ibihugu ca Kongo Brazaville.
OMS ivuga ko abantu 58 basuzumwe ko banduye uyo mugera.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5300940' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5300940.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Igabisha ko Ikehaniwe Amafaranga yo Kurwanya Ebola muri RDC
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS risaba uburyo bwihuta bw’imiliyoni 40 z’amadolari y'abanyamerika yo gufasha mu bikorwa vyo kurandurana n'imizi umugera wa Ebola mu buseruko bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo.
Umuvugizi wa OMS, Tarik Jasarevic avuga ko kudafasha mur’ivyo bikorwa bishobora kubangamira utwigoro hamwe n’intambwe nziza ziriko ziraterwa mu kurwanya Ebola.
Mu mezi arenga abiri, Jasarevic avuga ko hagati y’abantu 3 na 15 bandura Ebola aribo bamenyekana buri ndwi.
OMS ivuga kandi ko igabanuka ry’ikwirakwira ry’uwo mugera n’igabanuka ry’abandura ari ivyo kwishimira.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2459388' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/imiti-ya-ebola-muri-afurika/2459388.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola: Imiti Izageragezwa muri Afurika y'Uburengerazuba
Imiti ya Ebola igiye kugeragezwa muri Afrika yo mu Burengerazuba. Iyo miti izageragezwa ni nk’umwe mu migambi yo gushakisha vuba na vuba bwo kuvura iyo ndwara ihitana abantu umusubizo.
Ikigo gifasha abatishoboye gifite icyicaro cyacyo I Londre mu Bwongereza, cyitwa the Wellcome Trust, cyavuze ko gihaye miliyoni 5.2 z’amadolari imiryango itanga infashanyo, ibigo by’ubushakashatsi n’ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, kugirango bishyireho ibigo by’ubuvuzi byo kugeragerezamo ubuvuzi bwa Ebola.
Kugeza ubu Ebola nta muti igira nta n’urukiko. Iyi ndwara imaze kwanduza abantu barenga 5,600 kandi yahitanye abarenga 2,800 mu Burengerazuba bwa Afrika muri uyu mwaka, abenshi ni abo muri Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone.
Ikigo the Wellcome Trust, kivuga ko abakora imiti bafite uruhare muri uwo mushinga barimo, MAPP Biopharmaceutical, gifite umuti uzwi ku izina rya Zmapp utarageragezwa, wahawe abantu bake barwaye Ebola, kimwe n’isosiyeti yo muri Canada, Tekmira, n’indi ifite icyicaro muri Leta Zunze ubumwe za Amerika yitwa Sarepta.
Uburyo igeragezwa ry’iyo miti rizakorwa birajyaganirwaho. The Wellcome Trust ivuga ko amatsinda azakora iryo gerageza, arimo gukorana n’abakozi bo mu buvuzi mu bihugu birimo indwara ya Ebola, kugirango bahitemo ahantu habereye iryo gerageza ry’imiti.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5016595' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5016595.html' term='ebola'>
Arabiya Sawudite Yahagaritse Gutanga Visa ku Banyekongo
Igihugu ca Arabiya Sawudite cahagaritse guha ama visa abantu bavuye muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo kubera ikiza ca Ebola kivurwa muri ico gihugu. Ivyo naho ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi ryari ryasavye ko ingingo nkiyo itofatwa.
Bamwe mu bayislamu bo muri Kongo bari bafise imigambi y’ukugira urugendo mu kibanza ceranda c’idini rya kiyisilamu muri Arabiya Sawudite mu kwezi kuza.
Ikete ubushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire bwa Arabiya Sawudite bwandikiye ku musi wa gatatu Ambasade ya Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo i Riyadh, itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abanyamerika, Associated Press ryashoboye kuronka rivuga ko Arabiya Sawuduite yafashe iyo ngingo kugira ikingire abantu bagira urugendo mu kibanza ceranda c’idini rya kiyisilamu muri ico gihugu hamwe n’abandi.
Arabiya Sawudite yarahagaritse kandi gutanga ama visa ku bantu bava mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero igihe ikiza ca Ebola ciyadukiza muri ako karere. Abantu barenga 11,000 barahitanywe n’ico kiza muri ako karere ico gihe.
Ingingo ya Arabiya Sawudite yerekeye umuntu uwariwe wese avuye muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, harimwo n’abadafise ubwenegihugu bwaho. Ntaco Reta ya Kongo iratangaza ku mugaragaro kuri iyo ngingo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2445821' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2445821.html' term='ebola'>
Ishirahamwe, Bill and Melinda, ryemeye Gutanga Imiliyoni 50 y'amadolari, y'Ukurwanya Ebola
Ishirahamwe The Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation, ryatangaje ko ryiyemeje gutanga imiliyoni mirongo itanu y'amadolari, agenwe kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola, gitera gikwiragira, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Ishirahamwe Bill and Melinda Foundation, rifise cicaro mu gisagara ca Seattle, muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ryamenyesheje ko rizoha buno nyene ayo mafranga, ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu O-N-U, n'amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu y'abagira neza, kugira agure ibintu bikenewe vyihutirwa, n'ugufasha ibikorwa vyihutirwa, mu bihugu bigeramiwe n'ikiza ca Ebola.
Ishirahamwe, Bill and Linda Foundation, rimenyesha kandi ko rizokorana n'abandi, kugira binyarutse gushiraho uburyo bw'ukuvura, incandago n'uburyo bw'ugupima, kugira bashobore kuvura neza, n'ugutuma ikiza ca Ebola kidatera gikwiragira.
Ku musi wa kabiri kandi, ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu O-N-U, ryatanze imiliyoni zitatu n'ibihumbi amajana umunani vy'amadolari, agenewe gufasha kujana infashanyo, ibikoresho n'abahinga, mu vy'ubuvuzi, mu bihugu bigeramiwe n'ikiza ca Ebola.
Imihango y'ugutanga ayo mafranga ikwirikiye akamo katewe n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu O-N-U, Ban Ki-moon, k'inyishu ikomeye cane y'amakungu, ku vyerekeye ikiza ca Ebola.
Ku bw'ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi, O-M-S, ikiza ca Ebola kimaze guhitana abantu bagera ku bihumbi bibiri n'amajana atatu, muri uyu mwaka, benshi muribo mu bihugu vya Guinee, Sierra Leone na Liberia.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4903828' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4903828.html' term='ebola'>
Umuvuduko w'Abandura Ebola Muri Kongo Uriyongera
Umuryango mpuzamahanga utabara imbabare uratangaza ko icyorezo cya Ebola muri Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo gikomeje kugarika ingogo.
Kimaze guhitana abarenga 1,000. Uwo muryango uravuga ko mu cyumweru gishize abantu 23 banduye mu munsi umwe gusa. Uwo ni wo mubare munini w’abanduye ubwo burwayi mu gihe cy’umunsi umwe kuva mu mwaka wa 2018.
Ejo ku wa gatanu minisiteri y’ubuzima muri Kongo yavugaga ko Ebola imaze guhitana abagera ku 1,008.
Imvururu zirangwa mu bice bimwe by’icyo gihugu ntibyorohereza inzego z’ubuzima gahunda zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi itera Ebola. Uko abantu bashya bagenda bandura ni nako gahunda zo kuvura no gukumira iyo ndwara zikomwa mu nkokora. Abantu benshi batinya kujya aho bivuriza Ebola kubera gutinya imvururu bagahitamo kwigumira mu rugo bityo bakanduza ababarwaza n’abaturanyi babo.
Nicole Fassina, ushinzwe guhuza ibikorwa byo kurwanya indwara ya Ebola mu muryango mpuzamahanga utabara imbabare aravuga ko bishoboka ko abantu benshi bashobora kwandura kubera ikibazo cy’umutekano kitorohereza imiromo y’ubutabazi. Yavuze ko ubuke bw’ibikoresho n’abakozi b’inzego z’ubuzima bakora mu kurwanya iyi ndwara nabyo bishobora gutuma ikwira no mu bindi bihugu bituranye na Congo.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe ibikorwa by’ingoboka mu muryango mpuzamahanga wita ku buzima Michael Ryan, yavuze ko ibi ari ibihe bikomeye handi biruhije babona ko abantu benshi bashobora kwandura icyo cyorezo.
Abantu benshi bahitanywe na Ebola muri Afurika y’uburengerazuba aho kuva mu mwaka 2014 kugeza 2016 abarenga 11,000 bari bamaze kwicwa n’iki cyorezo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2460861' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2460861.html' term='ebola'>
Perezida Obama Yateye Akamo Gasaba Gutuza Intagondwa Z’Abaislamiste
Mw’ijambo yashikirije inama nkuru y’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ku musi wa gatatu itariki 24 y'ukwezi kw'icenda, umwaka w'2014, umushingantahe Obama yavuze kw’uyo murwi utera ubwoba abanyagihgu bo muri Iraki na Syria, mu kubaca imitwe, mu kurasaba abana, mu gufuba imivyimba mu kinogo kimwe hamwe no m u kwicisha inzara abanyagihugu bari mu madini y’abantu bari ku rushi.
President wa reta zunze ubumwe za amerika , Baracak Obama yateye akamo amakungu, na cane cane abaIslamu, kabasaba kwiyamiriza bivuye inyuma ivyiyumviro hamwe n’ingendo vy’imirwi y’intagondwa, Etat Islamic hamwe na Al-Qaida. Yavuze kw’ako karanda k’izo ntagondwa, gategerezwa kurangira.
Umushingantahe Obama yiyamirije kandi agasotoro k’igihugu c’Uburusiya mu gihugu ca Ukraine.
Vyongeye, yateye akamo amakungu yose, gasaba guhagarika ikiza ca Ebola, kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw’anyagihugu ibihumbi n’ibihumbi muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4983810' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4983810.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Hafi y'Urubibe na Sudani y'Ubumanuko
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu bemeje ko hari umuntu yanduye Ebola ku bilometero 70 umuntu avuye ku rubibe Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo ihana n’igihugu ca Sudani yo mu bumanuko.
Ivyo birateye impungenge kubera Sudani yo mu bumanuko ititeguye bikwiriye guhangana n’ikiza ca Ebola hamwe cokwiyadukiza muri ico gihugu.
Inkuru yerekeye umuntu yanduye Ebola hafi ya Sudani yo mu bumanuko yatangajwe uno musi ku wa kabiri n’ubushikiranganji bujejwe amagara y’abantu muri ico gihugu.
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu bemeje iyo nkuru uno musi ku wa kabiri.
Kuva cadutse, ikiza ca Ebola kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 1.500 muri Kongo. Ico kiza kikaba caratandukiye igihugu ca Uganda aho cishe abantu 2 mu kwezi guheze.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3123099' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3123099.html' term='ebola'>
Gineya: Nta Ngwara ya Ebola Ikiharangwa
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi batangaza ko igihugu ca Gineya cakuwe kurutonde rw’ibihugu birimwo ingwara ya Ebola, nyuma yaho abantu barenge 2,500 bahitanywe nayo muri ico gihugu.
Iryo tangazo rituma hasigara igihugu ca Liberiya conyene kurutonde rw’ibihugu vyari birindiriye kuva kururwo rutonde.
Umukuru wa banki nkuru y’isi Jim Yong Kim yasoye urwandiko ashimira reta n’abanyagihugu ba Gineya, kuba bashitse kuri iyo ntambwe ikomeye. Yasavye yivuye inyuma ko vyoguma ata muntu n’umwe asubiriye kwandura iyo ngwara.
Ejo ku musi wa gatatu ku mugwa mukuru wa Conakry, niho hazoba umusi mukuru wo gushikiriza icese iryo tangazo.
Umugwayi wanyuma yari azwi kuba akiriko aravugwa Ebola muri Gineya mukwezi kwa cumi na rimwe, yari uruyoya rw’imisi 21 rwari ruri mwivuriro riri mugisagara ca Conakry.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2551260' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2551260.html' term='ebola'>
Sierra Leone, Yarenganye Liberia, Ku Bijanye n'Igitigiri c'Abantu Bafise Ebola
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, rimenyesha kw’abandi bantu bashasha babandanya kwandura Ebola, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, ishirahamwe O-M-S, rikaba rivuga ko Sierra Leone yarenganye Liberia, nk’igihugu gifise igitigiri kiri hejuru cane, c’abantu banduye Ebola.
Ibiharuro vyashikirijwe, ku musi wa mbere, n’ishirahamwe O-M-S, vyerekana kw’igihugu ca Sierra Leone, gifise abantu ibihumbi indwi n’amajana indwi na mirongo icenda n’umunani bafise Ebola, mu vyerekana ko Ebola ikIriko ikwiragira ningoga cane rwose, muri ico gihugu.
Urugero rw’abandura Ebola ruriko ruragabanuka muri Liberia, aho abafise Ebola bari hejuru gatoyi y’ibihumbi indwi n’amajana indwi.
Abantu baracahitanwa na Ebola, ari benshi, muri Liberria, kurusha mu bindi bihugu bigeramiwe n’ico kiza, muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S, ryatangaje ko muri rusangi, Ebola yandukiye abantu begera ku bihumbi cumi n’umunani, ihitana abantu ibihumbi bitandatu n’amajana atatu na mirongo ine na batandatu.
Igitigiri kinini c’abanduye Ebola cibonekeje, mu bihugu vya Liberia, Sierra Leone na Guinee.
Mu raporo yayo mu ndwi iheze, ishirahamwe O-M-S, ryamenyesheje kw’abantu babandanya kwandura Ebola, muri Sierra Leone. Igice kigeramiwe bikomeye cane akaba ari umurwa mukuru wa Sierra Leone, Freetown.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S, rivuga kw’ibitigiri biriko bisa n’ibitera bigabanuka, mu bihugu vya Liberia na Guinee.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4724318' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/congo-internet-izoguma-yugaye-gushika-hamenyekanye-uwatsinze/4724318.html' term='ebola'>
Congo: Internet Izoguma Yugaye Gushika Hamenyekanye Uwatsinze
Ubutegetsi muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo buracugaye internet mu gihugu cose mu gihe abanyagihugu barindiriye ivyavuye mu matora yo ku munsi wa Mungu yaranzwe n'akajagari mu turere tutari duke.
Umuhanuzi wa Perezida Joseph Kabila, Barnabe Kikaya bin Karubi, yasiguye ko Reta yugaye internet n'imbuga zose ngurukanabumenyi mu ntumbero yo kwirinda imigumuko, inyuma yaho hari amakuru y'ibihuha y'ivyavuye mu matora yahanahanywe ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi.
Bitegekanijwe ko ivyavuye mu matora bitangazwa igenekerezo rya 15 k'uno kwezi kwa mbere umukuru w'igihugu mushasha nawe akarahira itariki 18. Baba abatavuga rumwe na Reta co kimwe n'abashigikiwe n'ubutegetsi bose bavuga ko bizeye intsinzi.
Mu gihe amatora mu turere tuvugwamwo Ebola n'umutekano muke nka Beni, Butembo na Yumbi yungururijwe mu kwezi kwa gatatu uno mwaka, abasesanguzi muri politike bavuga ko bishobora kuzokwega amatati na rirya azotunganywa umukuru w’igihugu mushasha yahejeje kurahira.
Ubutegetsi bwa Congo bwatangaje ko internet n'imbuga zicishwako amakuru bitariko birakora kuva kuri uno wa mbere bizoguma vyugawe gushika ivyavuye mu matora bitangajwe.
Hambavu ya internet yaciwe muri Congo, n'iradiyo mpuzamakungu y'Abafaransa RFI Abanyekongo batari bake bakurako amakuru yarugawe.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4524405' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-yahitanye-uwugira-11-muri-kongo-/4524405.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yahitanye Uwugira 11 muri Kongo
Ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu muri Kongo bwatangaje kuri uno wa gatandatu ko ikiza ca Ebola cahitanye uwundi muntu umwe wo muri Kivu y’Amajepfo.
Uwo umwe yiyongeye ku bandi cumi bo mu karere ka Beni bari bamaze kwemezwa ko bahitanywe na Ebola muri uku kwezi kwa munani.
Mu gihe akarere ka Beni kariko kavugwa mwo Ebola gahanzwe n’abarwanyi bitwaje ibigwanisho batandukanye, abategetsi mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu bavuze ko hari umurwi w’abahinga mu vy’ukuvura barungitswe gucungera umutekano no kubandnaya amahimiriza.
Ni inyuma yaho kuri uno wa gatanu abagera kuri batandatu bishwe n’abarwanyi bo mu murwi ADF urwanya Reta ya Uganda.
Bugize ubugira cumi Kongo ihangana na Ebola kuva yadutsemu 1976.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2562906' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2562906.html' term='ebola'>
Ingaruka z'Ubukungu mu Bihugu Byahuye na Ebola
Ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku biribwa ryatangaje ko umubare w’abaturage bazahura n’ikibazo cy’ubuke bw’ibiribwa mu bihugu byazahajwe na Ebola – Guinea, Liberia na Sierra Leone, ushobora kuba warenze miliyoni mu kwezi kwa gatatu muri 2015..
Iri shami, FAO, rivuga Ebola yatumye bigorana kugeza ibiribwa ku masoko muri ibyo bihugu bitatu byari n’ubundi bisanganywe ikibazo cyo kutagita ibiribwa bihagize bigeza ku baturage babyo.
Mu itangazo, FAO yagaragaje ko gufunga imipaka, gushira abantu mu kato n’ibindi byemezo byagiye bifatwa muri gahunda yo gukumira Ebola byagiye bibangamira gahunda zo kugeza ibiribwa ku masoko.
Umubare w’abantu bafite ikibazo cy’ibiribwa ubu uhagaze hafi ku bihumbi 500 muri ibyo bihugu uko ari bitatu.
Kuri uyu wa gatatu, muri Sierra Leone mu murwa mukuru Freetown, batangije igikorwa cyo gusaka amazu bashakisha abantu bashobora kuba barwaye badashaka ko bimenyekana.
Mu itangazo prezida w’icyo gihugu Ernest Bai Koromo yasabye abaturage kudahisha abarwayi ubwo abashinzwe ubuzima bazaba basura amago yabo.
Hagati aho Sierra Leone yahagritse ibirori by’iminsi ya noheli bikorerwa mu ruhame kugirango barinde abantu kwanduzanya ebola.
Hakurikije imibare y’ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 6800.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3068106' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3068106.html' term='ebola'>
Liberiya: Ebola Yongeye Kubura
Mu gihugu ca Liberiya abantu batatu nibo bongeye kumenyekana ko banduye umugera wa Ebola. Ivyo bishitse mugihe ata mezi arahera hahimbajwe mur’ico gihugu umusi mukuru wo gusezerera ico kiza.
Abo bantu batatu bagizwe n’umwana w’umuhungu w’imyaka cumi hamwe n’abandi babiri bo mu muryango wiwe nkuko bimenyeshwa n’abajejwe ubuvuzi muri Liberiya.
Mu kwezi kwa gatanu italiki icenda niho ishirahamwe ryita kumagara y’abantu kw’isi OMS ryatangaza ko Igihugu ca Liberiya kitakivugwamwo Ebola.
Liberia ni kimwe mu bihugu vyo muri Afrika y’Uburengero vyasinzikajwe n’ico kiza aho kuva mu mwaka wa 2013 abantu bashika 10000 bawanduye, muri bo abarenga 4800 bakaba barahasize ubuzima.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2566977' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2566977.html' term='ebola'>
Ban Ki moon, Ari mu Rugendo, Mu Bice Bisinzikajwe, na Ebola, muri Afrika yo mu Burengero
Umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ON-U, Ban Ki moon, ari mu rugendo, mu bihugu vyo muri Afrika yo mu burengero, biriko bihangana n’indwara ya Ebola, aho yemeye kw’ishirahamwe O-N-U rizobandanya, mu rugamba rw’ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
Ban Ki moon, yaragendeye, Sierra Leone, ku musi wa gatanu, aho yahayagije abakozi bajejwe amagara y’abantu, bariko barwanya Ebola, mu kubita intwari.
Umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe O-N-U, Ban Ki moon, yatangaje kw’abantu bose bategerezwa kuba magabo, ku vyerekeye umugera wa Ebola. Akaba yavuze kw’umugambi uhari, ar’ugutuma ata muntu numwe asubira kwandura umugera wa Ebola.
Mu masaha yo gitondo, co ku musi wa gatanu, muri Liberia, Bana Ki moon, yatangaje kw’afise umwizero witondewe, kw’ikiza ca Ebola gishobora gutsindwa.
Yatangaje kw’igitigiri kinini c’abantu bashobora kwivuza, yamara yaragabishije kw’umuntu umwe, yanduye uwo mugera, ashobora gutuma Ebola isubira kuba ikiza kibica bigacika.
Ibiharuro bishasha vyashikirijwe, ku musi wa gatanu n’ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, rivuga kw’igitigiri c’abantu bafise Ebola kigera ku bihumbi cumi n’umunani n’amajana atandatu na batatu, abamaze gupfa nabo bagera, ku bihugu bitandatu n’amajana icenda na cumi na batanu.
Raporo y’ishirahamwe, O-M-S, imenyesha kw’igitigiri c’abantu bashasha bandura Ebola, kiriko kiragabanuka, mu gihugu ca Liberia, gitera gihindagurika muri Guinee, mu gihe ico gitigiri gishobora kuba carahagaritse kwiyongera, mu gihugu ca Sierra Leone.
Iyo raporo itangaza kandi kw’ata bantu bashasha ,bavurwa ko banduye Ebol,a mu gihugu ca Mali, kuva kw’italiki 24 z’ukwezi kw’icumi na rimwe.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5203334' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/abanduye-ebola-bariyongereye-mu-burasirazuba-bwa-congo-/5203334.html' term='ebola'>
Abanduye Ebola Bariyongereye mu Burasirazuba bwa Kongo
Abantu banduye Ebola bariyongereye mu burasirazuba bwa Republika ya demokrasi ya Kongo. Abagera kuri 20 babaruwe mu bayanduye Ebola mu minsi itatu ishize babivuze uyu munsi kuwa kane.
Abandi 10 babimenyeshejwe ejo kuwa gatatu i Mabalako honyine, mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru, nyuma ya batandatu bo kuwa kabiri nk’uko byatangajwe na komite yashinzwe kurwanya Ebola. Ni komite ihuriwemo n’impuguke zitandukanye. Batatu muri batandatu bayigize ni abavuzi ba gihanga.
Abantu barenga 2,200 barapfuye kuva hatangajwe icyorezo cya Ebola muri Kongo mu kwezi kwa 8 mu mwaka ushize.
Komite ikurikirana indwara ya Ebola muri Kongo ivuga ko ibitero by’imitwe yitwaje intwaro ku bakozi bo mu buvuzi bahanganye na Ebola, byazitiye ibikorwa byabo mu bice bya Beni, Biakato na Mangina.
Ibyo bitero byatumye Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima, OMS n’Umuryango w’Abaganga Batagira Imipaka (MSF) bakura abakozi i Biakato.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5000478' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5000478.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Umurwayi wa Mbere wa Ebola Yabonetse i Goma
Umuntu wa mbere yanduye umugera wa Ebola yemejwe i Goma, igisagara kinini Ebola itanguye kwibonekezamwo kuva itangura kugaragara mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo mu kwezi kwa munani umwaka uheze, nkuko vyashikirijwe n’ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu ejo kuw’Imana.
Uwo murwayi yashitse i Goma mu mutwenzi wo kuw’Imana avuye i Butembo, kimwe mu bisagara vyagaragayemwo Ebola mu ntara ya Kivu y’Uburaruko.
Ubwo bushikiranganji bwemeza ko Goma itazosinzikara kuko Ebola yamenyekanye agishika ndetse n’abantu barikumwe muri bus batangura gucandarwa kuri uyu wa mbere.
Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo imaze guhitana ubuzima bw’abantu 1,655, nkuko bishikirizwa n’ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu. Iyi nkuru Ijwi ry’Amerika riyikesha itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa, AFP.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3291731' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3291731.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Kurwanya Zika Birihutirwa
Abasenateri ba Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika bo mu mugambwe w’aba Demokrate basaba bagenzi babo b’aba republika biharije inama nshingamateka y’Amerika kwemeza itegeko rigena amafaranga ashika umuliyaridi n’ibice icenda vy’amadolari yo kurwanya umugera wa Zika muri Amerika.
Abo ba senateri b’aba demokrate bidogera bagenzi babo b’aba republika ko bariko barakwega amaguru mugihe abanyamerika bashika 800 bageramiwe n’uyo mugera, harimwo abakenyezi 89 bibungenze bageramiwe cane.
Leta ya Perezida Barack Obama yatangaje mu ndwi irangiye ko ishobora kuba irikora ku miliyoni 510 z’amadolari yari agenewe kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola mu guhangana n’uwo mugera wa Zika.
Abategetsi bo muvy’amagara y’abantu muri Amerika baremeje mu ndwi iheze ko abakenyezi bibungeze banduye uwo mugera wa Zika bavyara abana bafise imitwe mito. Babasaba kwirinda kuja mu bihugu vyo muri Amerika y’epfo aho uwo mugara waturutse.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4518302' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4518302.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Abantu 9 Bashasha Baramaze Kwicwa na Ebola
Abantu icenda nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko bishwe na Ebola kuv’aho ico kiza congeye kwiyadukiza muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo muri uku kwezi. Ivyo vyashikirijwe n’umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu kuri uyu wa kabiri.
Ibiharuro vya mbere vyari vyashikirijwe n’abategetsi vyari indwi, babiri biyongereyeko mu nyuma, bose ni mu ntara ya Beni mu buraruko bw’intara ya Kivu y’uburaruko.
Mu kiza gihitiye, abantu 34 barapfuye mu buraruko bushira uburengero, cari catangajwe ko casezerewe mu mpera z’ukwezi kw’indwi.
Umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu yashikirije ejo kuwa kabiri ko abantu 43 aribo bagaragaje ibimenyetso vya Ebola, abandi 46 bakiriko baragirwako amatohozwa.
Ibikorwa vyo gucandaga bitegekanijwe gutangura kuri uyu wa gatatu, kuko abajejwe ico gikorwa baza baramaze gushika mu ntara ya Beni, nkuko bishikirizwa n’uwo mushikiranganji.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4533030' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-yabaye-ndanse-muri-kongo-/4533030.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yabaye Ndanse muri Kongo
Leta ya Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo na OMS baratangaza uyu munsi ko abantu 78 banduye ebola mu burasirazuba bw’igihugu. Abandi bantu 24 bayikekwaho barimo barakurikiranwa hafi, naho abandi 44 yarabihitanye. Muri aba 44 bitabye Imana, 41 ni abo mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru. batatu bandi ni abo mu ntara bituranye ya Ituri.
Iyi ebola yahagurukije umuyobozi w’ikigo CDC cya Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika gishinzwe gukumira no kurwanya ibyorezo, Robert Redfield. Uyu munsi yaganiriye na minisitiri w’ubuzima wa Congo, Ilunga Kalenga, i Kinshasa. Bavuganye kuri gahunda za CDC zo guhugura abanyekongo barwanya ibyorezo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4807250' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4807250.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Ikigo Kivura Ebola Caratewe n'Abarwanyi i Butembo
Abantu bitwaje ibirwanisho barateye ikigo kivura abanduye umugera wa Ebola mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo ejo ku musi wa gatatu, baragiturira imbere yo gutana mu mitwe n’abajejwe umutekano, ivyo vyashikirijwe n’abategetsi mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu. Aya makuru yashikirijwe n'itororokanirizo ry'amakuru ry'Abongereza, Reuters.
Ibiranga abo barwanyi hamwe n’imvo yatumye babikora ntibiramenyekana.
Umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu yavuze ko abarwayi 38 bakekwa kuba baranduye Ebola hamwe n’abandi 12 batowe uwo mugera bari muri ico kigo igihe ico gitero caba. Yavuze ko bane muri abo banduye bahunze kandi baracaronderwa.
Nta n’umwe muri abo barwayi canke mu bakozi yakomeretse, nkuko vyashikirijwe n’uwo mushikiranganji.
Ishirahamwe ry’abafaransa ry’abaganga batagira imbibe, MSF, rirongoye ico kigo rifatanije n’ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu baraneguye ico gitero.
Ico gitero cabereye mu gisagara ca Butembo kigize kabiri muri iyi ndwi kibaye mu karere ko mu buseruko kavugwamwo Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5024393' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5024393.html' term='ebola'>
Umwana Niwe wa Gatatu Yanduye Ebola i Goma
Umwana w’umukobwa w’umwaka umwe yabaye uwa gatatu yasuzumwe ko yanduye Ebola mu gisagara ca Goma, muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, nkuko vyashikirijwe n’abategetsi mu karere kuri uyu wa gatatu. Amakuru ashikirizwa n’abategetsi avuga ko ari umwana w’umurwayi wa kabiri yapfuye mu ntango z’iyi ndwi.
Dogiteri Aruna Abedi ajejwe gutunganya ibikorwa vyo kurwanya Ebola mu ntara ya Kivu y’uburaruko, yabwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa, AFP ko gutanga incanco za Ebola vyatanguye i Goma kandi ko abashizwe ku rutonde rwa mbere ari ababanye n’uwo murwayi.
Ejo kuwa gatatu nyene, hatangajwe ko abantu 15 bashizwe ahabonyene mu mihana yo hafi y’intara ya Kivu yo mu bumanuko, bamaze gukekwa ko banduye uwo mugera.
Muri rusangi, abantu 1,803 baramaze gutakaza ubuzima bishwe na Ebola mu biharuro vyashikirijwe ejo kuwa gatatu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3242283' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3242283.html' term='ebola'>
Abanyafurika Ntibanezewe n'Imibereho Yabo
Abantu mu bihugu vyo muri Afurika bitari bike, harimwo Uburundi, Benin, u Rwanda, Gineya, Liberiya, Tanzaniya, Madagascar na Togo nibo bantu ba nyuma kw’isi batanezewe n’ukuntu babayehoku bwa raporo y’ukugene abantu banezewe n’ubuzima kw’isi yo mu mwaka w’2016.
Iyo raporo yaravye amafranga abantu baronka ku giti cabo ku mwaka, ikiringo bababo, ruswa, ukugene bafashwa n’ubwigenge bwabo bw’uguhitamwo ibintu mu buzima nk’ibimenyetso vy’ukunezerwa n’ukuntu babayeho.
Ikiza ca Ebola cihaye inkumbi mu gihugu ca Liberiya caragize uruhara mu gutuma ico gihugu kiza mu bihugu vya nyuma kw’isi ku kugene abantu batanezerewe n’ukuntu babayeho. Ruswa muri reta ibandanya kuba intambamyi kw’iterambere ry’akarere vka Afrika.
Danemark nico gihugu kiza ubwa mbere ku rugero abantu banezerewe n’ukugene babayeho. Ico gihugu gikwirikirwa n’Ubusuwisi.
Ibindi bihugu cumi biza imbere y’ibindi ku vyerekeye ukugene abanyagihugu banezewe n’ukugene babayeho na Iceland, Norvege, Finlande, Canada, Ubuholande, Nouvelle Zelande, Australiya n’Ubusweda.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4962083' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-ishobora-kuba-yageze-muri-kenya-/4962083.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Ishobora Kuba Yageze muri Kenya
Mu gihugu ca Kenya abaganga bariko barasuzuma umurwayi mu ntara yo mu burengero afise ibimenyetso vy’ingwara ya Ebola. Ayo makuru atangajwe inyuma muri Uganda ico kiza cahitanye babiri mu ndwi iheze.
Umurwayi ariko asuzumirwa muri Kenya ni umupfasoni. Amakuru atangwa n'ibitaro vyo mu karere ka Kericho avuga ko yashizwe mu kibanza ca wenyene.
Uyo mupfasoni yari yagendeye umutambukanyi wiwe ku rubibe igihugu ca Kenya gihana n’igihugu ca Uganda, ari kumwe n’abandi bantu batatu bo mu muryango wiwe. Mur’iki gihe nabo nyene bariko barakwirikiranirwa hafi, nk’uko amakuru atangwa n’ivyo bitaro, abivuga.
Ivyavuye mu bipimo vyakozwe kuri uyo mupfasoni bizomenyekana mu masaha ari hagati ya 12 na 24.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5163806' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5163806.html' term='ebola'>
Ubumwe bwa Bulayi Bwemeje Ikoreshwa ry'Urucanco rwa Ebola
Komisiyo y’umuryango w’ubumwe bwa Bulaya waremeje urucanco rwa Ebola muri iyi ndwi. Ni igikorwa OMS ivuga ko gihambaye mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu kw’isi kandi kizogira akamaro mu kurwanya ico kiza.
Bubaye ubwa mbere urucanco rwa Ebola ruhabwa uburenganzira bwo gukoreshwa ahantu hose kw’isi. Intambwe igira kabiri igiye gukurikira n'uko rushimwa na OMS, kandi vyitezwe mu minsi iri imbere.
Urucanco rwa Ebola rusanzwe ruriko rurageragezwa mu buseruko bwa Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Kongo, aho Ebola yagaragaye. Rwarakoreshejwe mu gukingira abantu barenga 250000 mu ntara za Ituri na Kivu y’uburaruko.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4661193' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4661193.html' term='ebola'>
Abasirikare 6 ba Monusco Barishwe muri RDC
Abasirikare indwi ba ONU bo mu nteko za Monusco barishwe mu bitero bakoranye n’abasirikare ba reta mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo. Batandatu mu bapfuye bamuka muri Malawi, uwundi umwe n’uwo muri Tanzaniya.
Abandi cumi muri abo basirikare babungabunga umutekano barakomeretse, uwundi umwe araburwa irengero, nkuko amakuru yashikirijwe n’umuvugizi w’umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU avuga. Abasirikare batari bake ba Kongo hamwe n’igitigiri kitazwi c’abarwanyi bariko bahangana na bo bavugwa ko bishwe canke bakomeretse muri iyo mirwano.
Izo ntambara zabereye hafi y’igisagara ca Beni, mu ntara ya Kivu y’uburaruko, ahavugwa ikiza ca Ebola. Itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa AFP ryashikirije ko abasirikare ba ONU hamwe n’aba Kongo batanye mu mitwe n’abarwanyi b’umuhari ADF mu birindiro vyawo vy’ahitwa Kididiwe.
ADF ni abarwanyi bava muri Uganda bamaze imyaka bakorera muri Kongo.
Umutegetsi wa ONU atashimye kumenyekana ntiyashatse kwemeza ko ari ONU yariko irahiga abo barwanyi, ariko bavuze ko uko gutana mu mitwe kwabaye mu misi ibiri irenga.
Inteko za ONU muri Kongo, MONUSCO, zifise abasirikare bashika ku bihumbi 18, bamaze imyaka irenga 20 muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo mu gihe ico gihugu casinzikajwe n’intambara hamwe n’ubwicanyi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2444554' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2444554.html' term='ebola'>
Igitigiri c'Abamaze Guhitanwa na Ebola, Ciyongeyeko Amajana Abiri, mu Misi Ine Yonyene.
Igitigiri c'abapfuye bahitanywe n'ikiza ca Ebola, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, kimaze gushika ku bantu ibihumbi bibiri n'amajana abiri na mirongo icenda na batandatu, ico gitigiri kikaba ciyongeyeko abantu amajana abiri mu misi ine yonyene.
Ibiharuro vya nyuma, vyashikirijwe n'ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi, O-M-S, ku musi wa kabiri, vyerekana kw'abantu bagera ku bihumbi bine n'amajana atatu, bafise Ebola batangajwe, mu bihugu bitanu, vyo muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Musi gatoyi y'igice c'abo bantu bose bafise Ebola, canke bahitanywe n'ico kiza, bava mu gihugu ca Liberia.
Raporo y'ishirahamwe O-M-S, ku gihugu ca Liberia, yasohotse ku musi wa mbere, yaragabishije kw'igitigiri c'abantu bashasha bafise Ebola, muri Liberia, kiriko ciyongera bikomeye cane, iyo raporo ikaba ivuga bishobora kwiterwa kw'abantu bashasha ibihumbi n'ibihumbi, bashobora kwandura umugera wa Ebola mu ndwi zitatu zimirije.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S, ritangaza ugukwiragira gukomeye kw'iyo ndwara, kubandanya kandi mu bihugu vya Guinee na Sierra Leone.
Muri ico gihe, Umunyamerika agira kane, yanduye umugera wa Ebola, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, yarashitse muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, kugira avurwe.
Uwo munyamerika atatangajwe izina, yajanywe n'indege, ku musi wa kabiri, mu gisagara ca Atlanta, mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, akaba yajanywe, mu bitaro vyo kw'ishule kaminuza ya Emory.
Mu kwezi guheze, ivyo bitaro vyarashoboye kuvura abagira neza babiri b'abanyamerika, bari banduye Ebola, muri Liberia barakira.
Uwundi munyamerika ariko avurwa indwara ya Ebola, mu ntara ya Nebraska.
Aba Docteurs batangaje, ku musi wa kabiri, kw'amagara yiwe ariko amera neza kurushiriza.
Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, zemeye ayandi mafranga, ku musi wa kabiri, ajejwe gufasha urugamba rw'ukurwanya indwara ya Ebola, muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2519874' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2519874.html' term='ebola'>
Liberia: Prezida Yarakuyeho Amategeko Adasanzwe, ku Vyerekeye Ebola
Prezida w’igihugu ca Liberia, Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yakuyeho amategeko yo mu bihe bidasanzwe, yashizeho kubera ikiza ca Ebola.
Yamara mw’ijambo yashikirije, ku musi wa kane, prezida Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yatangaje kw’urugamba rw’ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola rutarangiye, kw’ingingo zimwe zimwe zizogumaho.
Preizda wa Liberia, Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yatangaje kw’amasoko ashobora gususbira kwugurura, couvre-feu izoshika isaha zitandatu zo mw’ijoro, mu bice bitageramiwe na Ebola..
Prezida Sirleaf, yatangaje kw’ata bantu bashasha banduye Ebola, mu bice cumi ku bice cumi na bitanu vy’igihugu ca Liberia, kuva ku musi w’Imana.
Amategeko yo mu bihe bidasanzwe yarategetswe, mu gihugu ca Liberia, kuva mu kwezi kw’umunani.
Mu bihugu bitatu vyo muri Afrika, aho ikiza ca Ebola cashimikiye, Liberia nico gihugu casinzikajwe kurusha ivyo bindi bihugu bibiri, n'ukuvuga Guinee na Sierra Leone.
Yamara ibintu bimeze nabi muri Sierra Leone.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi ritangaza kw’ibitigiri vy’abantu banduye Ebola, vyiyongeye cane, muri Sierra Leone, mu gihe abantu bashasha 421, banduye umugera wa Ebola batangajwe, muri iyi ndwi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4401345' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4401345.html' term='ebola'>
Batatu Banduye Ebola mu mujyi wa Mbandaka muri Kongo
Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo yemeje ko abantu 3 bagaragayeho icyorezo cya Ebola. Minisitiri w'ubuzima Oly Ilunga yatangaje ku wa gatanu ko abanduye Ebola bakomoka mu mugi wa Mbandaka, utuwe n'abantu miliyoni 1.2. Mu minsi mike ishize na bwo habonetse undi urwaye.
Minisitiri Ilunga yagize ati "Mu bantu 43 basuzumwe, 17 basanzwe baranduye; hari ibyago by'uko abandi 21 na bo baba baranduye naho 5 bakekwa ko barwaye."
Ishami ry'umuyango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, ryanze kwemeza ko ari icyorezo gisaba ubutabazi mpuzamahanga bwihuta. OMS ariko ivuga ko ibyago by'ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara biri hejuru cyane.
OMS ivuga ko hari ibyago cyane by'uko iyi ndwara yagera no mu bihugu bituranyi 9 ariko ku rundi ruhande ivuga ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi mu karere bidakwiye guhagarikwa.
Byitezwe ko urukingo rushya ruzageragezwa mu ntangiriro z'icyumweru gitaha. Mu myaka mike ishize, urwo rukingo rwatanze umusaruro mu bihugu by'uburengerazuba bw'Afurika. Muri Kongo hamaze kugezwa inkingo ibihumbi 4 kandi hari izindi zikiri mu nzira.
Abashinzwe ubuzima bagowe no kubika izo nkingo ahantu hakonje; kubera igihugu ari kinini kandi kitagira ibikorwaremezo. Mu myaka isaga 40, Ebola igaragaye muri Kongo inshuro 9; ariko mu bihe bya mbere yagarukiraga mu bice by'icyaro. Icyorezo cya ebola cyadutse inshuro 2 mu murwa mukuru Kinshasa utuwe na miliyoni 10. Gusa icyo gihe cyahise gihagarikwa.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3264721' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3264721.html' term='ebola'>
Guinee: Abantu 800 Bakingiwe Ebola
Abantu bagera ku majana umunani mu gihugu ca Guinee barakingiwe Ebola mu ndwi iheze.
Muribo, harimwo abantu ijana na mirongo umunani na babiri babonwako bashobora kwandura iyo ndwara kurusha abandi kubera bashobora kuba begeye abantu banduye iyo ndwara.
Ivyo bitangazwa n’ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S.
Muri rusangi, ibiro vy’ishirahamwe O-M-S muri Guinee bimenyesha kw’abantu barenga igihumbi bashobora kuba baregeye abantu banduye Ebola bamenyekanye. Barakwirikiranywe n’abajejwe ubuvuzi.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S, ririko rishira mu ngiro umugambi w’ugucandaga abantu bose bagereye abantu bafise Ebola.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S ririko rifasha abaganga n’abakwirikirana indwara ya Ebola hamwe n’abajejwe gutanga inyigisho ku vyerekeye iyo ndwara muri Guinee.
Ugusubira kwiyadukiza kwa Ebola guherutse kuba muri Guinee kwibonejeke mu bantu umunani n’abantu indwi bahitanywe n’iyo ndwara kuva mu kwezi kwa kabiri.
Bwari ubwa mbere ivyo biba kuva ishirahamwe, O-M-S ritangaje ko Ebola itakirangwa muri Guinee kw’italiki 29 z’ukwezi kw’icumi na kabiri, mu mwaka w’i 2015.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4915550' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ikigo-kivura-ebola-muri-congo-casubiye-guterwa-/4915550.html' term='ebola'>
Ikigo Kivura Ebola muri Congo Casubiye Guterwa
Abategetsi muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo bavuga ko ikibanza abantu bavurirwamwo indwara ya Ebola mu buseruko bw’igihugu casubiye guterwa.
Umukuru w’igisagara ca Butembo, Sylvain Kanyamanda yatangaje uno musi ku wa mbere ko umwe mu bateye ico kibanza kiri ahitwa Katwa yishwe mw’ijoro ryashiriye uno musi ku wa mbere.
Abantu babiri bariko bavurwa Ebola nabo nyene barapfuye inyuma yuko abaforoma bose bahunze ico kibanza abarwaye Ebola bariko bavurirwamwo.
Umukuru w’igisagara ca Butembo, Sylvain Kanyamanda yasavye ababa muri ico gisagara gufasha abajejwe kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
N’irya mbere ikiza ca Ebola cibonekeje ubwa mbere mu kwezi kw’umunani muri Kongo ciyadukiza mu karere karimwo intambara.
Ukwinuba ivyerekeye Ebola, uruhagarara n’ubwicanyi mu karere ko mu buseruko bwa Kongo vyarageramiye utwigoro tw’uguhagarika iyo ndwara.
Ishirahamwe ryitaho amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS ryagabishije mu ndwi iheze ko Ebola ishobora gutandukira izindi ntara muri Kongo niyo uruhagara n’ibwicanyi vyobandanya.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2490507' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2490507.html' term='ebola'>
O-M-S Ivuga ko Ubu nta Ebola Ihari muri Nigeria
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, ryatangaje kw’ata Ebola ikiri, mu gihugu ca Nigeria, inyuma y’imisi mirongo ine n’ibiri irangiye ata bandi bantu bashasha banduye iyo ndwara, batangajwe.
Uwuserukira ishirahamwe O-M-S, Rui Gam,a yatangaje, ku musi wa mbere kw’iyo ari inkuru ikomeye cane.
Prezida w’igihugu ca Nigeria, Goodluck Jonathan, yasohoye itangazo, ku musi wa mbere, rihayagiza Abanya Nigeria bakoze kugira batume Ebola idakwiragira.
Yongeye ategeka kw’ingingo zose z’ukurwanya Ebola, muri Nigeria zigumaho, harimwo gusuzuma abantu binjira mu gihugu.
Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu, mu gihugu ca Nigeria, Onyebuchi Chukwu, yavuze kw’izo ntambwe zashitsweko, kubera ubuyobozi bukomeye, n’ugukorera hamwe.
Hari abantu mirongo ibiri bari bafise Ebola, muri Nigeria, umunani muribo bakaba barahitanywe n’iyo ndwara. Ebola imaze guhitana abantu barenga ibihumbi bine n’amajana atanu, mu karere ko muri Afrika, yo mu burengero.
Ubushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire bwa Amerika bwatangaje, ku musi wa mbere, ko bufise abantu amajana atandatu na cumi n’indwi, ku murwa mukuru wa Liberia, Monrovia, na Dakar, muri Senegal, ubwo bushikiranganji bufise imigambi y’ukurungika abandi bantu mirongo umunani, ku musi wa gatatu, gufasha kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4412107' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4412107.html' term='ebola'>
Uwundi Muntu Yishwe na Ebola muri RDC
Uwundi umuntu yatangajwe ko yishwe na Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, bica bishikana ku gitigiri c'abantu 12, nkuko bishikirizwa n’ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu.
Uwo muntu yapfiriye mu karere ka Iboko, mu buraruko bushira uburengero bw’intara ya Equateur.
Umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu avuga ko hari abandi bane bashasha bakekwa kuba barafashwe muri iyo ntara.
Gushika ubu Reta yemeza ko abantu 35 bafashwe n’iyo ndwara.
Gucandaga gutangurana no kuri uyu wa mbere mu bice vya Bikoro na Iboko mu ntara ya Equateur, mu gihe mu ntara ya Mbandaka baza baratanguye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2468337' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2468337.html' term='ebola'>
Umuntu Wa Mbere Asuzumwe Ebola Muri Amerika
Umukuru w’ibiro bijejwe gukingira ingwara, Muganga Torn Frieden, ejo ku musi wa kabiri, yaremeje kw’iyo ngwara yabonete ku mugabo yayanduriye mu gihugu ca Liberia.
Uyo mugabo yatanguye kugira ibimenyetso vy’iyo ngwara kuva aho ashikiye mu gisagara ca Dallas , mu ntara ya Texas kw’igenekerezo rya 20 ry’ukwezi kw’icenda.
Muganga Frieden yavuze kw’uyo murwayi yaciye yinjizwa mu bitaro ku musi wa mungu, kandi aca ashirwa mu kibanza ca wenyene.
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu, bariko baragerageza kuraba abantu bashobora kuba baregereye uyo mugabo. Abo nabo ngo bashobora kuba ar’abagenzi biwe hamwe n’umuryango wiwe.
Abategetsi bariko barakwirikirana uyo mugabo, bavuga kandi kw’ata muntu n’umwe mu bantu bari mu ndege imwe n’uyo mugabo, arashobora kuba yaranduye.
Bavuga kandi ko bazokora ibishobotse vyose kugira ngo bahagarike iyo ngwara.
Naho hari hamaze kuboneka abanyamerika bakora umwuga w’abavuzi banyarukanwa muri Amerika banduye ingwara ya Ebola, uyo mugabo wo mu ntara ya Texas, abaye uwa mbere asuzumiwe iyo ngwara muri Amerika.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4398105' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-igeze-mu-gisagara-ca-mbandaka-muri-kongo-/4398105.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yatandukiriye Igisagara ca Mbandaka muri Kongo
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryitaho amagara y'abantu kw'isi, OMS, ritangaza ko ingwara ya Ebola yatandukiriye igisagara ca Mbandaka inyuma yaho ihitanye abagera kuri 17 muri 27 bagaragaje ibimenyesto vyayo mu karere ka Bikoro kari mu ntara ya Equateur haraheze iminsi.
OMS yavuze ko ifise amakenga yuko Ebola ishobora kwunyuka gusumba muri Kongo.
Igisagara ca Mbandaka catandukiriwe na Ebola kiri mu ntara ya Equateur iherereye mu buraruko bushira uburengero bwa Kongo, kibamwo abantu barenga umuriyoni umwe.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1264562' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/a-18-2006-03-29-voa3-93017844/1264562.html' term='ebola'>
Umuryango w'Abibumbye Uratabariza RDC
Umuryango w’Abibumbye uvuga ko nta handi ku isi abantu bapfa cyangwa bagirirwa nabi buri munsi nko muri Repuburika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo.
Ushinzwe ibikorwa by’ubutabazi by’uwo muryango muri Congo, Ross Mountain, yinubira ko ubwo bubabare bwose butabera ahagaragara, imbere ya cameras z’abanyamakuru, ngo bumenyekane ku isi yose.
Ross Mountain avuga ko muri Congo muri rusange hapfa abantu 1200 bose buri munsi bazize indwara z’amoko yose, harimo za malaria, mugiga, na ebola. Ubu noneho hari no kuvugwa indwara y’ibicurane bituruka ku biguruka.
Ross Mountain yifuza ko uko isi yahagurukiye gutangaza ibyo bicurane by’ibisiga ari na ko yahagurukira kuvuga ku Banyecongo barimo kuzira izindi ndwara zitakivugwa cyane.
Ross Mountain yinubira ko Abanyecongo barimo kuzira indwara zishobora kwirindwa. Ubu ngo barazira indyo mbi, amazi mabi, umwanda, no kutagira kirengera kubera amahanga yabatereranye.
Kugeza ubu Umuryango w’Abibumbye ngo umaze kwemererwa gusa munsi ya kimwe cya gatatu cy’a miriyoni 682 z’amadolari ukeneye muri uyu mwaka kugira ngo ukomeze ibikorwa by’ubutabazi muri Congo. Ayo mafaranga ngo akenewe kugira ngo barokore abantu, banarwane ku batishoboye bibasirwa, bagakorerwa ibya mfura mbi n’andi mabi menshi.
Ross Mountain ushinzwe ibikorwa by’ubutabazi by’Umuryango w’Abibumbye muri Congo avuga ko ari ngombwa kwita by’umwihariko kuri ibyo bibazo byose Congo ifite ubu kubera amatora rusange yegereje. Avuga ko hazaba ingaruka zikomeye niba nta ngamba zifashwe kugira ngo umutuzo wuzuye ugaruke muri Congo, na guverinoma izatorwa ihabwe inkunga ikeneye kugira ngo ishobore gukomeza gukora.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5005216' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5005216.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola muri Kongo Ntiyobuza Uruja n'Uruza n'Ibihugu Bibanyi
Ikiza ca Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gikwiye kugirwa umwitwarariko w’amagara y’abantu wihutirwa n’amakungu, nkuko bishikirizwa n’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS.
OMS yavuze ko kubona hari umurwayi yagaragaye mu gisagara ca Goma, kimwe mu bisagara binini muri Kongo, ari yo mvo itumye bashikiriza ivyo. OMS ivuga kandi ko umuvuduko w’abandura uteye ubwoba, aho abantu bari hagati ya 10 na 15 bandura buri munsi kandi 1,676 bamaze gupfa kuva Ebola itanguye kwibonekeza mur’ico gihugu.
Mu gihe igisagara ca Goma gihana urubibe n’u Rwanda kandi kirimwo ikibuga c’indege, OMS isaba ibihugu bibanyi kutabuza ingenzi gufata ingendo.
Umuyobozi wa OMS Dr. Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus asaba amakungu guhaguruka akarwanya ico kiza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3177042' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3177042.html' term='ebola'>
Abantu 55 muri Sierra Leone nta Ebola Bafise
Igihugu ca Sierra Leone carekuye ejo ku musi wa gatatu abantu 55 bari bakumiwe inyuma yuko vyibonekeje ko ata Ebola bafise. Bari bakumiwe mu kwezi guheze inyuma yuko abantu babiri bemejwe ko bafise Ebola.
Sidi Yahya Tunis, umuvugizi w’ibiro bijejwe ibikorwa vyihutirwa ku bijanye n’amagara y’abantu mu bushikiranganji bujejwe amagara y’abantu muri Sierra Leone, yatangaje kw’abarekuwe vyibinekeje ko ata Ebola bafise.
Yatangaje kw’abanya Sierra Leone bomenya ko uko biri kwose igihugu muri iki gihe gifise uburyo bw’ugutuma abantu bashasha basanganywe umugera wa Ebola badashobora kuwukwiragiza.
Sidi Yahya Tunis yatangaje kw’abo bantu 55 bari bakumiwe mu kiringo c’imisi mirongo ibiri n’umwe, bakaba barangije ikiringo c’imisi 21 umugera wa Ebola umara mu mubiri imbere yuko ibimenyetso vyigaragaza hanze.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2478293' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2478293.html' term='ebola'>
ONU Irasaba Abatuye Isi Gushyira Ingufu mu Kurwanya Ebola
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU, Ban Ki-moon avuga ko ibihugu byo ku isi bikwiye kwongera ingufu mu guhangana n’icyorezo cya Ebola mu Burengerazuba bwa Afrika.
Ibyo yabivugiye kuri uyu wa kane, inaha I Washington, mu nama ya Banki y’isi yose, ku ndwara ya ebola, yarimo abategetsi bo mu nzego zo hejuru n’abaprezida w’ibihugu byazahajwe cyane n’iyo ndwara, Guinee, Liberia, na Sierra Leone. Bamwe bari mu nama hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa video.
Bwana Ban yavuze ko inkunga yakogerwa ikwiye kubamo za labolatoire zimukanwa, imodoka, za kajugujugu, imyambaro yo kwirinda Ebola, habamo kandi guhugura abakozi bo mu buvuzi, no kwongera ubushobozi bwo kujyana abantu aho bagomba kuvurirwa.
Prezida wa banki y’isi yose, Jim Yong Kim, yabwiye abari mu nama ko icyorezo cya Ebola kiramutse kitabashije guhagarikwa vuba na bwangu, Afrika yazaba itorohewe mu bihe biri imbere.
Yavuze ko hakenewe cyane abantu bahuguwe mu by’ubuzima, mu bihugu birimo indwara ya Ebola. Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima rivuga ko, Ebola yahitanye abakozi bo mu buvuzi barenga 230 mu burengerazuba bwa Afrika, uyu mwaka.
Kim yavuze ko kuri uyu wa kane, inama iri buganire ku bikorwa bifatika byakorwa mu gufasha ibihugu byibasiwe na Ebola kwihutisha urugamba rwo kurwanya icyo cyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka z’igihe kirekire mu byerekeye ubukungu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2570803' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2570803.html' term='ebola'>
ONU Irakurikirira Hafi Ikibazo cya Ebola muri Afurika
Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, rivuga ko umubare w’abantu bamaze guhitanwa na Ebola, wiyongerye. Bamaze kurenga ibihumbi 7,500, kandi ko abanduye Ebola babarirwa hafi mu bihumbi 20.
Imibare iheruka, yatangajwe ejo kuwa mbere, igaragaza ko umubare w’abanduye Ebola muri Liberia na Guinea wagabanutse, mu gihe muri Sierra Leone uwo mubare wazamutse. Ibyo bihugu uko ari bitatu bibarwamo impfu hafi ya zose, z’abahitanywe na Ebola.
Mu bindi bihugu nta cyahindutse, muri Mali havugwa batandatu, muri Nigeria iyo ndwara yahitanye abantu umunani, n’umwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kuwa mbere kandi, umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU, Ban Ki-moon, yavuze ko umuryango mpuzamahanga, ukwiye kurushaho kwitegera neza icyorezo gishobora kuzongera kwaduka ku isi, aho yavuze ko, ari ikigeragezo gishoboka.
Bwana Ban aherutse mu ruzinduko mu bihugu byo mu Burengerazuba bwa Afrika, byibasiwe na Ebola. Yavuze ko isi igomba gufatira amasomo kuri iki cyorezo, avuga ko gisaba gukaza inzego z’ubuzi bw’abaturage.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2442683' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2442683.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola, Ikibazo Kihutirwa Ku Mutekano Bwite wa USA
Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika ikwiye kugira icyorezo cya Ebola ikibazo kihutirwa ku mutekano bwite wayo.
Ni ko President Obama yatangaje mu kiganiro yahaye television NBC. Muri urwo rwego, yasobanuye ko ingabo ze zigiye gufasha ibihugu byayogojwe na Ebola muri Afrika y’uburengerazuba mu birebana n’ibikoresho, gushyira abarwayi mu kato, n’umutekano w’abaganga.
President Obama aragira, ati: “Tutabikoze aka kanya, wasanga Ebola ikomeje kwiyongera ndetse ikarenga n’Afrika y’uburengerazuba igwakwira isi.”
Umukuru wa Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika asaba kandi amahanga yose guhagurukira icyorezo cya Ebola, kimaze guhitana abantu barenga ibihumbi bibili muri Guinea, Liberia, Sierra-Leone, na Nigeria.
Naho Addis-Abeba, umuyobozi w’inama y’ubutegetsi y’Afrika yunze ubumwe, Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma, yakoresheje inama yihutirwa y’abahagarariye ibihugu byabo muri uwo muryango kugirango bafate ibyemezo byo gukumira Ebola, nko gufunga imipaka y’ibihugu birimo Ebola, no guhagarika indege zijya cyangwa zituruka muri ibyo bihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4389802' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/oms-ebola-ishobora-kunyuka-muri-kongo-/4389802.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola Ishobora Kunyuka muri Kongo
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryitaho amagara y'abantu kw'isi, OMS, ryatangaje ko indwara ya Ebola ishobora guhitana abatari bake muri Kongo.
OMS isigura ko mu kiringo c'indwi imwe, ku bantu 27 bagaragaje ibimenyesto vy'iyo ndwara, 17 bo mu karere ka Bikoro kari mu ntara ya Equateur bitavye Imana.
Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Kongo yahamagariye OMS kwihutira gukorana n'amashirahamwe ariko arafasha gutorera inyishu ico kibazo amazi atararenga inkombe.
OMS imenyesha ko ikiza ca Ebola kimaze gutera muri Kongo incuro icenda kuva mu 1976.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4959771' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/oms-yoba-igiye-kwemeza-ebola-nk-ikiza-gihangayikishije-isi-/4959771.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Yoba Igiye Kwemeza Ebola nk'Ikiza Gihangayikishije Isi?
Abahinga batangaza ko ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, ryotegerezwa kandi ko rishobora gutangaza ko ikiza ca Ebola ari ikibazo cihutirwa kw’isi.
Ni inyuma yuko ico kiza gitandukiye igihugu ca Uganda kivuye muri Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo. Umurwi w’abahinga bajejwe guha impanuro ishirahamwe OMS babonanye uno musi ku wa gatanu.
Ikiza ca Ebola muri Kongo nico kiza ca kabiri ciyadukije kuva ico kiza cadutse ubwa mbere mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero hagati y’umwaka w’i 2014 n’umwaka w’2016.
Ishirahamwe OMS ryatangaje ku musi wa kane ko abantu babiri bapfuye mu gihugu ca Uganda bahitanywe na Ebola inyuma yuko bashitse muri Uganda bavuye muri Kongo bafise iyo ndwara.
Umurwi w’abahinga mu vyerekeye amagara y’abantu bigenga 13 bari muri komite ijejwe ibikorwa vyihutirwa y’ishirahamwe OMS babonanye uno musi ku wa gatanu kugira bihweze ivyemezo vya nyuma hamwe nuko niba ikiza ca Ebola ari ikibazo cihutirwa cerekeye amagara y’abantu giteye impungenge amakungu.
Ingingo nkiyo yotuma ingingo zikomeye zifatwa, n’amafaranga n’uburyo biboneka mu rugamba rw’ukurwanya ico kiza. Uwo murwi w’abahinga bazoshikiriza ivyiyumviro vyabo umuyobozi mukuru w’ishirahamwe OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus azofata ingingo ya nyuma.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2419485' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2419485.html' term='ebola'>
Umutegetsi Ukurikirana Ebola muri O-N-U, Azogenderera Afrika
Umutegetsi mukuru w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu, O-N-U, akwirikirana ikiza ca Ebola, yatangaje ko azoja mu karere ka Afrika, mu mpera z’iyi ndwi.
Docteur, David Nabarro, yatangaje, ku musi wa kabiri, ari i New York, ko yabonanye n’umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe O-N-U, Ban Ki-moon, akaba yagiye i Washington, mu nama, uno musi ku wa gatatu, n’abategetsi bo mu biro bijejwe kurwanya indwara, hamwe n’abategetsi b’ibanki y’isi yose.
Docteur Nabarro, yatangaje kw’azogirisha inama i Dakar, ku musi wa kane, mu nyuma yaho aje mu bihugu vya Liberia, Sierra Leone na Guinee. Amenyesha kw’ashobora kuja, mu gihugu ca Nigeria.
Docteur Nabarro, yatangaje kw’igikorwa nyamukuru c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu O-N-U, ari uguhagarika ikwiragira ry’umugera wa Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4622876' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4622876.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Abarwanyi ba ADF Barishe Abantu 15 muri Beni
Abarwanyi b’umuhari witwaje ibirwanisho ADF warishe abanyagihugu 15 bongera banyuruza abana barenga cumi mu gitero cabereye mu gice co hagati muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gihitiyemwo ikiza ca Ebola. Ivyo vyashikirijwe n’igisirikare ku musi w’Imana.
Ico gitero cabaye mu gihe ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS ryari rikiri mu bikorwa vyo kurwanya Ebola.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, aranegura ico gitero mu gihe umutegetsi wa OMS muri iyo ntara avuga ko batazi ikiringo ibikorwa barimwo bizorangirira.
Umuhari w’abarwanya ubutegetsi bwa Reta ya Uganda bo mu murwi, “Allied Democratic Forces”, ADF mu mpfunyapfunyo warateye ibirindiro vy’abasirikare ba Kongo no mu micungararo y’intara ya Beni ku musi ya gatandatu n’uwa Mungu, nkuko vyashikirijwe na Kapitene Mak Hazukay Mongha wo mu nteko za MONUSCO.
Ico gitero co mw’ijoro cabaye inyuma y’aho abakozi babiri bo mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu hamwe n’abasirikare b’igihugu bishwe n’uwundi muhari w’aba Mai Mai witwaje ibirwanisho, ubwa mbere abo bakozi bishwe muri iki gihe co kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5067280' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5067280.html' term='ebola'>
Guterres Asaba Imfashanyo Zikwiye zo Kurwanya Ebola
Umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU Antonio Guterres asaba abatanga amafaranga gushitsa ivyo basezeranye kugira ikiza ca Ebola kirwanywe. Yabishikirije mu rugendo rw’imisi itatu muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gushigikira ibikorwa vyo kurwanya ico kiza.
Guterres yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru i Kinshasa ejo kuwa mbere ko ONU imaze kuronswa ibice 15 kw’ijana gusa vy’amafaranga akenewe yo kurwanya Ebola mu gice gisigaye c’umwaka. Yabishikirije imbere yo kubonana na perezida Felix Tshisekedi.
Uwo mukuru wa ONU ku musi w’Imana yaragendeye kandi ikigo categekanirijwe kuvura abanduye Ebola mu buseruko bw’igisagara ca Beni.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5039854' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5039854.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yoba Igiye Kuronka Umuti?
Imiti ibiri kuri ine iriko irageragezwa kugira ivure Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo yerekanye ko ikiza kandi ko ari yo ikwiye guhabwa abarwayi.
Iyo miti yiswe REGN-EB3 na mAb-114, inyuma yo kugeragezwa yatumye abahinga bayigira iya mbere mu gukoresha ku barwayi muri Kongo, aho Ebola imaze guhitana ubuzima bw’abarenga 1800 ku mwaka.
Mu bantu bativuza barwaye Ebola, batatu kuri bane barapfa, nkuko bishikirizwa na dogiteri Michael Ryan yo mw’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS.
Kuvura Ebola cabaye ikibazo ku bategetsi ba Kongo bivanye n’intambara hagati y’abenegihugu, kuko benshi bahitamwo kuguma mu mihana yabo iyo barwaye, bigatuma uyo mugera urandarara.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2465748' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2465748.html' term='ebola'>
Umuganga W’Umunyamerika Yanduye Ebola Muri Sierra Leone Yashitse Muri Amerika
Uyo muganga yashikanywe ku kibanza c’indege co mu ntara ya MaryLand ejo ku musi wa mungu, aho yavuye mu ndege atambuka, yambaye impuzu zera zikingira iyo ngwara.
Umuganga mukuru akwirikirana ingwara zandukira akorera ibiro vya reta zunze ubumwe bijejwe kwitaho amagara y’abanatu biri hafi y’igisagara ca Washington, ntaco yashatse kuvuga cerekeye uyo mugwayi, yamara yavuze ko muri rusangi, umuntu yegereye abagwaye ingwara ya Ebola, adaca yandukirwa.
Mw’itangazo ryasohowe ejo ku musi wa gatandatu, ivyo biro vyavuze kw’uyo murwayi azoca yinjizwa mu bitaro kugira asuzumwe, kandi akwirikiranwe.
Ivyo biro vyavuze kandi kw’uyo muganga yanduye ingwara ya Ebola, azoshirwa mu kibanza ca wenyene mu buryo bwitondewe cane.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4529155' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4529155.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Isaba Ko Intambara Ihagara Muri Kivu Ya Ruguru
Umukuru w’ibiro vy’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU bijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus avuga ko intambara iri mu buraruko bwa Kivu ituma ikiza c’ingwara ya Ebola gikomera kurusha icibonekeje mu myaka ya 2014 na 2015 mu burengero bwa Afrika. Abantu barenga ibihumbi cumi na kimwe bicwa n’iyo ngwara, gushika igihe ihagarikiwe mu mwaka wi 2016.
Tedros arangirije urugendo rwiwe mu karere ka Benin a Mangina mubuseruko bwa Kongo aho Ebola iriko itikiza inganda, avuga ko yari afise amakenga imbere yo gufata urugendo, ariko ko nyuma yaho amakenga yiwe yiyongereye kurusha aho yiboneye n’amaso yiwe ingaruka z’iyo ntambara iriko ibera mu kare Kivu y’uburaruko.
Amenyesha ko imigwi ishika ijana y’abitwaje ibigwanisho iriko ikorera muri ako karere. Avuga kandi ko hamaze kuba ubwicanyi ku ncuro 120, aho abantu bicwa, bakanyuruzwa, bagafatwa kunguvu canke bagakoregwa ayandi mabi.
Tedros ahamagarira impande zose z’abariko baragwana guhagarika intambara, akagabisha kw’iyo ngwara ya Ebola yandukira cane uwariwe wese.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2954336' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2954336.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ni Ngombwa Gukomeza Kwirinda Ebola
OMS, ibiro vy’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU bijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, bimenyesha ko ibikogwa vyo kugwanya ikiza ca Ebola bigenda bitera intambwe. Nyamara OMS iragabisha kw’ico kiza kitarahera neza na neza, kandi kw’ibihugu iyo ngwara yandukiyemwo abantu ku bwinshi bitegerezwa kuguma birikanuye.
OMS imenyesha ko ahanini amakuru yerekeye ukwo ibikogwa vyo kugwanya iyo ngwara biriko biragenda aremesha. Kuva mu kwezi kw’indwi, ibitigiri vy’abantu banduye iyo ngwara ntibagera kuri cumi. Muribo, bane bava mu gihugu ca Sierra Leone mu kigwati ca Kambia, mu ndwi iheze naho uwindi umwe wenyene niwe yanduye iyo ngwara mu gihugu ca Gineya.
Icegera c’umuyobozi w’ibiro vya OMS Bruce Aylward, avuga ko muri Gineya ariho ibintu vyifashe neza kurusha. Avuga ko indwi iraheze ata muntu yanduye iyo ngwara. Ati iyo niyo misi myinshi yambere irenze ata muntu yandiye Ebola, kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu kw’umwaka uheze. Ati ivyo rero vyerekana kw’ibikoga vyo kugwanya iyo ngwara vyateye intambwe zidasanzwe.
Dr. Ayland avuga ko Afrika y’uburengero yageze ku ntambwe zitatu zikomeye mundwi iheze. Amenyesha kw’igihugu ca Liberia ca renze imisi 42 ata muntu yanduye iyo ngwara, ivyo bigasigura ko bahagaritse iyo ngwara, kandi kw’ico gihugu cavuye kurutonde rw’ibihugu bifise Ebola incuro igira kabiri. Ati umugwa mukuru wa Sierra Leone nawo, umaze imisi 21 ata muntu yanduyeyo iyo ngwara. Itambwe ya gatatu ikomeye, ikaba ari ukw igihugu ca Guinea cose kimaze indwi ata muntu n’umwe ayanduye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4402139' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4402139.html' term='ebola'>
Kongo: Ebola Imaze Guhitana Abantu 26
Minisitiri w’ubuzima muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo yatangaje ko undi muntu umwe yishwe na Ebola uyu munsi ku cyumweru.
Byatumye umubare w’abazize iyo ndwara ugera kuri 26 kuva icyo cyorezo cyadutse mu ntara ya Equateur mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw’igihugu.
Itangazo rya minisitiri riheruka ryemeza, abandi bantu bane babonetseho virusi ya Ebola muri Kongo.
Kuva iki cyorezo gitangiye kuvugwa, abantu 46 bose hamwe banduye indwara itera umuriro no kuvirirana. Makumyabiri n’umwe byemejwe ko barwaye Ebola. Abandi makumyabiri n’umwe babashobora kuba bayirwaye. Naho bane birakekwa cyane ko baba barwaye iyo ndwara ya Ebola.
Perezida Joseph Kabila n’abaminisitiri be bafashe icyemezo ejo kuwa gatandatu cyo kwongera amafaranga mu kigega cyagenewe gufasha kurwanya Ebola byihutirwa. Ayo mafaranga amaze kurenga miliyoni enye z’amadolari
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2489253' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2489253.html' term='ebola'>
Oxfam:Ebola Ishobora Kuba Arico Kiza Gikomeye Cane mu Bihe vya None.
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakunguriujejwe gutabara, Oxfam ryasavye abashikiranganji bajejwe imigendenire b'ishirahamwe ry'ibihugu vy'i Bulaya,, gukora kurushiriza, ku vyerekeye kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
Umuyobozi mukuru w’ishirahamwe Oxfam, Mark Goldring, yasavye irungikwa ry’izindi nteko, uburyo n’abaganga, muri Sierra Leone, Guinee na Liberia, ibihugu bisinzikanjwe kurusha ibindi n’ikiza ca Ebola.Goldring yatangaje kw’ibihugu bitazokwiyemeza ku vyerekeye kurwanya Ebola, bishobora gutuma ubuzuma bw’abantu batari bake bugeramirwa.
Prezida w’igihugu ca Liberia, Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yatangaje, ku musi w’Imana kw’amakungu afise uruhara, mu rugamba rw’ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola. Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yatangaje kw’ari igikorwa c’abantu bose kw’isi, kurungika ubutumwa ko batazoreka abantu imiliyoni n’imiliyoni ngo birwaneko, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, rimenyesha kw’abantu barenga ibihumbi bine n’amajana atanu bapfuye, bahitanywe na Ebola, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Abahinga bajejwe amagara y’abantu bavuga kw’abandi bantu ibihumbi n’ibihumbi bazohitanwa n’iyo ndwara, imbere yuko uyu mwaka urangira.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4498760' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4498760.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yasezerewe muri RDC
Igihugu ca Republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo catangaje ko ikiza ca Ebola carangiye, gishimira abategetsi muvy’amagara y’abantu hamwe n’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS, kuba baranyarutse kurwanya ico kiza.
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom arashimira reta ya Kongo kuba yarakerebutse mu guhangana n’ico kiza, no mu gusaba imfashanyo mu maguru masha, hamwe no gutanga amakuru ku banyagihugu ibintu bitarayangara.
Ico kiza ca Ebola gihitiye catanguye kandi kwibonekeza mur'ico gihugu mu kwezi kwa kane, mu mihana yo mu buraruko bushira uburengero bwa Kongo, mu nyuma gitandukira igisagara ca Mbandaka.
Abantu 33 nibo cahitanye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2485859' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2485859.html' term='ebola'>
Amerika n'Uburayi Byahagurukiye Hamwe mu Kurwanya Ebola
Abaministiri b’ubuzima bo mu bihugu byo ku mugabane w’Uburayi bateraniye I Bruseli mu gihugu cy’Ububiligi mu nama ku kibazo cy’icyorezo cya Ebola no kwigira hamwe uburyo batangira gupima abagenzi ku mipaka n’ibibuga by’indege.
Iyi nama iteranye mu gihe Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika zamaze gutangiza gahunda yo gupima abagenzi bose baturuka mu bihugu bya Liberia, Sierra Leone na Guinea. Usibye gupimwa, abagenzi bazajya banabazwa niba barigeze bahura n’umurwayi wa Ebola.
Iyo gahunda yatangijwe ku bibuga bitanu byakira nibura 90 ku ijana ry’abagenzi bose binjira mu gihugu cy’Amerika bavuye mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika.
Hagati aho inteko ishinga amategeko y'Amerika yatumije abahanga mu by’ubuvuzi ngo bagezweho ingamba zirimo gufatwa kugira ngo icyo cyorezo kidakwirakwira muri Amerika.
Ibi bibaye mu gihe inzego zishinzwe ubuzima zikomeje guperereza uburyo abaforomokazi bavuraga umunyaliberiya muri leta ya Texas banduye ebola kandi barakoresheje uburyo bwose bwo kwirinda burimo kwambara imyenda yabugenewe n’ibikoresho bibabuza kwandura.
Kuri uyu wa gatatu Prezida Barack Obama yasubitse ingendo yagombaga gukorera mu gihugu, ahamagaza inama y’abaministiri yigaga ku kibazo cya Ebola.
Ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS, ryatangaje ko iki cyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika. Mu minsi 10 gusa abantu 425 bamaze kwandura muri Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5033763' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5033763.html' term='ebola'>
RDC-Ebola: Abagirizwa Urupfu rwa Dogiteri Mouzoko Bafashwe
Abaganga batatu b’abakongomani bagirizwa iyicwa ry’umuganga mugenzi wabo yakorera ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS yari mu bafasha kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo bafunzwe, nkuko vyashikirijwe n’umucamanza wa sentare ya gisirikare kuri uyu wa gatatu.
Dogiteri yamuka muri Kameruni, Richard Valery Mouzoko Kiboung, yishwe arashwe itariki 19 z’ukwezi kwa kane mu gitero ku bitaro vyo mu gisagara ca Butembo mu buseruko bwa Kongo.
Abo baganga bose uko ari batatu bagirizwa kuba batunganije inama kugira babone ingene bica Mouzoko.
OMS ivuga ko Mouzoko yari yarungitswe mu murwi w’abaganga bagiye gufasha kurwanya Ebola yateye mu kwezi kw’umunani umwaka uheze muri Kivu y’uburaruko.
Inyuma y’iyicwa rya Mouzoko mu kwezi kwa kane, umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yavuze ko batazotekerwa n’ubwoba, bazobandanya igikorwa cabo gushika ku musozo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4512673' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4512673.html' term='ebola'>
Ikindi Cyorezo cya Ebola muri Kongo
OMS imaze kwemeza bidakuka abantu bane banduye Ebola i Mangina, mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo. Abandi bantu babiri barakurikiranirwa hafi, mu gihe 20 bitabye Imana ariko OMS ntiyemeza ko bose bazize Ebola.
OMS yohereje imiti n’abaganga gutera inkunga mu rugamba rwo kurwanya iki cyorezo. Ariko ntibizoroha kubera ibibazo by’umutekano, nk’uko umuyobozi w’ibikorwa byihutirwa cyane muri OMS, Peter Salama, yabibwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika.
Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo ikunze kwibasirwa na Ebola. Iki cyorezo ni icya cumi kuva mu 1976
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2636550' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2636550.html' term='ebola'>
Abantu barenga 9,000 Bamaze Kwandura Ebola
Umubare w’abantu bahitanywe n’indwara ya Ebola, wamaze kugera ku 9,152. Ubwiyongere buri hejuru, nyuma y’ibyumweru byari bishize icyo cyorezo gisa n’icyacitse intege.
Amakuru atangazwa n’ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, yerekana ko, hari abantu bagera ku 150 bapfuye, kuva mu minsi itatu ishize, ubwo iryo shami rya ONU ryatangaje imibare iheruka.
OMS yavuze ko umubare w’abantu banduye bwa mbere, wiyongereyeho 303, 136 babarurwa muri Liberiya, 113 muri Sierra Leone, na 54 muri Gineya.
Intumwa yihariye ya ONU ku ndwara ya Ebola, Docteur, David Nabarro, yabwiye abanyamakuru, ari i Geneve, mu Busuwisi ko imibare mishya yerekana ko icyo cyorezo kitarabasha guhagarikwa. Yavuze ko intego ari ukugabanya umubare w’abandura kugeza ugeze kuri zeru.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4387592' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4387592.html' term='ebola'>
Abaganga ba OMS Barashitse muri RDC Guhangana na Ebola
Umurwi w’abaganga b’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS kuri uyu wa gatatu niho bashika muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo guhangana n’umugera wa Ebola, mugihe abategetsi ba Reta mu karere bariko barashiraho ibikenewe kugira barwanye ico kiza.
OMS yatangaje ku musi wa kabiri ko igihugu ca Kongo congeye guterwa na Ebola mu karere ka Bikoro mu ntara ya Equateur, itangaza kandi ko yasohoye umuliyoni umwe w’Amadolari mu mafaranga yayo yogufasha vyihuta kugira ifashe guhangana na Ebola. Ivyo OMS yabishikirije hamaze gupfa abantu 17, abategetsi mu gisata c’ubuganga bemeza ko abashika kuri babiri mur’abo bari banduye Ebola.
Umushikiranganji wa Nijeriya ajejwe amagara y’abantu, Isaac Adewole yavuze ejo kuwa gatatu ko igihugu ciwe catanguye gusuzuma ingenzi ziva muri RDC zinjira mu gihugu kandi ko biteguye kurungika umurwi w’abaganga gufasha muri Kongo kurwanya ico kiza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3071757' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3071757.html' term='ebola'>
Liberia: Icyorezo cya Ebola Cyongeye Kugaragara
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima bavuga ko umwana yahitanywe na Ebola, ko ari uwa mbere uhitanywe n’iyo ndwara mu mezi hafi atandatu.
Umwana w’imyaka 15 y’amavuko wo mu burasirazuba bw’umurwa mukuru , Monrovia, yasuzumwe iyo ndwara mu cyumweru gishize. Ise n’umuvandimwe we nabo babasanganye Virusi ya Ebola. Bajyanywe kuvurirwa mu kigo kiri mu nkengero za Monronvia hamwe n’abandi bantu batatu bo mu muryango.
Abategetsi muri Liberiya, barimo gucungira hafi abandi bantu barenga 150 bashobora kuba bafite iyo virusi. Barimo abakozi bo mu buvuzi n’abandi bagize aho bahurira n’uwo muryango.
Kuba hari abantu bashya banduye, bisubije inyuma icyo gihugu cyo mu burengerazuba bwa Afrika, byari byavuzwe ko kitakirangwamo Ebola kw’ itariki ya 9 y’ukwezi kwa 5 n’ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS. Cyakora abantu bashya bongeye kuboneka baranduye mu kwezi kwa 6.
Umuyobozi w’itsinda rishinzwe gutabara ku byerekeye Ebola muri OMS, Bruce Aylward, yavuze ko bitarasobanuka ukuntu uwo mwana w’umuhungu yanduye Ebola. Yavuze ko, uwo mwana hamwe n’umuryango we, ntaho bizwi mu mateka ko bahuye n’abarokotse Ebola cyangwa abo yahitanye.
Liberia ni kimwe mu bihugu 3 byazahajwe cyane n’icyorezo cya Ebola, cyatangiye mu kwezi kwa 12 umwaka wa 2013. Abantu barenga ibihumbi 10 banduye iyo ndwara muri icyo gihugu. Ibihumbi birenga 4,800 yarabahitanye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5122678' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5122678.html' term='ebola'>
Urucanco Rugira Kabiri rwa Ebola Ruzogeragezwa muri Kongo
Muri Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Kongo, abaganga bagiye kuzogerageza urucanco rugira kabiri rwa Ebola kuva mu kwezi kwa 11, mu ntara zitatu mu buseruko bw’ico gihugu.
Ni mu rugamba rwo kurwanya uwo mugera, nk'uko vyashikirijwe na Jean-Jacques Muyembe, arongoye ibikorwa vyo kurwanya Ebola muri Kongo.
Muyembe yavuze ko amakomine ya Majingo na Kahembe yacaguwe gutangurirwamwo guhabwa urwo rucanco kuko ni yo yasinzikaye kurusha ayandi.
Mu gihe rwokora neza, ruzoca rukoreshwa no mu ntara za Kivu y’ubumanuko na Ituri zihana imbibe na Uganda, u Rwanda hamwe n’Uburundi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2458384' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2458384.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola Isa n'Iyahagaritswe muri Senegali no muri Nijeriya
Ibiro vy’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu bijejwe amagara y’abantu (OMS), bitangaza ko ikiza ca Ebola muri Nigeriya na Senegal, gisa nicahagaritswe naho igitigiri c’abantu bamaze guhitanwa nayo murako karere kigeze hafi ku bihumbi 2,800.
Icegeranyo c’ibiro vya OMS muri Afrika casohowe cerekana ko ata muntu mushasha arandura iyo ngwara muri Nigeriya kuva kw’itariki 8 z’ukwezi kw’icenda, kandi ko atanuwundi muntu arayandura muri Senegal, kuva hatangajwe umuntu wambereye yayanduye kw’itariki 29 z’ukwezi kw’umunani.
O.N.U itangaza ko, abantu babandanya kwandura Ebola muri Guinea, Liberia na Sierra Leone. Igitigiri c’abamaza kuyandura kikaba kigeze ku bihumbi 5,762. Igitigiri c’abamaze guhitanwa nayo kigeze ku bantu ibihumbi 2,793.
OMS itangaza kandi ko, ubundi bwoko bw’ikiza ca Ebola muri Republika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo bumaza kwica abantu 40, abandi 71 bakaba bamaze kuyandura.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2491423' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2491423.html' term='ebola'>
Urukingo rwa Ebola Rushobora Kuboneka mu Ntangiriro za 2015
Ishami rya ONU ryita ku Buzima OMS, riravuga ko urukingo rwa Ebola rushobora kuzaba rwatangiye gukoreshwa bitarenze ukwezi kwa mbere k'umwaka utaha.
Umuyobozi wungilije wa OMS, Dr. Marie Paule Kieny, ejo kuwa kabiri yavuze ko, urukiko rwa Ebola ubu rurimo kugeragezwa, ko bitegeanyijwe ko ruzakoreshwa ku mu gabane w’Uburayi, muri Leta Zunze ubumwe za Amerika, no muri Afurika. Yavuze ko, bigaragaye ko nta mbogamizi urwo rukingo rwatera, rushobora gukorerwa igeragezwa mu burengerazuba bwa Afurika. Avugana n’abanyamakuru I Geneve mu Busuwisi, Dr. Kieny ntiyavuze igihe urukingo rwa Ebola, rwazaba rwabonetse ahantu hose.
Muri Espagne, abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima, bavuga ko ibyiciro bibiri by’igeragezwa ry’urwo rukingo, byerekanye ko umukozi wo kwa muganga ufatanya n’umuforomo, wari wanduye Ebola, ubu nta virusi ikimurwangwamo. Teresa Romeo Ramos, yari mu bitaro kuva aho amariye gusuzumwa iyo ndwara ya Ebola, mu ntangiliro z’uku kwezi. Iyi ndwara imaze guhitana abantu barenga ibihumbi 4 na magana 5 mu burengererazuba bwa Afurika uyu mwaka.
Ejo kuwa mbere, OMS yatangaje ko nta Ebola irangwa muri Nijeriya, nyuma y'iminsi 42 nta muntu ugaragayeho iyo ndwara. Cyakora perezida wa Nijeriya, Goodluck Jonathan, yasabye ko ingamba zoze zo kurwanya Ebola muri Nijeriya zigumaho, harimo no gupima abantu bose binjiye mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5101249' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5101249.html' term='ebola'>
Abahinga Bagabisha Ku Ndwara y'Ikiza Ishobora Kwica Benshi
Abahinga mu vyerekeye amagara y’abantu baragabisha ko indwara y’ikiza ishobora kugeramira amakungu ishobora kwaduka. Yamara ntibazi igihe iyo ndwara izokwadukirako.
Abajejwe amagara y’abantu bagabishije ku vyerekeye iyo ndwara y’ikiza muri iyi ndwi mu gihe abategetsi b’ibihugu vyo kw’isi bakoraniye mu nama rusangi y’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU i New York.
Abo bahinga bavuga ko ico kiza gishobora gukwiragira kw’isi yose mu kiringo c’amasaha 36, kigahitana abantu bagera ku miliyoni 80. Batangaza kandi ko ico kiza gishobora gusinzikaza bikomeye ubutunzi kw’isi.
Umurwi w’abahinga mu vyerekeye amagara y’abantu wigenga utangaza ko intambwe zikomeye zashitsweko mu vyerekeye ubuvuzi mu myaka itari mike irangiye. Batanze akarorero k’indwara ya Sida mu ntango iherezo ry’abayanduye kwari ugupfa.
Yamara batangaza ko muri iki gihe uburyo bw’ukuvura abafise iyo ndwara bwarahindutse, ubushakashatsi ku vyerekeye gutora urucandago kuri iyo ndwara bukaba butanga icizere.
Vyongeye haravugwa ko indwara ya malariya ishobora guhagarikwa burundu. Malariya yica abantu 500,000 kw’isi uko umwaka utashe, benshi muri bo abana.
Abahinga mu vy’ubumenyi bari hafi y’ugutorera inyishu indwara ya Ebola. Incadago kuri iyo ndwara ziriko zirakoreshwa ku bayanduye muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo.
Mbere y’izo ncandago, Ebola yica abagera ku bice 90 kw’jana vy’abantu bayanduye. Yamara ubu si ko ibintu bikiri.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4718468' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/congo-polisi-yarashe-abigaragambya-bamagana-isubika-ry-amatora-/4718468.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Polisi Yarashe Abigaragambya Bamagana Isubika ry'Amatora
Muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, polisi yakoresheje amasasu y’intambara mu mujyi wa Beni, mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru, irasa mu baturage bari mu myigaragambyo yo kwamagana icyemezo cyo gusubika amatora.
Kugeza ubu nta nkuru ivuga niba hari abapfuye cyangwa abakomeretse.
Usibye i Beni, imyigaragambyo yabaye no mu mujyi wa Goma. Yiganje cyane cyane muri quartier yitwa Majengo ituwe ahananini n’abantu bakomoka Beni na Butembo.
Abanyeshuri ba kaminuza ya Goma na bo bakoze imyigaragambyo.
Muri iyi myigaragambyo, polisi yataye muri yombi abantu bataramenyekana umubare.
Komisiyo y’igihugu ishinzwe amatora, CENI, yatangaje ejo ko amatora, aho kuba ejobundi ku cyumweru nk’ahandi hose mu gihugu, yimuriwe mu kwezi kwa gatatu k’umwaka utaha wa 2019.
Izo ntara zasubitswemo amatora Beni, Butembo, Yumbi, no mu nkengero z’ahantu hose hari icyorezo cya Ebola. Icyorezo kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 350. Indi mpamvu y’isubikwa ry’ayo matora CENI itanga, ni umutekano muke.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2552045' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2552045.html' term='ebola'>
Ingufu zo Kurwanya Ebola Zigomba Gushyirwa muri Sierra Leone
Intumwa yiyariye ya ONU ku kibazo cya ONU David Nabarro avuga ko impungenge zireba ikwirakwira rya EBOLA ubu ziganje mu burengerazuba bwa Sierra Leone.
Aha ni mu nkengero z’umujyi wa Port Loko , mu murwa mukuru Freetown ndetse no mu majyaruguru ya Gineya. Yasobanuye ko Umuryango w’Abibumbye n’abafatanya bikorwa bawo bazashyir aingufu nyinshi muri utwo turere kugirango barandure Ebola.
Nabarro yabwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika ko ubwiyongere bw’ubwandu bwa EBOLA mu burengerazuba bwa Sierra Leone bwatewe n’uko abaturage baho batitabiriye inyigisho bahawe zo kwirinda Ebola.
Nabarro avuga ko hagikenewe ibindi bitanda byo gushyira mu bigo bivura Ebola, kandi ko hakenewe abakozi bo mu rwego mpuzamahanga. Yagize ati, hakenerwa hafi abantu 300 bo gukora mu kigo gifite ibitanda by’abarwayi 50.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5212879' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5212879.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Intambara muri Kongo Zirabangamiye Ukurwanya Ebola
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS rishikiriza ko umutekano muke hamwe no kutabasha gushika mu bice birimwo intambara muri Republika ya demokarasi ya Kongo bikiri intambamyi nyamukuru zo kurandurana n’imizi ikiza ca Ebola.
Raporo ya nyuma ya OMS yemeza ko abantu 3354 kugeza ubu ari bo banduye Ebola, barimwo 2218 yahitanye.
Abategetsi mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu bahagaritswe umutima n'uko intambwe zatewe mu kurwanya Ebola mu ntara z’uburaruko bwa Kivu na Ituri zishobora kuba imfagusa kubwo intambara z’imihari yitwaje ibirwanisho zikibandanya.
OMS ishikiriza ko uwo mugera warwanijwe mu duce 25 tw’izo ntara, kandi ko abantu bane kw’icumi ari bo bashasha bakiriwe mu ndwi ziheze.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5062881' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5062881.html' term='ebola'>
Uwa Kabiri Yagaragaye ko Yanduye Ebola muri Uganda
Umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu wa Uganda yaremeje ku mugoroba wo kuwa kane ko hari umwana w’umukobwa w’imyaka icenda yagaragaye ko yanduye Ebola yinjiye muri Uganda. Uwo mwana yaciye atwarwa mu kigo categuriwe abanduye Ebola muri distrikte ya Kasese mu burengero, nkuko amakuru ashikirizwa n’umumenyeshamakuru w’Ijwi ry’Amerika i Kampala, Halima Athumani abivuga.
Mw’itangazo ryasohowe ejo kuwa kane, Dr. Joyce Moriku Kaducu, ajejwe ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu, yavuze ko uwo mwana yinjiye na nyina muri Uganda ava muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo ku musi wa gatatu.
Abaye uwugira kabiri amenyekanye ko yanduye Ebola muri Uganda aturutse hanze y'igihugu. Mu kwezi kwa gatandatu, umwana w’umuhungu w’imyaka itanu yarapfiriye muri Uganda, inyuma yo kwinjira mur’ico gihugu n’umuryango wiwe bavuye muri Kongo, aho abantu barenga 1,800 bamaze gupfa bishwe na Ebola kuva mu kwezi kwa munani 2018.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3042178' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3042178.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola Yaba Yaracitse muri Sierra Leone
Ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, irateganya gutangaza kuri uyu wa gatandatu ko Ebola yarandutse muri Sierra Leone. Hashize iminsi 42 nta muntu wongeye kwandura icyo cyorezo.
Abaturage barategura ibirori hirya no hino mu gihugu kugirango bishimire iyo nsinzi, ariko kandi banazirikane abantu ibihumbi bine Ebola yahitanye muri Sierra Leone. Nk’uko Abdulla Bayraytay, umuhuzabikorwa byo kurwanya Ebola muri Sierra Leone abitangaza, Perezida Ernest Koroma nawe azageza ijambo ku baturage b’igihugu cye.
Biteganijwe ko azashimira abagize uruhare bose mu rugamba rwo guhashya Ebola, ariko kandi azibutsa rubanda ko bagomba gukomeza kuba maso no gukurikiza ibisabwa byose bwo kwirinda Ebola, kugirango itazabatungura ikagaruka nk’uko byagenze mu baturanyi babo ba Liberia na Guinea.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5182944' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/imirwano-i-beni-yatumye-oms-yimurira-abakozi-bayo-i-goma-/5182944.html' term='ebola'>
Imirwano i Beni Yatumye OMS Yimurira Abakozi Bayo i Goma
Abakozi ba ONU barenga igice ca gatatu bari mu bikorwa vyo kurwanya Ebola mu gisagara ca Beni mu buseruko bwa Republika ya demokarasi ya Kongo bimuriwe mu bumanuko bwa Goma kuri uyu wa kabiri.
Ishami ry’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU ryita ku magara, OMS rivuga ko imirwano itaborohereza mu twigoro barimwo two kurwanya Ebola, yatanguye kwiyadukiza mu 2018 mu kwezi kw’umunani.
OMS ivuga ko intambara i Beni yatumye abakozi 49 badakenewe cane bimuriwa i Goma.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2440114' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2440114.html' term='ebola'>
Umunyamerika wa Gatatu Wanduye Ebola Aratashye
Umunyamerika Rick Sacra, abaye umukozi ushinzwe ubuzima wa gatatu, wanduriye Ebola mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika.
Uyu muganga arimo kugaruka muri Amerika aho azagurikiranwa n’inzobere z’abaganga.
Kuri uyu wa gatanu nibwo Sacra, wakoreraga muri Liberia, yitezwe kugera muri leta ya Nebraska iri hagati mu burengerazuba bw’Amerika.
Sacra, azavulirwa mu bitaro bya Nebraska Medical Center, kiri mu mujyi wa Omaha.
Abandi banyamerika babiri banduye Ebola, ni muganga Kent Brantly na Nancy Writebol. Bombi baje gukira nyuma yo kuvurirwa mu bitaro bya kaminuza ya Emory, biri mu majyepfo ashyira uburasirazuba bw’umujyi wa Atlanta muri leta ya Georgia.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2494621' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2494621.html' term='ebola'>
Mali: Umukobwa w'Imyaka 2 ni we wa Mbere Wanduye Ebola
Igihugu ca Mali caratangaje umuntu wa mbere arwaye Ebola.
Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu mu gihugu ca Mali, Ousmane Kone, yatangaje kuri televiziyo ya Reta, ku musi wa kane mw’ijoro, kw’uwo murwayi ari umwana w’umukobwa w’imyaka ibiri, yazanywe mu bitaro, avanywe mu gihugu kibanyi ca Mali, ca Guinee, kimwe mu bihugu bitatu bisizikajwe bikomeye n’ikiza ca Ebola.
Ousmane Kone, yatangaje kw’amagara y’uwo mwana w’umukobwa ariko atera amera neza kurushiriza, kubera yavuwe mu buryro bwihuta.
Ari mu gisagara ca Kayes, kiri mu burengero bw’igihugu ca Mali.
Muri ico gihe, mu gisagara ca New York, Craig Spencer, umuganga aherutse kuvura abantu barwaye Ebola, mu gihugu ca Guinee yapimwe iyo ndwara mu bitaro Bellevue Hospital vyo mu gisagara ca New York.
Ku musi wa kane, Spencer yabwiye Ishirahamwe rijejwe gutabara, Medecins sans Frontieres, yakorera mu gihugu ca Guinee, ko yari afise ubushuhe bwinshi mu mubiri, kandi yumva afise iseseme, ibimenyetso bibiri vy'indwara ya Ebola.
Yajanywe vyihuta mu bitaro vyo mu gisagara ca New York, Bellevue Hospital, kugira asuzumwe.
Ukwiyadukiza kw’ikiza ca Ebola, gushimikiye cane cane, mu bihugu bitatu vyo mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, n’ukuvuga Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4385835' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4385835.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Abantu 17 Baramaze Guhitanwa na Ebola
Igihugu ca Republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo catangaje ko ikiza ca Ebola kimaze kugaragara mu karere ka Bikoro mu ntara ya Equateur, inyuma y’aho abantu 17 bamaze kumenyekana ko baheruka gupfa, abandi babiri batangajwe ko bafashwe.
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS, ryatangaje kuri uyu wa kabiri ko igihugu ca Kongo catewe na Ebola. OMS imenyesha ko yasohoye umuliyoni umwe w’Amadolari y’Abanyamerika yo gufasha vyihuta kurwanya ico kiza.
OMS yavuze ko mu ndwi zitanu ziheze, abantu batanu bamenyekanye ko barwaye Ebola muri ako karere. Abantu cumi n’indwi barapfuye.
OMS ivuga ko itegekanya kurungika abahinga b’indwara z’ibiza, abaganga hamwe n’abahinga bajejwe kugenzura irwirirana ry’imigera muri ako karere mu misi iza. Ivuga kandi ko yamaze kubimenyesha ibihugu bibanyi na republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo.
Mu mwaka w’2017 niho Ebola iheruka muri RDC mu karere k’ubuvuzi ka Likati, aho abantu bane bapfuye kuri munani bari bafashwe. Bubaye ubugira icenda, ikiza ca Ebola gitera kuva aho uwo mugera umenyekaniye mu mwaka w’1976.
Ibihugu ico kiza cihayemwo inkumbi ni Guinea, Sierra Leone, na Liberiya. Cahamaze kuva mu mwaka wa 2014 gushika 2016 cica abarenga ibihumbi cumi na kimwe.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3147376' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3147376.html' term='ebola'>
Sierra Leone: Uwundi Muntu Yahitanwe na Ebola
Umutegetsi mu gihugu ca Sierra Leone, amenyesha kw’ikiziga c’umuntu capimwe bagisangamwo umugera wa Ebola, umusi umwe gusa inyuma yuko ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, ritangaje ko ukwiyadukiza kwa Ebola kwarangiye mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Ishirahamwe OMS, ryamenyesheje mw’itangazo uno musi ku wa gatanu ko ryemeza ivyerekeye uwo muntu yahitanywe na Ebola mu gihugu ca Sierra Leone. Ikiziga c’uwo muntu w’igitsinagore casuzumwe inyuma yuko arwaye yitaba Imana mu ntango z’uku kwezi.
Ishirahamwe, OMS, rivuga ko ivyo vyerekana ko gukwirikiranira hafi n’ukwishura ku vyerekeye gusubira kwiyadukiza kwa Ebola bikenewe cane mu mezi ari imbere.
Ejo ku musi wa kane, Ishirahamwe OMS, ryatangaje kw’ukwiyadukiza kw’umugera wa Ebola kwarangiye mu gihugu ca Liberiya.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5094511' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5094511.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Yagiriza Tanzaniya Guhisha Aboba Baranduye Ebola
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS, ryashikirije ku musi wa gatandatu ko reta ya Tanzaniya idashira ahabona amakuru y'abakekwa kuba baranduye umugera wa Ebola muri ico gihugu.
OMS yashikirije ko yaronse amakuru ko hari abantu batari bake banduye Ebola mu bice bitandukanye muri ico gihugu co muri Afrika y’ubuseruko kandi bashizwe mu bwiherero, harimwo n'i Dar es Salaam.
Ni mu gihe abategetsi mu bihugu vyo mu buseruko no hagati muri Afurika bameze magabo kugira bakinge ko Ebola yamamara mu karere, inyuma y’aho yadukiye muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo, aho imaze guhitana abarenga 2,000 kuva mu kwezi kwa munani 2018.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4963814' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ubwicanyi-bushingiye-ku-moko-bwabaye-ndanze-muri-congo-/4963814.html' term='ebola'>
Ubwicanyi Bushingiye ku Moko Bwabaye Urudaca muri Kongo
Muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo, abantu barenga ibihumbi 300 bavuye mu byabo mu byumweru bibiri bishize kubera ubwicanyi hagati y’amoko y’abahema n’abalendu, mu ntara ya Ituri, mu majyaruguru y’uburasirazuba bw’igihugu.
Ni umuvugizi wa HCR (Ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku mpunzi), Babar Baloch, wabitangaje uyu munsi mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru ku cyicaro gikuru cya HCR i Geneve mu Busuwisi.
Ejo, ubuyobozi bw’intara ya Ituri bwatangaje ko ubu bwicanyi bwahitanye abantu 161. Imirwano hagati y’abahema n’abalendu yabaye agahoraho. Mu mwaka ushize, nabwo barwanye bapfa ubutaka.
Abantu barenga ijana babiguyemo. Abandi barenga ibihumbi 350 nabwo bavuye mu byabo, bamwe muri bo bahungira muri Uganda bambutse ikiyaga Albert. Hagati y’umwaka w’1999 n’umwaka w’2003, abahema n’abalendu bararwanye, intambara ihitana abantu batabarika.
Kuba abantu bahunga ari benshi biteye ikibazo cyo kurwanya icyorezo cya ebola kirimo kiyogoza Ituri. Abantu bashobora kuyikwirakwiza kugera no muri Uganda na Sudani y’Epfo. Ituri ihana imbibi n’ibi bihugu byombi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1886921' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/1886921.html' term='ebola'>
Mali: Gutohoza Icaduka ca Ebola Byaratanguye.
Abajejwe amagara y’abantu barungitse ibipomo vy’abo bantu mu gisagara ca Atlanta, muri reta zunze ubumwe za amerika kugira ngo bapime , barabe kw’iyo, ar’ingwara ya Ebola koko.
Mu kurindira ibizova mur’ico gipimo kizokorerwa muri laboratoire yo mu gisagara ca Atlanta, abo bantu batatu bikekwa ko bagwaye ingwara ya Ebola, babaye barakumirirwa mu kibanza ca bonyene, aho bariko baravurwa.
Ibiro vy’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu bijejwe amagara y’abantu, vyatangaje kw’abantu bashika 86, bamaze kwicwa n’ingwara ya Ebola mu ntara ya Afrika yo mu burengero, cane cane mu gihugu ca Guinee, hamwe no mu gihugu ca Liberia aho iyo ngwara imaze kwica abantu indwi
Ivyo biro vyatangaje kandi ko biriko biratohoza amakuru avuga kw’abantu 154 bashobora kuba bagwaye iyo ngwara ya Ebola, cane cane mu gihugu ca Guinee.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5285499' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5285499.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Igomba Kwemeza Niba Ebola Ikiri Icyorezo Cyihutirwa
Uyu munsi, abahanga ba OMS, ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, bateraniye i Geneve mu Busuwisi. Bagomba kwemeza niba Ebola muri Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Congo ikiri ikibazo cyihutirwa ku rwego rw’isi.
Mu kwezi kwa karindwi mu mwaka ushize, OMS yatangaje ko Ebola ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose kigomba kwitabwago ku rwego rwa mbere. Bityo OMS yagize ububasha budasanzwe, nko gushaka amafaranga no kugamabya ingendo za rubanda ku isi yose. Ebola yateye muri Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Congo mu kwezi kwa munani 2018. Yahitanye abantu ibihumbi bibiri na 300.
Mbere y’inama y’uyu munsi i Geneve, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Ghebreyesus, yatangaje ko Ebola yagabanutse ku buryo bushimishije. Ati: “Mu cyumweru gishize, abantu batatu bonyine ni bo bayanduye. Muri iyi minsi itatu ishize, nta muntu n’umwe yafashe.” Kuri we, ni “intsinzi ikomeye ariko ntakwirara kuko umuntu umwe wanduye ashobora gutuma na none icyirezo kigaruka.” Dr. Tedros Ghebreyesus yavuze ko azajya muri Repubulika demokarasi ejo kuwa kane kuganira na Perezida Félix Tshisekedi.
Naho aba bahanga mpuzamahanga bari mu nama i Geneve bagize itsinda riterana buri mezi atatu iyo hari icyorezo giteye aho ari hose ku isi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4842398' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4842398.html' term='ebola'>
UNICEF Irasabira Imfashanyo Abana muri Kongo
Ikigega mpuzamakungu c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU cita ku bana UNICEF, gisaba reta nshasha ya Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gutanga imfashanyo ku banyagihugu baba mu ntara zasinzikajwe n’intambara, aho imiliyoni 13 z’abantu bacumukura kugira baronke ico bafungura, uburaro hamwe n’inyigisho.
Umuyobozi mpuzabikorwa wa UNICEF, Henrietta Fore hamwe n’umwunganirizi w’umunyamabanga ajejwe imfashanyo, Mark Lowcock yatahutse avuye muri Kongo mur’iyi ndwi, asaba amafaranga yo gufasha imiliyoni zine z’abana hamwe n’abanyagihugu bamugaye.
Intumwa za ONU muri Kongo zarabonanye na perezida Felix Tshisekedi kandi ngo baragiranye ibiganiro vyubaka kubijanye no gutanga imfashanyo ku banyagihugu.
Izo ntumwa kandi zarabonanye n’umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu, Oly Ilunga bavuga ku kiza ca Ebola cateye ibisagara vya Beni na Butembo. ONU ivuga ko abana barenga 1000 batandukanijwe n’abavyeyi babo canke babaye impfuvyi. Abana bagize ica gatatu c’abanduye Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2618488' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2618488.html' term='ebola'>
O-M-S Ishimikiye ku Gikorwa c'Ukurandurana n'Imizi, Ebola
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S, ryamenyesheje, ku musi wa kane, kw’utwigoro tw’ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola, muri iki gihe, dushimikye ku vyerekeye kurandurana n’imizi ico kiza, inyuma yuko igitigiri c’abantu bashasha bandura Ebola, uko indwi itashe, kigabanutse ku rugero ruri hasi cane, mu bitari bwabe kuba, mu kwezi kwa gatandatu.
Abantu bashaha mirongo icenda n’icenda nibo batangajwe, mu ndwi iheze, ko banduye Ebola, mu bihugu vya Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone, vyasinzikajwe bikomeye n’ikiza ca Ebola, umuntu afatiye ku biharuro bishasha vy’ishirahamwe O-M-S.
Igitigiri c’abanduye Ebola, caragabanutse bikomeye cane, mu gihugu ca Sierra Leone, aho abantu bashasha mirongo itandatu na batanu, bafise Ebola, batangajwe, mu ndwi iheze, umuntu abigereranije n’abantu ijana na cumi n’imdwi, mu ndwi y’imbere yaho, n’abandu ijana na mirongo umunani na bane, indwi zitatu z’imbere yaho.
Mu gihugu ca Liberia, abantu bashasha bane, nibo batangajwe ko bafise Ebola, mu ndwi iheze, bavuye ku bantu amajana atatu, ku ndwi, mu kwezi kw’umunani, n'ukwezi kw'icenda.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4956064' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/ebola-yahitanye-umwana-muri-uganda-babiri-bandi-barayandura-/4956064.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yahitanye Umwana muri Uganda Babiri Bandi Barayandura
Umwana w’umuhungu w’imyaka itanu wo mu gihugu ca Uganda yari arwaye indwara ya Ebola yitavye Imana. Abaye umuntu wa mbere vyibonekeje ko afise Ebola mu karere ka Afurika y'ubuseruko kuva ico kiza cadutse muri Republika iharanira Demokrasi ya Kongo, ihana urubibe na Uganda hareheze umwaka.
Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Uganda, Dr. Jane Ruth Aceng, yemeje ayo makuru yavuze ko uwo mwana yari yajanywe mu bitaro vya Kagando mu burengero bw’igihugu.
Nyakwigendera n'umuryango wiwe binjiye muri Uganda bavuye muri Republika iharanira Demokrasi ya Kongo ku musi wa mbere.
Aceng avuga ko abategetsi ba Reta ya Uganda bemeje ko abandi bantu babiri banduye Ebola. Yasavye abanya Uganda gukorana n’abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu mu ntumbero y’ugutuma Ebola idakwiragira mu bindi bice vy’igihugu.
Ishirahamwe OMS rivuga ko Ebola imaze guhitana abantu bagera ku 1.400 mu karere kuva mu kwezi kw’umunani kw’umwaka uheze w’i 2018.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2476458' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2476458.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Ebola Ihitanye Umuntu wa Mbere Wayikuye muri Liberiya
Thomas Duncan umurwayi wa Ebola wari mu bitaro muri leta ya Texas iri mu majyepfo ya Amerika yitabye imana. Duncan ni we murwayi wa mbere wagaragayeho indwara ya Ebola muri Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika, yari yararembeye mu bitaro byitwa “Texas Health Presbyterian Hospital”.
Itangazo ry’ibyo bitaro rivuga ko Thomas Duncan yitabye Imana saa moya n’iminota 51 ku isaha yaho, taliki ya 8 y'ukwa cumi 2014.
Hagati aho, ibitangazamakuru biravuga ko Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika, izashyira abakozi ku bibuga by’indege n’ahandi abagenzi binjirira kugirango basuzume abantu niba badafite ibimenyetso bya Ebola.
Amakuru dukesha ibiro ntaramakuru by’abanyamerika, the Associated Press, avuga ko uwungilije ministri w’umutekano w’imbere mu gihugu, Alejandro Mayorkas, yavuze kuri uyu wa gatatu ko, abakozi ba Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika, bazashyirwa ahantu h’ingenzi hanyura abantu benshi binjira muri Amerika, kugirango basuzume ibimenyetso kandi batange n’amakuru ajyana na virusi ya Ebola.
Mayorkas ntiyavuze igihe izo ngamba zizatangira kubahilizwa. Yavuze ko abarinda za gasutamo n‘imipaka, bazatanga impapuro ziriho urutonde rw’ibimenyetso bya Ebola hamwe n’amabwiriza ku bo bashinzwe ububima bagomba kwitabaza.
Muri iki gitondo cyo kuwa gatatu intumwa za ONU muri Liberia, zavuze ko umukozi wabo wa kabiri yanduye Ebola. Mu itangazo, izo ntumwa za ONU zavuze ko umutegetsi mu rwego rw’ubuvuzi mpuzamahanga, arimo kuvurwa, ariko ntiryavuze igihugu akomokamo. Uwa mbere mu ntumwa za ONU wanduye Ebola yitabye imana mu kwezi gushize.
Icyorezo cya Ebola kimaze guhitana abantu barenga ibihumbi bitatu na magana ane, abenshi muribo ni abo muri Liberiya, Gineya na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2609222' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2609222.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Iragenda Ikendera muri Afurika y'Uburengerazuba
Mu burengerazuba bwa Afrika, ubwandu bwa Ebola bwagabanutse cyane.
Umubare w’abantu banduye Ebola mu burengerazuba bwa Afurika wababanutse cyane mu cyumweru gishize, bikaba byongera icyizere cy’uko icyo cyorezo kigiye gucika mu karere.
Amakuru dukesha Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, abantu 145 ni bo baheruka kwandura Ebola muri Guineya , Liberia na Sierra Leone, mu mpera z’icyumweru cyarangiye ku itariki ya 18 y’uku kwezi kwa mbere.
Icumi muri abo banduye, babonetse muri Liberia, ni umubare muto mu bihumbi bitatu kugeza kuri bine banduye buri cyumweru mu kwezi kwa munani n’ukwa cyenda.
Abantu 170 bashya, byemejwe ko banduye muri Sierra Leone, ariko naho, OMS ivuga ko, umubare w’abarwayi bashya waganutse vuba. Umubare uheruka gutangazwa, ugaragaza ko ubwandu bwa Ebola bwagabanutseho ibirenga 50 ku ijana mu byumweru bibiri bishize.
Abategetsi muri ONU bishimiye iryo gabanuka ry’ubwandu, ariko kandi bashimangira ko, bikenewe kuguma kuba maso, no gukomeza ingamba zirimo gukoreshwa, mu guhagarika virusi ya Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4561519' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4561519.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Ebola Yatandukiriye Butembo, Abapfuye Bageze kuri 88
Abamaze kwica na Ebola mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo bamaze gushika kuri 88. Vyashikirijwe ejo kwa kane n’umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu mugihe uwo mugera uriko uratandukira igisagara ca Butembo, gikomeye mu bucuruzi kandi kibamwo abantu bashika ku muliyoni.
Umuntu wa mbere yagaragaye ko yanduye uwo mugera i Butembo yari umugore hamwe n’umukozi wo kwa muganga yariko aramuvura.
Uwo mugore yapfuye ku musi wa kabiri yari yahungiye hafi ya Beni ariko yanka gusuzumwa b’abaganga inyuma y’aho yanduriye, nkuko umushikiranganji abandanya avuga.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5029656' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/uganda-yatanguye-gukoresha-urucanco-rwa-ebola-/5029656.html' term='ebola'>
Uganda Yatanguye Gukoresha Urucanco rwa Ebola
Igihugu ca Uganda catangaje uno musi ku wa mbere ko catanguye gukoresha urucanco rushasha rukiriko rugeragezwa. Urwo rucanco rushobora kuzokoreshwa mu gihugu kibanyi ca Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo.
Bitegekanijwe ko igeragezwa ry’urucanco, “MVA-BN” rwatunganijwe n’isosiyete, “Johnson & Johnson” rimara imyaka ibiri.
Urwo rucanco ruzokoreshwa ku baganga n’abaforoma 800 mu karere ka Mbarara kari mu burengero bw’igihugu ca Uganda. Bivurwa ko igikorwa c’ugucandaga kiza caratanguye.
Urucanco ku ndwara ya Ebola rwakoreshejwe ubwa mbere ku gitigiri kinini c’abantu igihe iyo ndwara yiyadukiza muri Kongo.
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu bakoresheje urucanco, “rVSV-ZEBOV” rwatunganijwe n’isosiyete ikora imiti yo muri Amerika, “Merck”.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, ryasavye ko urwo rucanco rukoreshwa kurushiriza.
Urucanco, “MVA-BN” ruvurwa ko rukora neza kandi ko rwakoreshejwe ku bantu barenga 6.000 mu karere k’i Bulaya, Reta zunze ubumwe za Amerika n’ibihugu vyo muri Afrika harimwo igihugu ca Uganda.
Urucanco, “rVSV-ZEBOV” rwakoreshejwe mu gihugu ca Guinee igihe ikiza ca Ebola ciyadukiza mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero hagati y’umwaka w’i 2013 n’umwaka w’i 2016. Ivyo vyatumye abahinga mu vyerekeye ubumenyi bavuga ko rwakoze neza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5263687' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5263687.html' term='ebola'>
Virusi ya Corona Ishobora Guhungabanya Ubukungu bw'Afurika
Ubuyobozi bw’igihugu cy’Afurika y’Epfo kuri uyu wa kabiri bwavuze ko bwiteguye ibishoboka byose kugira ngo bakumire Virusi ya Corona mu nkombe z’Afurika. Ubuyobozi buravuga ko kugeza ubu nta muntu uragaragaraho iyo Virusi yatangiriye mu gihugu cy’ubushinwa imaze kwica abagera ku 106.
Ikigo cy’igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya indwara zandura cyatangaje ko ubuyobozi bwafashe ingamba zikomeye ku kibuga cy’indege cya Johannesburg kinyuraho abantu benshi kurusha ibindi bibuga byo muri Afurika. Mu minsi yashize, iki kibuga cy’indege cyashyizeho uburyo bwo gupima abantu umuriro n’izindi ndwara z’ibyorezo nka Ebola na Zika.
Iki kigo cyavuze ko hari uburyo bwerekana byihuse umuntu waba afite ibimenyetso by’iyi Virusi byagaragara ku mipaka y’igihugu. Ushinzwe ubukungu muri imwe mu mabanki y’Afrika y’Epfo yavuze ko nubwo nta muntu urarwara muri iki gihugu ariko ubukungu bw’igihugu bumaze kugwa bitewe n’uko ubuhahirane hagati y’Afrika y’Epfo n’Ubushinwa bwagabanutse. Iyi mpuguke mu bukungu ivuga ko virusi ya corona izatuma amasoko y’imari ahungabana ku mugabane w’Afurika.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2491809' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2491809.html' term='ebola'>
Rwanda: Gusuzuma Ebola Abantu Bavuye muri Amerika na Espagne
Igihugu c’Urwanda categetse abantu bavuye muri Amerika na Espagne, gushikiriza imisi yose, amakuru ajanye n’amagara yabo abategetsi bajejwe ubuvuzi, bakoresheje telephon,e kubera indwara ya Ebola.
Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, na Espagne nivyo bihugu bibiri, hanze y’akarere ka Afrika, vyatangaje abantu banduye Ebola.
Uwariwe wese yagiye muri ivyo bihugu bibiri, ategerezwa gushikiriza amakuru yerekeye amagara yiwe, abategetsi b’Urwanda, mu kiringo c’imisi mirongo ibiri n’umwe ya mbere, azoba amaze mu gihugu.
Nta Ebola, iri mu gihugu c’Urwanda, muri iki gihe, ico gihugu kikaba gishaka kw’ibintu biguma gutyo.
Urwanda ruza rwaraziririje abantu baje bava mu bihugu vya Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone, ibihugu bigeramiwe n’ikiza ca Ebola. Abantu bavuye mu gihugu ca Senegal, cigeze gutangaza umuntu umwe yari afise Ebola, nabo nyene baraziririjwe kuza mu Rwanda
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4510294' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4510294.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Ibindi Bimenyetso vya Ebola muri Kivu y'Uburaruko
Abantu bane baramaze kugaragara ko bafise ibimenyetso vy’umugera wa Ebola mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, nkuko vyatangajwe n’abategetsi b'ico gihugu kuri uyu wa gatatu.
Buramatari w’intara ya Kivu ya ruguru, Julien Paluku, yabitangaje, mugihe hari haheze indwi imwe reta ya Kongo ifadikanije n’abategetsi ba OMS batangaje ko ico kiza casezerewe burundu mur’ico gihugu, inyuma yo guhitana abantu 33.
Abahinga bo mu bushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu bitezwe muri ako karere kuri uyu wa kane kuraba uko vyifashe, nkuko bishikirizwa n’umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2493206' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2493206.html' term='ebola'>
Amerika: Gukurikirana Ebola ku Bavuye muri Liberia, Gineya na Sierra Leone
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu, muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, bategetse abantu bavuye mu bihugu vyo mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero, gukwirikirana amagara yabo, mu kiringo c’imisi mirongo ibiri n’umwe, hanyuma bagatanga amakuru, imisi yose, ku bimenyetso ivyarivyo vyose, vy’indwara ya Ebola.
Abo bantu boba bavuye mu bihugu vya Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone, ibihugu aho indwara ya Ebola yatse indaro.
Uwo mugambi uzotangura, ku musi wa mbere, mu ma Reta atandatu yo mu buseruko bwa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Georgia, Maryland, New Jersey, New York, Pennsylvania na Virginia, aho benshsi mu bantu bavuye muri ivyo bihugu bogendera.
Abantu bazoba bavuye mu bihugu vya Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone, bazohabwa ibikoresho bipima Ebola, igihe bazoba bashitse, ku bibuga vy’indege, harimwo igipimo c'ubushuhe bw'umubiri, thermometre.
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu, muri Amerika, bavuga kw’imisi mirongo ibiri n’umwe ariyo misi Ebola imara, mu muntu kugira yibonekeza.
Ku musi wa gatatu, abaganga n’abaforoma bashasha bo mu gihugu ca Cuba baragiye, mu bihugu vya Guinee, na Liberia, gufasha kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2518023' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2518023.html' term='ebola'>
Umuforoma yanduye Ebola Yarapfuye muri Mali
Abategetsi mu gihugu ca Mali, bavuga kw’umuforoma yanduye umugera wa Ebola, yapfuye.
Uwo muforoma yapfuye, mu masaha akuze yo ku musi wa kabiri abaye umuntu agira kabir,i mu gihugu ca Mali, yemejwe kuba ahitanywe n’indwara ya Ebola. Umuntu wa mbere yishwe n’iyo ndwara, n’umwana w’umukobwa w’imyaka ibiri, yapfuye mu kwezi guheze.
Ubushikiranganji bujejwe amagara y’abantu bwamenyeshej,e ku musi wa gatatu, kw’uwo muforoma yakora, mu bitaro ku murwa mukuru w’igihugu ca Mali, Bamako, hakaba hafashwe ingingo kw’ata bantu binjira muri ivyo bitaro.
Abategetsi bavuga kw’uwo muforoma yavuye umuntu bemera ko yapfuye, inyuma yuko yanduye Ebola.
Igihugu ca Mali gihana urubibe n’gbihugu ca Guinee, aho ikiza ca Ebola cadutse, mu mwaka uheze.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi bitanu barapfuye, bahitanywe na Ebola, benshi muribo, mu bihugu ca Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4725719' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/kuki-abanyekongo-bahungira-muri-uganda-/4725719.html' term='ebola'>
Kuki Abanyekongo Bahungira muri Uganda?
Ishirahamwe ryitaho imbabare Croix Rouge ryatangaje ko abanyekongo amajana n’amajana b’impunzi bajabutse urubibe bakinjira mu gihugu ca Uganda.
Irene Nakasita, umuvugizi w’iryo shirahamwe muri Uganda, uyu musi ku wa gatatu, yatangaje ko izo mpunzi zatanguye gushika inyuma y’aho habereye amatora ku musi wa mungu kandi ko ziguma zishika ari nyinshi.
Uwo muvugizi asigura ko abanyekongo batari bake basubijwe inyuma, inyuma y’aho bankiye abakozi bajejwe amagara y’abantu ku ruhande rwa Uganda kubasuzuma ibimenyetso vy’ingwara ya Ebola.
Ivyo kandi vyatumye abantu bagira amakenga ko ikiza ca Cholera kimaze kwiha inkumbi mu gihugu ca Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo, gishobora gutandukira no muri Uganda.
Reta ya Kongo yaranse gukoresha amatora mu ntara zo mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw’igihugu zirimwo abanyagihugu bashika ku muliyoni, kubera ikiza ca Cholera cahadutse.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3868489' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3868489.html' term='ebola'>
Sudani y'Ubumanuko Yugaye Imipaka Kubera Ebola
Abategetsi b’Igihugu ca Sudani y’Ubumanuko batangaje ko imipaka ico gihugu gihana na Republika Iharanira Demokrasi ya Kongo yugawe, mu ntumbero yo kwirinda ikiza ca Ebola cica, catangajwe n’Ishami ry’Ishirahamwe Mpuzamakungu ONU, OMS, haraheze indwi zibiri. Ni mu gihe OMS imaze gutangaza ko abantu bane bahitanywe na Ebola muri Kongo.
Lino Utu, icegera ca Buramatari wa Reta ya Tambura, muri Sudani y’Ubumanuko yatangaje ko bahagaritse uruja n’uruza rw’abantu n’ibintu k’umupaka wa Ezo, gushika hasohotse irindi tegeko. Utu yavuze ko ako karere karangurirwamwo ibikorwa bitari bike, kandi ko abantu baho bafitaniye imigenderanire ikomeye y’urudandaza.
Utu yatangaje kandi ko abakozi b’amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu, harimwo n’abo muri OMS, ubu bari mu gikorwa co guhimiriza abanyagihugu ku bijanye no kubigisha uburyo iyo ndwara yirara mu bantu.
Abategetsi bo muri Reta ya Gbudue, nayo nyene ihana urubibe na Kongo, batangaje ko urudandaza rw’inyama rwabaye rurahagarikwa mur’ako karere, mu ntumbero yo gucungera uruja n’uruza rw’abadandaza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2438042' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2438042.html' term='ebola'>
O-M-S, Yasavye Amakungu Kwishura, Ari Hamwe, Mu Rugamba rw'Ukurwanya Ebola
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi, O-M-S, ryasavye inyishu y'amakungu, ku vyerekeye kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola, gitera ciyongera, kigeramiye ibice vyo mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Margaret Chan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishirahamwe O-M-S, yatangaje, ku musi wa gatatu kw'ikiza ca Ebola kimaze guhitana abantu barenga igihumbi n'amajena icenda muri iki gihe, abandi ibibumbi bitatu n'amajana atanu bakaba bamaze kwandura iyo ndwara, mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S, rivuga ko bizotwara imiliyoni amajana atandatu y'amadolari, mu rugamba rw'ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
Abahinga baragabishije kw'ikiza ca Ebola gishobora gukwiragira mu bindi bihugu, uretse ibimaze kugeramirwa n'ico kiza vya Guinee, Liberia, Nigeria, Senegal na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4691119' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4691119.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Ebola Yarinjiye mu Gisagara ca Butembo
Ikiza ca Sida muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo catandukiye igisagara ca Butembo gikomeye mu buseruko bw’igihugu. Kirimwo abantu barenga umuliyoni.
Abahinga mu vyerekeye amagara y’abantu barafise impungenge ko incandago ziriko zigeragezwa zizoba zikwiye mu rugamba rw’ukurwanya ico kidasa n’ikiriko kirarangira.
Umuyobozi mukuru w’ishirahamwe ry’abagiraneza, “Medecins Sans Frontieres” muri ico gisagara, John Johnson, avuga ko bafise impungenge ku kugene ibintu vyifashe ku bijanye n’ikiza ca Ebola.
Avuga ko abantu bashasha bandura iyo ndwara bariko batera biyongera mu bice vyo ku nkengera z’ico gisagara.
Gushika ubu abantu bamaze kwemezwa ko bafise Ebola muri Kongo ni 423, harimwo 225 bemejwe ko bamaze gupfa.
Iyo abantu 41.000 badacandagwa gushika ubu muri Kongo, abantu baba bamaze kwandura Ebola baba bamaze kurenga ibihumbi 10.000. Ivyo bitangazwa n’ubushikiranganji bujejwe amagara y’abantu mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3849480' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3849480.html' term='ebola'>
Abantu Batatu Bamaze Guhitanwa na Ebola Muri RDC
Ikiza ca Ebola catangajwe mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Congo, aho yahitanye abantu batatu kuva kw’italiki mirongo ibiri na zibiri z’ukwezi kwa kane. Ivyo vyatangaje uno musi ku wa gatanu n’ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS.
Ku bw’iryo shirahamwe, ico kiza ca Ebola kiri mu karere karimwo ishamba mu ntara ya Bas-Uele, ku rubibe n’igihugu ca Centrafrika. Ubwa nyuma Ebola yiyadukije muri Congo hari mu mwaka w’i 2014. Yararwanijwe ningoga, yamara yahitanye abantu mirongo ine na babiri, mu biharuro vyatangajwe icese.
Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagera y’abantu muri Congo, Oly Ilunga yaremeje ukwiyadukiza gushasha kwa Ebola. Yasavye abanyagihugu kutagira ubwoba.
Yamenyesheje ko Reta yafashe ingingo zikenewe kugira yishure mu buryo bwihutirwa kuri ico kiza ca Ebola gisubiye kwiyadukiza.
Ishirahamwe OMS rimenyesha ko ririko rikorana n’abategetsi ba Reta ya Congo, kugira barungike ibikoresho n’abakozi bajejwe gufasha guhagarika ningoga ico kiza ca Ebola ciyadukije mu gice kitoroshe gushikamwo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4067007' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4067007.html' term='ebola'>
Urucanco rwa Ebola Rwoba Rugiye Kuboneka
Incanco zibiri ziriko zirageragezwa ku mugera wa Ebola zisa n’izitanga ivyizere.
Ivyigwa vyatangajwe mu kinyamakuru “The New England Journal” co mu Bwongereza candika kuvy’amagara y’abantu, vyerekana ko incanco zageragejwe ku bantu 1500, abashika 80 kw’ijana babonetse ko imibiri yabo ishobora kurinda Ebola.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu ntumbero yo gukorera hamwe hagati ya Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika na Liberiya ku mugera wa Ebola.
Mwibuke ko ikiza ca Ebola cihaye inkumbi cane cane muri Liberiya, muri Guinee no muri Sierra Leone hagati y’imyaka ya 2013 na 2016 gihitana ubuzima bw’abantu barenga ibihumbi cumi na kimwe.
Incanco zishika 15 nizo ziriko zirageragezwa. Abahinga bavuga ko incanco za mbere zishobora kwemezwa mu mwaka wa 2018 uza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3368883' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3368883.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yacitse muri Liberiya
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi OMS, ryatangaje kur’uyu wa kane ko ata mugera wa Ebola ukirangwa mu gihugu ca Liberiya. Aho n’inyuma y’iminsi 42 ata muntu abonetse ko yoba awufise.
Ishirahamwe OMS, ryakeje Reta ya Liberiya, n’abanyagihugu bayo k’uburyo bigenje neza mu kiza ca nyuma giheruka. Muganga Alex Gasasira, asanzwe aserukira OMS muri Liberiya, yavuze ko iryo shirahamwe rizobandanya gufasha Liberiya mu gukinga, gucungera no kuvura uwo mugera, igihe woba usubiye kuboneka.
Iri ribaye irigira kane, mu kiringo c’imyaka ibiri, umugera wa Ebola wibonekeje muri Liberiya, inyuma yaho uba watujijwe. Ikiza giheruka catewe n’umugore avuye muri Gineya ari kumwe n’abana, baraheza bawinjirana muri Liberiya.
Abantu 11.000 barapfuye bahitanywe na Ebola, mu bihugu bitatu uwo mugera wabangamiye kurusha, mu karere ka Afurika y’uburengero.
Ishirahamwe OMS ryatangaje ko umugera wa Ebola waheze mu mpera z’umwaka uheze.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4913477' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4913477.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Ishobora Kugera Mu Bihugu Bituranye na Kongo
Ishami ry’umiryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS riravuga ko Ibitero by’imitwe yitwaje imbunda, gutanga nabi amakuru kimwe no kubura ingengo y’imari; biza ku isonga mu gukoma mu nkokora ibikorwa byo kurwanya icyorezo cya Ebola muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo.
OMS iranatanga impuruza ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuganza imbaraga zo kukirwanya.
Umutekano muke mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw’igihugu urabuza abarimo kurwanya iki cyorezo gukurikirana abarwayi no gukingira abatarandura. Ibi bikubiye mu cyegeranyo giheruka cya OMS cyashyizwe ahagaragara ku wa gatanu w’iki cyumweru dusoza.
OMS iravuga ko iki cyorezo kitazabasha kugenzurwa neza mu gihe imitwe yose yitwaje imbunda mu ntara ya Kivu y’Amajyaruguru n’iya ituri idatanze agahenge.
Mugihe uwo mutekano utaboneka byakongera ibyago by’uko ebola yakwirakwira no mu bindi bice by’igihugu ikaba yagera no mu bihugu by’u Rwanda, Uganda na Sudani y’epfo bituranye na Kongo.
Imirwano hagati y’ingabo za leta n’imitwe igera kuri 50 y’inyeshyamba; kwibasira abakozi bajya gushyingura abo ebola yahitanye mu mugi wa Butembo byasubije ibintu irudubi mu kwezi gushize konyine nk’uko OMS ibitangaza. Ni naho hapfuye umuganga w’umunyakameruni w’imyaka 41 y’amavuko wakoreraga OMS.
Ku wa Kane w’icyumweru dusoza umunyamakuru w’ijwi ry’Amerika mu mujyi wa Butembo yabonye impapuro zakwirakwijwe ku mihanda izindi zimanikwa ku mazu zihaniza uwo ari we wese wafasha abashinzwe kurwanya ebola. Izi nyandiko bivugwa ko zakwirakwijwe n’inyeshyamba za mai mai zari zanditse mu rurimi rw’igiswahili kandi zivuga ko abapolisi, abasirikare n’abandi bose bazafatanya n’abarwanya ebola bazibasirwa bikomeye.
Anderson Djumah ufite umwana w’imyaka 10 urimo kuvurirwa ebola ku bitaro bikuru bya Butembo yinubira kuba umutekano muke ukomeje gutuma abantu barushaho guteseka.
Minisiteri y’ubuzima ivuga ko abantu 1,600 ari bo basuzumwe Ebola, 1,534 ni bo bayanduye bidashidikanywaho mu gihe 66 bo bayiketsweho. Iyi ni imibare yagiye ahagaragara ku wa gatatu w’iki cyumweru gisatira umusozo. Iki cyorezo kimaze guhitana abantu 1,069 kandi ni icya kabili kibayeho kibi nyuma y’icyayogoje uburengerazuba bw’Afurika mu 2014-2015 cyahitanye abasaga 11,000.
Ebola ntiyari imenyerewe mu bice by’amajyarugu n’uburasirazuba bw’igihugu, ibice byabaye isibaniro ry’imirwano ahabarizwa imitwe y’abarwanyi igera mu 100; ikura ibihumbi by’abaturage mu byabo.
Urujya n’uruza kimwe n’ubucucike mu miturire muri utu duce, byongera ibyago by’uko iki cyorezo cyagera no muri Uganda, u Rwanda na Sudani y’Epfo.
OMS itanga inama yo gukomeza gutanga inkingo ku bwinshi no guhugura cyane abajyanama b’uhuzima.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3249124' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3249124.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yasubiye Kwiyadukiza muri Gineya
Abategetsi b’igihugu ca Liberiya bategetsi kw’urubibe n’igihugu kibanyi ca Gineya rwugarwa uno mjsi ku wa kabiri mu gihe hari impungenge zuko umugera wa Ebola ushobora gusubira kwaduka.
Umushikiranganji ajejwe gutangza amakuru wa Liberiya, Lenn Eugene Nangbe yabwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abongereza, Reuters, kw’iyugarwa ry’urubibe ari ingingo y’ugutuma indwara cya Ebola idakwiragira.
Yamenyesheje kw’urubibe ruzoguma rwugaye gushika ibintu bimere neza kurushiriza muri Gineya.
Nangbe yavuze ko Liberiya yarungitse kandi abnakozi bajejwe ubuvuzi mu bice abantu banijiriramwo ku rubibe n’igihugu ca Gineya.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, ryatangaje ko Ebola itakirangwa muri Gineya mu kwezi kw’icumi na kabiri mu mwaka uheze.
Yamara kw’italiki 17 z’ukwezi kwa gatatu, iryo shirahamwe ryaremeje kw’abantu babiri bashasha banduye Ebola mu mihana y’ahitwa Koropara muri Gineya, umuvyeyi n’umwana wiwe w’umuhungu w’imyaka itanu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2536867' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2536867.html' term='ebola'>
Uburayi Bwafashije u Burundi mu Kurwanya Ebola
Umuryango w’ubumwe bwa Bulaya wahaye guverinoma y’u Burundi amafaranga miliyoni 250 z’amarundi.
Iyo nkunga ni iyo gufasha Uburundi kwigisha abakozi bo mu buvuzi kurwanya ikiza Ebola n’ukurwanya ikiza ruhonyanganda Sida mu Burundi.
Umunyamakuru w'Ijwi ry'Amerika mu Burundi Tabitha Mukamusoni araduha ibisobanuro.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2506542' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/heza/2506542.html' term='ebola'>
Rwanda: Urubyiruko Rwumva Rute Ebola?
Urubyiruko rwo mu Rwanda rutangiye gusobanukirwa uko rwakwirinda icyorezo cya Ebola kigiye kumara umwaka kibasira ibihugu bitatu byo muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba.
Mu biganiro binyuranye abayobozi b'u Rwanda bageza ku baturage, ntibahwema kubasobanurira neza ibimenyetso by'icyo cyorezo ndetse n'uko bakwitwara mu gihe bumvise ko hari umuntu, yaba umuvndimwe, umuturange cyangwa se undi wese bazi yanduye Ebola.
Mu kiganiro cy'ububyiruko Heza gitegurwa n'Ijwi ry'Amerika, turumva uko bamwe mu rubyiruko babyumva.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4768146' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4768146.html' term='ebola'>
Urucanco Rurama rwa Ebola Rwoba Rwimirije Kuboneka
Abashakashatsi b’abanyamerika bariko bararondera urucanco rushasha kandi rurama rw’umugera utera Ebola. Ni mu gihe abantu barenga 700 barwaye, abarenga 400 barapfa muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo. Ibihugu bibanyi, Sudani yo mu bumanuko na Uganda bariko barafata ingingo zo gukinga ico kiza ntikibinjirane.
Dr. Paul Spearman, arongoye akagwi kari muri ubwo bushakashatsi ku bitaro vy’abana vyo mu gisagara ca Cincinnati muri reta ya Ohio, avuga ko mu gihe vyogaragara urwo rucanco rukora, rushobora kuzokoreshwa aho hose ico kiza kizokwaduka mu bihugu vya Afrika.
Ni mu gihe hari urundi rucanco rusanzwe ruriko rurakoreshwa mu gihugu ca Kongo. Abo bahinga bashikiriza ko bafise icizere ko mu gihe boronka urucanco rurama, bazoba baranduranye n’imizi Ebola muri Afrika.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4426483' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4426483.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Nta Bashasha Bandura Ebola muri RDC
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS ritangaza ko ata muntu mushasha arasubira kwibonekeza ko yanduye Ebola muri Republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo kuva kw’igenekerezo rya 17 z’ukwezi kwa gatanu.
Kugeza ubu, OMS yemeza ko abantu 25 aribo bamaze guhitanwa n’ico kiza.
Umuvugizi wa OMS, Tarik Jasarevic avuka ko atawokwijajara, kuko ngo ibiharuro vy’abanduye bishobora guhinduka bivanye n’uko hatazwi aboba barabonanye n’abari baranduye. Ati umuntu umwe yanduye Ebola ashobora kwanduza benshi bagiye barabonana mu manza canke amakoraniro nko mu masengero no ku maziko.
Jasarevic aremeza ko hari intambwe batewe mu gucandaga abantu babonanye n’abanduye.
Ebola yibonekeje incuro y’icenda muri Kongo kuva mu mwaka w’1970. Mu myaka itanu iheze, Ebola yishe abantu barenga ibihumbi 11 mu karere ka Afrika y’uburengero.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1264976' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/a-18-2007-12-10-voa2-93020554/1264976.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola ku Birometero Bitagera kuri 500 Uvuye ku Mupaka w'u Rwanda na Uganda
Ku italiki ya 10 z’ukwezi kwa 12 mu mwaka wa 2007, umunyamabanga wa Leta ushinzwe kurwanya SIDA n’ibindi byorezo, Dr. Nyaruhirira Innocent, yagiranye ikiganiro n’abanyamakuru ku vyerekeranye n’icyorezo ca Ebola. Yatangaje ko virus ya Ebola yagaragaye muri Uganda ari nshya, atari isanzwe. Yamenyesheje ko umuntu ashobora kuyimarana hagati y’iminsi 2 kugera kuri 21 yihishe mu mubiri w’umuntu.
Dr. Nyaruhirira yatangarije abanyamakuru ko indwara ya Ebola ubu iri ku birometero bitagera kuri 500 uvuye ku mupaka w’u Rwanda na Uganda. Gusa, yavuze ko nta muntu iragaragaraho mu Rwanda, kandi ko bitaraba ngombwa ko u Rwanda rufunga imipaka yarwo na Uganda.
Dr. Nyaruhirira yabwiye abanyamakuru ko ku mipaka ya Gatuna, Rubavu, Kagitumba na Cyanika hoherejwe ikipe z’abakozi bo kwa muganga babihuguwemo, kugira ngo bagenzure abinjira mu Rwanda, kandi bategure ahagenewe gushyirwa uwagaragayeho ibimenyesto bya Ebola.
Dr. Nyaruhirira yasobanuriye abanyamakuru ko mu gihugu cya Uganda Ebola imaze kugaragara mu turere twa Bundibugyo, Mbarara no mu mujyi wa Fort Portal. Abanyarwanda bakaba basabwa kugabanya ingendo mu bice byagaragayemo Ebola.
Dr. Nyaruhirira yavuze ko Ebola yabonetse muri Uganda iteye impungenge zikomeye u Rwanda. Kugeza ubu ubushakashatsi buracyari gukorwa kugira ngo hamenyekane aho itandukaniye n’iya mbere yabonetse muri Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo, ndetse no muri Sudani.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5335770' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/sierra-leone-yahagaritse-ingendo-z-indege-kubera-virusi-ya-corona-/5335770.html' term='ebola'>
Sierra Leone Yahagaritse Ingendo z'Indege Kubera Virusi ya Corona.
Sierra Leone yahagaritse ingendo kubera icyorezo cya Virusi ya Corona.
Mw’itangazo yakoze, minisiteri ishinzwe gutwara abantu n’ibintu, ya Sierra Leone, yavuze ko izo ngamba zizatangira kwubahiriza kuwa gatandatu kandi ko zizagumaho kugeza hagize ikindi gitangazwa. Ingendo za nkenerwa ni zo zizemererwa gukomeza.
Kugeza ubu, nta muntu wanduye Virusi ya Corona wari wavugwa muri Sierra Leone. Cyakora yabonetse mu bihugu bituranye, ari byo Guinee Bissau na Liberiya.
Sierra Leone yibasiwe bikomeye n’icyorezo cya Ebola mu 2014-2016, ubwo cyadukaga mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika. Icyo cyorezo cyatwaye ubuzima bw’abaturage bagera ku 4,000 muri icyo gihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4407667' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4407667.html' term='ebola'>
Babiri mu Banduye Ebola Bivanye mu Bitaro i Mbandaka Barapfuye
Abantu batatu bari baranduye umugera wa Ebola barikuye mu bitaro batarekuwe n’abaganga bo mu bitaro vy’i Mbandaka muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, ivyo vyatangajwe n’umwe mu bakuru b’umuryango w’abaganga batagira imbibe, Médecins sans frontières, kuri uyu wa gatatu.
Henry Gray, atunganya ibikorwa vyo gufasha abanduye Ebola muri MSF i Mbandaka yavuze ko abo bantu bavuye mu bitaro vy’i Wangata hagati yo ku musi w’Imana no kuwa gatatu. Babiri muri bo baramaze gupfa.
Gray avuga ko kuva ivyo bibaye, hariko harakorwa ibishoboka kugira bumvishe abarwayi ndetse n’imiryango yabo kutava mu bigo vy’ubuvuzi bakoranirijwemwo kugira babandanye bavurwa.
Ikiza ca Ebola cagaragaye kw’itariki ya munani z’ukwezi kwa gatanu mu gace ka Bikoro, ku birometero 100 uva mu gisagara ca Mbandaka hamwe n’ibirometero 600 uva ku murwa mukuru Kinshasa.
Ibitigiri vy’abamaze gupfa bishika kuri 27, kuri 58 bagaragaye ko banduye canke bakekwa kuba baranduye, nkuko OMS ryabishikirije ku musi wa gatatu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2689418' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2689418.html' term='ebola'>
Muri Liberia, Ebola Yarasubiye Kwandukira Umunyagihugu
Iyo ngwara isubiye kwduka, inyuma y’indwi zitari nke, zari ziheze ico kiza kitavugwa. Bavuga kandi kw’uyo muntu yaciye atwarwa mw’ivuriro riri ku murwa mukuru Monrovia.
Abajejwe amagara y’abantu mu gihugu ca Liberia, bari bahaye uruhusha rwo kuva mu bitaro umugwayi wa nyuma w’ingwara ya Ebola kw’igenekerezo rya 5 ry’ukwezi kwa gatatu, arinavyo vyari vyatanze akizero kw’ico kiza catujijwe mu gihugu ca Liberia.
Ibihugu bitegerezwa kurindira imisi 42 imbere y’uko umurwayi wa nyuma w’ingwara ya Ebola asubiye gupimwa bagasanga ata ngwara ya Ebola afise.
Igihugu ca Liberia nico casinzikajwe cane n’ikiza ca Ebola, cadutse cane cane mu bihugu vyo muri Afrika yo mu burengero.
Abantu barenga ibihumbi 10 nibo bamaze kwicwa n’ico kiza, kandi benshi baba mu bihugu vyo muri Afrika yo mu burengero, birimwo Liberia, Guinee na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1264960' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/a-18-2007-12-05-voa2-93020449/1264960.html' term='ebola'>
Icyorezo cy’Indwara ya Ebola muri Uganda
Icyorezo cya Ebola kimaze iminsi kivugwa mu burengerazuba bwa Uganda, hafi ya Republika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo. Ubu noneho iyo ndwara ya Ebola irimo gusatira amajyepfo mu karere ka Mbarara, hafi y’u Rwanda.
Iyo ndwara mbi iterwa na virusi, ntikunze kugira umuti, nta n’urukingo, kandi ihitana hagati y’ibice 50 na 90 ku ijana by’abantu banduye virusi yayo. Yica vuba, kandi irandura cyane. Ibyo ni bimwe mubyo twasobanuliwe na Docteur Innocent Nyaruhirira, umunyamabanga wa leta muri ministeri y’ubuzima, ushinzwe kurwanya Sida n’izindi ndwara z’ibyorezo.
Docteur Nyaruhirira yanadusobanuliye ingamba zahise zifatwa mu kurinda abaturarwanda kuba bakwandura iyo ndwara ya Ebola.
Ibisobanuro birambuye murabisanga mu kiganiro cy’umuryango, Docteur Innocent Nyaruhirira yagiranye na Eugenie Mukankusi
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2519104' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2519104.html' term='ebola'>
MSF Izagerageza Imiti ya Ebola ku barwayi muri Afurika y'Uburengerazuba
Prezida wa Liberia Ellen Johnson Sirleaf, yahagaritse amabwiriza y’ibihe bikomeye, yari yashyizeho kubera icyorezo cya Ebola mu gihugu.
Mu ijambo yavuze taliki ya 13 y'ukwa 11 muri 2014, madame Sirleaf, yasobanuye ko urugamba ku ndwara ya Ebola rutari rwahagarara kandi ko zimwe mu nzitizi zikiriho.
Yavuze ati, kugeza intego y’igihugu yo kutagira umuntu n’umwe urwaye Ebola, mbere ya Noheli, izaba itaragerwaho, mu mpande zose z’isi, tuzakomeza kugendera ku ngamba zariho mbere, tureba aho twadohora bijyanye n’ibyo tuzaba tumaze kugeraho mu rugamba rwacu.
Prezida wa Liberia yavuze ko, amasoko ashobora kwongera gufungura imiryango, kandi ko amasaha y’umukwabu yigijwe inyuma, saa sita z’ijoro mu turere tutarimo indwara ya Ebola. Madame Sirleaf yavuze ko muri komini 10 kuri 15, nta muntu wagaragayeho ebola kuva ku cyumweru.
Hagati aha, ishyirahamwe ry’abaganga batagira imipaka, Medecins Sans Frontiers, rirateganya gutangira kugerageza imiti itatu ya Ebola mu burengerazuba bwa Afurika, kugira ngo barebe uzarusha iyindi guhangana na Ebola.
Iryo shyirahamwe ivuga ko yizeye kuzatangira kugerageza iyo miti, mu kwezi gutaha, ibizavamo bikazamenyekana ahagana mu ntangiriro z’ukwezi kwa kabiri muri 2015.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5000823' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/babiri-bakora-mu-gisata-co-gukinga-ebola-muri-kongo-bishwe-/5000823.html' term='ebola'>
Babiri Bakora mu Gisata co Gukinga Ebola muri Kongo Bishwe
Ministeri y’ubuzima muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo yatangaje ko abakozi bayo babiri bakoraga mu byo gukumira icyorezo cya Ebola biciwe mu burasirazuba bw’icyo gihugu mu ntara ya Kivu y’amajyaruguru. Hari hashize amezi baterwa ubwoba.
Abakozi ba ministeri y’ubuzima kandi batangaje ko umurwayi wa Ebola yagaragaye bwa mbere mu mugi wa Goma hafi y’umupaka icyo gihugu gihana n’u Rwanda. Uwo mugi utuwe n’abantu barenga miliyoni 2.
Abategetsi bavuze ko umurwayi basanze yaranduye iyo ndwara ari umu pasitoro wari waje muri bisi ivuye i Butembo, umwe mu migi yazahajwe na Ebola. Yageze i Goma ku cyumweru bahita bamujyana aho bavurira abanduye indwara ya Ebola.
Abashinzwe inzego z’ubuzima muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo baravuga ko uwo murwayi yahise amenyekana kandi n’abo bazanye mu modoka bakaba bazwi, impungenge ko iyo ndwara yakwirakwira mu mugi wa Goma zagabanutse.
Ibiro ntaramakuru by’Abafaransa byatangaje ko umushoferi w’iyo bisi n’abandi bagenzi bari bayirimo bahawe inkingo za Ebola kuri uyu wa mbere
Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 1600 muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo. Ingamba zo kuyirinda zakomeje gukomwa mu nkokora n’ubugizi bwa nabi bukorerwa abakozi bo mu rwego rw’ubuzima. Hari na bamwe mu baturage badakurikiza amabwiriza yo kujyana abo mu miryango yabo abanduye iyi ndwara kwa muganga cyangwa kudakurikiza amabwiriza yagenwe mu gushyingura abahitanywe n’iyi ndwara.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4404966' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4404966.html' term='ebola'>
Urukingo rwa Ebola Rurakora Neza
Hatagize igikorwa, icyorezo cy’indwara ya Ebola gishobora kurushaho guhitana abantu benshi muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo kurenza uko byagenze mu burengerazuba bw’Afurika.
Icyakora abashinzwe ibikorwa by’ubutabazi bavuga ko amahirwe bafite muri iyi minsi ari uko bafite inkingo batari bafite mu mwaka wa 2013 ubwo muri Gineya hadukaga icyo cyorezo bwa mbere.
Sosiyete ikora imiti yo muri Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika yitwa Merck imaze kohereza inkingo zirenga 8,000 zo mu bwoko bwa V920 kugirango zigeragezwe mu ntara ya Equateur muri Kongo. Izo nkingo zizatangwa n’abakozi b’ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS.
Muganga Benjamin Djoudalbaye ukora mu kigo nyafurika gishinzwe gukumira indwara yabwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika ko inkingo zonyine zidahagije ko bakeneye n’imiti yo guha abanduye iyo ndwara.
Mu cyumweru gishize umuryango w'Afurika y’Uburasirazuba watangaje ko wahagurukiye ibikorwa byo kwitegura kugirango wirinde indwara ya Ebola ntiyinjire mu bihugu biwugize.
Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo ihana imbibi n’ibihugu bitanu kuri bitandatu bigize uwo muryango w'Afurika y’Uburasirazuba.
Ibyo bihugu bisanzwe bikorana ubuhahirane ndetse n’urujya n’uruza hagati y’abaturage babituye. Kugeza ubu, nta bihe bidasanzwe biratangazwa muri Kongo.
Abamaze guhitanwa na Ebola muri Kongo barenga 25.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2493980' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2493980.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Gucunga Abagenzi Baturutse mu Bihugu Birimo Ebola
Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, ryiteguye kuvugana n’abanyamakuru kuri uyu wa kane, nyuma y’inama isuzuma ibimaze gukorwa mu kurwanya icyorezo cya Ebola.
Komite y’ubutabazi bwihutirwa ya OMS kuri Ebola, yatangiye inama ejo kuwa gatatu. Iyi komite kandi irimo gusuzuma niba yahindura inama zatanzwe mu guhangana n’icyorezo cya Ebola.
Abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi 9,900 bemejweho indwara ya Ebola, hamwe n’abashobora kuba barayanduye n’abakekwaho iyi ndwara. Abenshi ni abo muri Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone.
Abayobozi bashinzwe ubuzima muri Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika, bategeka abantu baturuka muri ibyo bihugu, gucunga ubuzima bwabo iminsi 21, bagaha departema ishinzwe ubuzima mu karere, amakuru buri munsi, ku muriro bifashe cyangwa se niba bafite ikimenyetso na kimwe mu biranga indwara ya Ebola.
Iyo programu yo gucunga abarwayi, izatangirira kuwa mbere muri leta esheshatu zo mu burazirazuba bwa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika. Izo ni Georgia, Maryland, New Jersey, New York, Pennyslvania na Virginia, aho abenshi muri abo bagenzi bakunze kugenderera.
Bakigera ku bibuga by’indege, bazajya bahabwa ibikoresho byo kwipima Ebola, birimo ibyo gufatisha umuriro.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4719958' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4719958.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Prezida Kabila Yemeza ko Ata Mpamvu Yohagarika Amatora
Prezida wa Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo, Joseph Kabila, avuga ko ata zindi mpamvu zihari zotuma amatora y’umukuru w’igihugu yo ku musi w’Imana ataba.
Ivyo ni inyuma yuko amatora asibishijwe mu kiringo c’imyaka ibiri. Yamara Prezida Kabila asigura ko ingingo yo ku munuta wa nyuma y’ukwigizayo amatora mu turere twa Beni na Butembo yatumwe n’ukwiyadukiza kw’ikiza ca Ebola.
Mu kiganiro yagiranye n’iterorokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’abanyamerika, Associated Press, Prezida Kabila yavuze hamwe abanyagihugu muri ivyo bice bibiri vyasinzikajwe n’ikiza ca Ebola botora ku musi w’Imana, ivyo vyogira inkurikizi zikomeye cane. Avuga ko umuntu umwe ashobora kwanduza abandi bantu amajana n’amajana.
Ivyatangajwe na Prezida Kabila ku musi wa kane ku muhingamo vyari bitandukanye n’ivyamenyeshejwe n’abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu. Batangaje ko ingingo zafashwe babifashijwemwo n’abategetsi bajejwe amatora kugira abantu bashobore gutora mu turere twa Beni na Butembo.
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryitaho amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, naryo nyene ryatangaje ko ingingo zafashwe mu gukaraba hakoreshejwe isabuni ikura imicafu mu ntoke hamwe n’ugusuzuma abatora bose bazoba bariko binjira mu bibanza vy’amatora.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4584960' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/kongo-abagera-kuri-18-baraguye-mu-mirwano-ya-adf-/4584960.html' term='ebola'>
Kongo: Abagera kuri 18 Baraguye mu Mirwano ya ADF
Radiyo Okapi muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo itangaza ko abantu 18 bapfuye mu bitero vy’abikekwa ko ari abarwanya ubutegetsi bwa Uganda, Allied Democratic Forces, ADF, mu mpunyapfunyo. Ivyo bitero vyabereye mu gisagara ca Beni kiri mu buseruko bw’igihugu. Ivyo ni mu gihe ako karere kabandanya kugeramirwa n’ikiza ca Ebola.
Radiyo Okapi, ishigikiwe n’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU, yatangaje ku musi w’Imana kw’abasivile 14 n’abasirikare 4 bishwe mu bitero vyabaye ku musi wa gatandatu w’iyi ndwi turangije mu karere ka Beni.
Abarwanya ubutegetsi bw’igihugu ca Uganda bo mu murwi ADF, bateye ikirindiro c’igisirikare ca Reta muri ako karere. Radiyo Okapi ivuga kandi ibibanza vy’ukudandarizamwo mw’isoko yo muri ako karere vyasahuwe n’abikekwa ko ari abarwanyi b’umurwi ADF.
Ibitero nk'ivyo birabangamira utwigoro tw’ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola. Abantu 118 baranduye Ebola, 69 bakaba bamaze guhitanwa n’ico kiza.
Abantu barenga 10.000 baramaze gukingirwa Ebola muri Kongo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4946299' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4946299.html' term='ebola'>
Abanduye Ebola Barashitse ku 2000 muri RDC
Abantu barenga 2000 baranduye ikiza ca Ebola muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, nkuko vyatangajwe n’umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu w’ico gihugu. Abantu 1,346 bapfuye batumye ico gihugu kija ku mwanya wa kabiri ku bantu bishwe na Ebola muri kahise k’isi.
Ku musi wa mbere, uwo mushikiranganji yavuze ko abantu 539 bavuwe barakira uwo mugera.
Uwo mushikiranganji avuga ko kurwanya Ebola vyafashijwe n’umutekano wiyongereye.
Kubw’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa, AFP, abakozi batanu bari mu bafasha kurwanya ico kiza barishwe n’imihari yitwaje ibirwanisho.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2529880' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2529880.html' term='ebola'>
ONU: Nta Ebola muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo
Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, ryatangaje ko nta Ebola ikirangwa muri Republika Iharanira Demokrasi ya Congo. Icyo cyorezo kidafite aho gihuriye n’icyibasiye uburengerazuba bwa Afrika, cyari cyibanze mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Congo mu ntara ya Equateur, kandi cyahitanye abantu 49.
Mw'itangazo ry’Ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, kuri uyu wa gatanu, yavuze ko hashize iminsi 42, n’ukuvuga iminsi ikubye kabiri, iminsi virusi ya Ebola igaragazamo ibimenyetso, nta muntu n’umwe ubonetseho Ebola muri Republika iharanira Demokrasi ya Congo. Ibyo OMS yatangaje byaje byemeza itangazo rya guverinema ya Republika Iharanira Demokrasi ya Congo, ryo mu cyumweru gishize ko iby’icyo cyorezo ari amateka.
Hagati aha, umuganga wo mu gihugu cya Mali, yishwe na Ebola, nyuma yo kuvura umurwayi waje guhitanwa na Ebola.Kugeza ubu Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 7 muri Mali.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2536793' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2536793.html' term='ebola'>
Nta Ngaruka Mbi Urukingo rwa Ebola Rwagize ku Bantu
Abashakashatsi bavuga ko urukingo rwa Ebola rugeragezwa rutagize ingaruka mbi ku bantu 20 baruhawe ku bushake bwabo.
Akanyamakuru "The New England Journal of Medicine" taliki ya 26 y'ukwa 11 mu mwaka wa 2014 kavuze ko abahanga bazakomeza gukurikirana abo bantu mu gihe cy’ibyumweru 48. Igeragezwa ry'urwo rukingo ryatangiye taliki ya kabiri y’ukwezi kwa cyenda.
Intego igamijwe mu kugerageza urwo rukingo rukorwa n’isosiyete GlaxoSmithKline yo mu Bwongereza ni ukureba niba rufite ubuziranenge.
Inkuru y’uko urwo rukingo rudafite ingaruka yatangajwe umunsi umwe nyuma y’uko ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS ryari ryatangaje ko, icyorezo cya Ebola kibasiye Afurika y’uburengerazuba, kimaze guhitana abantu hafi 5,700, kuri 16,000 bari bayanduye.
Iyo sosiyete GlaxoSmit Kline kandi imaze igihe ifatanya n’Ikigo cy’Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima, NIH, mu gukora urundi rukiko rwa Ebola iboneka gusa muri Republika iharnaira demokrasi ya Kongo. Ubu urwo rukingo rurimo kugeragezwa mu Bwongereza, muri Mali no mu Busuwisi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5013582' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/leta-ya-kongo-ntigitanga-amakuru-kuri-ebola/5013582.html' term='ebola'>
Leta ya Kongo Ntigitanga Amakuru kuri Ebola
Muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo, ibitangazamakuru byaramutse byinubira ko bitagihabwa amakuru ku cyorezo cya Ebola cyayogoje uburasirazuba bw’igihugu.
Ubusanzwe, minisiteri y’ubuzima yoherezaga e-mail ivuga uko byifashe buri munsi. Iyo imeyeli yohererezwaga ibitangazamakuru, inzego za leta zitandukanye, inzego n’imiryango mpuzamahanga bafite uruhare mu rugamba rwo kurwanya Ebola. Ariko kuva minisitiri w’ubuzima, Oly Ilunga, asezeye aya makuru ntagitangwa.
Dr Ilunda yeguye ejobundi kuwa mbere nyuma y’icyemezo cya perezida wa Repubulika, Félix Tshisekedi, cyo gushyira ibikorwa byose byo kurwanya Ebola mu maboko ye bwite.
Ubutumwa bwa imeyeli ya nyuma ya minisiteri y’ubuzima yagiye kuwa mbere. Yavugaga ko kuva mu kwezi kwa munani gushize, Ebola yari imaze guhitana abantu 1743, n’abandi 729 bayikize neza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5049115' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5049115.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Umwana w'Imyaka 7 Yishwe na Ebola muri Teritware ya Mwenga
Abategetsi muvy’amagara y’abantu muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo bashikirije kuri uyu wa mbere ko hagaragaye uwundi yishwe na Ebola mu ntara ya kivu y’ubumanuko, abaye uwugira gatatu mu buseruko bwa Congo.
Umwana w’imyaka indwi yarapfuye kuw’Imana yishwe na Ebola, hafi ya Chowe, muri Teritware ya Mwenga, nkuko vyashikirijwe na muganga Claude Bahizire, ajejwe gutangaza amakuru mu ntara y’ubuvuzi mu bumanuko bwa Kivu y’Ubumanuko.
Yongeye avuga ko abandi bagore babiri bakiriwe mu bitaro i Bukavu, ku murwa mukuru wa Kivu y’ubumanuko bafise ibimenyetso vya Ebola.
Haraheze umwaka, Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 1.934 abandi 862 barakira, nkuko ibiharuro vyatangajwe n’abategetsi mu binyamakuru ku musi w’Imana.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5041398' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5041398.html' term='ebola'>
Umuvyeyi n'Umwana Wiwe Batabarutse Ebola muri RDC Barishima
Inyuma y’imisi 29 bari mu kigo gikurikirana abanduye Ebola mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo, kandi barwana n’ubuzima, umuvyeyi hamwe n’umwana wiwe baratahutse ku musi wa kabiri bakize n’umunezero ntangere.
Esperance Nabintu n’umuhungu wiwe w’umwaka umwe Ebenezer Fataki, barishimwa kubona barokotse ico kiza cahitanye umugabo akaba na se w’umwana wiwe.
Bari mu bantu barenga 2,800 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye Ebola imaze guhitana abashika 1,900 kuva yadutse haraheze umwaka, mu buseruko bwa Kongo.
Uwo muvyeyi hamwe n’umwana batahutse inyuma y’aho abahinga batangarije ku musi wa mbere ko imiti ibiri bageragereje muri Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika yerekanye ko ivura Ebola kandi ko igiye guhabwa abarwayi bose ba Ebola muri Kongo.
Ariko Ntibiramenyekana umuti wakoreshejwe mu kuvura uwo muvyeyi n’umwana.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4855889' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4855889.html' term='ebola'>
Beni-Butembo na Yumbi nabo Batoye
Muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo, abaturage barenga miliyoni ba Beni-Butembo na Yumbi nabo noneho batoye kuri iki cyumweru.
I Beni-Butembo, mu ntara ya Kivu ya ruguru, mu burasirazuba bw’igihugu, ntibari bashoboye gutora ku italiki ya 30 y’ukwa 12 gushize kubera icyorezo cya Ebola.
Naho i Yumbi, mu majyepfo y’uburengerazuba bwa Congo, ntibari bashoboye gutora mu kwa 12 kubera ubwicanyi bukomeye bwabaye hagati y’amoko y’aba-Banunu n’aba-Butende ku italiki 16 na 17 z’ukwezi kwa 12 bwahitanye abantu amagana.
Kuri iki cyumweru, i Beni-Butembo n’i Yumbi batoye abadepite n’abayobozi b’inzego z’ibanze gusa. Ntibatoye umukuru w’igihugu. Ntacyo byari bimaze kubera ko Urukiko rurengera itegeko nshinga rya Congo rwarangije kwemeza burundu ko Félix Tshisekedi yayatsinze. Tshisekedi yarahiye kuri 24 y’ukwa mbere gushize.
Abadepite 15 bose hamwe batorwa kuri iki cyumweru nabo ntacyo bahindura mu nteko ishinga amategeko nshya kuko amashyaka y’abayoboke ba perezida wa Repubulika wacyuye igihe, Joseph Kabila, bafitemo ubwiganze busesuye cyane.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5221173' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/msf-yahagaritse-ibikorwa-vyayo-vyo-kurwanya-ebola-muri-kongo-/5221173.html' term='ebola'>
MSF Yahagaritse Ibikorwa Vyayo vyo Kurwanya Ebola muri Kongo
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ry’abaganga batagira imbibe,MSF (Médecins Sans Frontières), ritangaza ko ryahagaritse ibikorwa vyaryo vyo kugwanya ikiza ca Ebola mu karere k’ubuseruko bwa Republika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo.
MSF isigura ko yafashe iyo ngingo kubera hari imigwi y’abasirikare ba Reta ku mavuriro yaryo. Iryo shirahamwe risigura ko ivyo biteye kubiri n’amategeko yabo avuga ko bategerezwa gukora ataho begamiye kandi ata macakubiri bagira mu bikorwa vyabo.
Umuyobozi mu biro vy’imigambi n’ibikogwa vyihuta Trish Newport muri iryo shirahamwe yabwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika ko ikibazo kihari catanguye kwibonekeza mu mpera z’ukwezi kwa cumi na rimwe inyuma y’ibitero vyagizwe n’abantu bitwaje ibigwanisho.
Muri ivyo bitero harishwe abaganga batatu harakomereka abandi batari bake. Inyuma y’ico gitero Reta ya Kongo yaciye irungika abajejwe umutekano muri ako karere gucungera iryo vuriro.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4614229' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4614229.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Izakoresha Inama Yihutirwa kuri Ebola muri Kongo
Kuri 17 y’uku kwezi OMS izakoreshereza i Geneve mu Busuwisi inama kuri Ebola yugarije Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo. Kuva mu kwezi kwa munani gushize, Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 135 mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru.
Inama igomba kwemeza niba ari icyorezo cyugarije isi, nk’uko byabaye mu 2014 ubwo Ebola yahitanaga abantu barenga ibihumbi 11 na 300 muri Guinée, Liberia na Sierra Leone muri Afrika y’uburengerazuba no ku cyorezo cya Zika mu 2016 muri Amerika y’Epfo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5022831' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5022831.html' term='ebola'>
Uwugira Kabiri Yamenyekanye ko Yanduye Ebola i Goma
Abategetsi muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo bemeje ko umuntu agira kabiri yamenyekanye ko yanduye umugera wa Ebola mu gisagara ca Goma.
Dogiteri Aruna Abedi ajejwe gutunganya ibikorwa vyo kurwanya Ebola mu ntara ya Kivu y’uburaruko ni we yabibwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa, AFP ejo kuwa kabiri.
Goma ni igisagara kibamwo abantu barenga umuriyoni kandi gihana urubibe n’u Rwanda, aho abantu baharurwa mu bihumbi b’ivyo bihugu bibiri bajabuka n’amaguru ku musi ku musi.
Uwo muntu agira kabiri yafashwe yinjiye muri Goma avuye mu ntara ya Ituri.
Mu ntango z’uku kwezi. Umupasitori yasuzumwe ko yanduye Ebola inyuma y’aho ashikiye i Goma na bus, bituma haba ubwoba ko ishobora kwandukira abantu ningoga kubwo ubwinshi bw’abantu baba muri ico gisagara.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4934331' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/hishwe-undi-mukozi-mu-bahanganye-n-icyorezo-cya-ebola-muri-congo-/4934331.html' term='ebola'>
Hishwe Undi Mukozi mu Bahanganye n’Icyorezo cya Ebola muri Congo
Abaturage bishe umukozi wo mu buvuzi mu burasirazuba bwa Repuburika Iharanira demokarasi ya congo.
Uwo mukozi yari umwe mu bahanganye n’icyorezo cya Ebola. Abo baturage basahuye ikigo kivurirwamo iyo ndwara. Ibi biri muri raporo, ibiro ntaramakuru by’Abafaransa byabonye kuri uyu wa mbere.
Abatuye umudugudu wa Vusahiro mu karere k’ubuzima ka Mabalako mu ntara ya Kivu y’amajyaruguru barahagurutse kuwa gatandatu batera itsinda ry’abakozi barwanya Ebola. Ibyo byasohotse mu nyandiko yo ku cyumweru ya minisiteri y’ubuzima mu gihugu.
Ivuga ko umukozi mw’itsinda rishinzwe isuku mu rwego rwo kurwanya no guhagarika ubwandu bwa Ebola yapfuye arimo kujyanwa ku bitaro amaze gukomeretswa.
Ikigo cy’ubuzima cya Vusahiro cyarasahuwe gisigara kimeze nk’ahantu hajugunywa imyanda. Amazu atatu nayo mu mudugudu yarahiye arakongoka.
Mu kindi gitero, ikigo cya Valumba gisuzumirwamo indwara ya Ebola, mu ntara y’ubuzima ya Butembo cyarasahuwe ibintu biramenagurwa mw’ijoro ryo kuwa gatandatu rishyira ku cyumweru.
Icyorezo cya Ebola cyatangajwe mu burasirazuba bwa Congo mu kwezi kwa 8 kw’umwaka ushize. Cyahitanye abantu barenga 1,200 mu ntara ebyiri. Izo ni Ituri na Kivu y’amajyaruguru.
Mu byumweru bishize kandi abandi, abandi bantu baranduye.
Ibikorwa byo kurwanya icyo cyorezo, byatambamiwe n’ibitero by’abarwanyi ku bigo by’ubuvuzi, aho bamwe mu bakozi biciwe. Bishwe na bamwe mu baturage badashaka amatsinda ry’ubuvuzi. Kuva icyo gihe, ibitero byahitanye abantu bane. Abandi babarirwa muri mirongo barakomeretse, barimo n’abarwayi nk’uko minisiteri y’ubuzima yabitangaje kuwa gatanu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4586320' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/oms-ebola-ishobora-gusubira-kwaduka-muri-kongo-/4586320.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola Ishobora Gusubira Kwaduka muri Kongo
Igisata ca OMS kijejwe gukinga ingwara z'ivyaduka n'izisaba kwitabwaho bidatevye kigabisha ko ikiza ca Ebola gishobora gusubira gushinga imizi muri Kongo.
Muganga Peter Salama ajejwe ico gisata muri iryo shami rya ONU ryitaho amagara y'abantu kw'isi, OMS, asigura ko umutekano muke, abanyagihugu batemera ko bacandagwa n'abanyepolitike batera ubwoba abanyagihugu ku vyerekeye incanco ari muri bimwe bishobora gutuma Ebola yongera gutera Kongo.
Naho OMS ishima intambwe igezeko mu kurwanya Ebola mu buseruko bw’intara ya Kivu yo mu buraruko, yemeza ko izo ntambamyi co kimwe n'ibihe vy'amatora vyimirije bishobora kuyiciramwo.
Ibiharuro vya nyuma vyatangajwe n'abajejwe amagara y'abanyu muri ico gihugu vyemeza ko ico kiza aho giheruka cahitanye abagera kw' i 100 muri 150 bari bacanduye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2521944' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2521944.html' term='ebola'>
Nta Ebola Ikibazwa, muri Republika Iharanira Demaokrasi ya Congo
Republika iharanira Demokrasi ya Congo, yatangaje kw’ata Ebola ikiri mu gihugu, inyuma yuko ukwiyadukiza kwa Ebola, muri ico gihugu, mu kwezi kw’umunani, guhitanye abantu bagera, kuri mirongo itanu.
Ivyo umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Republika iharanira Demokrasi ya Congo, Felix Kabange Numbi, yabitangaje, ku musi wa gatandatu, yamara yaragabishije kw’ukurangira kw’iyo ndwara, atari ukuvuga kw’igihugu cogoroye burundu.
Numbi, yavuze ko Republika iharanira Demokrasi ya Congo, yageramiwe n’ubwoko bw’umugera wa Ebola, utandukanye n’uwuriko ugeramira ibihugu vya Guinee, Liberia na Sierra Leone, ishobora kwandukirwa n’ubwoko bwa Ebola, bwo muri Afrika yo mu burengero bwahitanye abantu barenga ibihumbi bitanu.
Muri ico gihe, umuganga yanduye Ebola, mu gihugu ciwe c’amavuko, ca Sierra Leone, yarashitse mu gisagara ca Omaha, mu ntara ya Nebraska, muri Amerika, kugira avurwe. Docteur, Martin Salia, aba muri Reta ya Maryland, yubakanye n’umunyamerikakazi, yari amaze igihe akora nk’umuganga mukuru, mu bitaro vyo ku murwa mukuru wa Sierra Leone, Freetown, igihe vyibonekeza ko yanduye Ebola. Azovurirwa mu bitaro, Nebraska Medical Center, bimwe mu bitaro bitari bike, bifise uburyo bw’ukuvura abantu bafise Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2492230' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2492230.html' term='ebola'>
Gukumira Ebola Bishobora Gufata Amezi Atandatu
Umuyobozi mukuru w’umuryango utabara imbabare Croix Rouge yavuze ko gukumira icyorezo cya Ebola kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 4,500 bishobora gufata hagati y’amezi 4-6, ingamba nyazo ziramutse zikurikijwe.
Mu kiganiro yahaye abanyamakuru ari mu Bushinwa, Elhadj As Sy yavuze ko abakekwaho iyo ndwara bakwiye gushyirwa mu kato, abanduye bakavurwa, abapfuye nabo bagashyingurwa hakurikijwe uburyo bwagenwe budatuma abashyigura bandura iyo ndwara.
Ibi bwana Sy abivuze mu gihe ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS, riri mu nama yo kwiga ingamba nshya zo kwirinda no gukumira icyoreza cya Ebola.
Hagati aho, sosiyete ikora imiti ya Johnson & Johnson yo muri Amerika yatangaje ko ifatanyije n'indi yitwa Bavarian Nordic yo muri Danemark barimo gukora urukingo rwa Ebola bakeka ko bazakorera igerageza mu kwezi kwa mbere k’umwaka utaha.
Iyi sosiyete ivuga ko imaze gushora miliyoni 200 z’amadolari mu bushakashatsi kuri Ebola.
Kuri uyu wa kabiri, OMS yatangaje ko urukingo rwa Ebola rushobora kuzaba rwabonetse muri uku kwa mbere.
Umuyobozi wungirije wa OMS Marie Paul Kieny yavuzeko igeragezwa rw’urwo rukingo ririmo gukorwa muri Amerika, ku mugabane w’Uburayi n’Afurika. Yavuze ko nibasanga urwo rukingo rukora, ruzatangira kugeragezwa ku bantu muri Afurika y’uburengerazuba mu kwezi kwa mbere k'umwaka utaha.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5013542' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5013542.html' term='ebola'>
Abarwanyi ba ADF Baba Barishe Abantu 12 mu Ntara ya Ituri
Abikekwa ko ari abarwanya ubutegetsi bwa Uganda bo mu murwi, “Allied Democratic Forces” mu mpfunyapfunyo, ADF, bishe abantu 12 mu bitero bibiri vyabereye mu karere ko mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo. Aka ni akarere kageramiwe n’ikiza ca Ebola.
Abikekwa ko ari abarwanya ubutegetsi mu murwi ADF, batereye ica rimwe ibisagara vya Eringeti na Oicha ku musi wa mbere w’iyi ndwi mu karere ka Beni. Umuyobozi w’akarere ka Beni, Kasereka Donat, avuga ko bishe abantu 9 mu gisagara ca Eringeti n’abantu 3 mu gisagara ca Oicha Donat. Amenyesha ko naho abasirikare batari bake ba Reta ya Kongo barungitswe muri ako karere, abanyagihugu baho batekewe n’ubwoba bwinshi kubera ivyo bitero.
Kuva mu kwezi guheze, Reta ya Kiyislamu yariyitiriye ibitero vyakozwe n’abarwanyi b’umurwi ADF. Yamara imigenderanire hagati y’iyo mirwi ibiri ntitomoye.
Umurwi ADF n’iyindi mirwi yitwaje ibirwanisho ikorera mu karere ko mu buseruko bwa Kongo yarageramiye bikomeye utwigoro tw’ukurwanya ikiza ca Ebola muri ako karere.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5023244' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5023244.html' term='ebola'>
Umuntu wa Kabiri Wanduye Ebola Yitavye Imana i Goma
Abategetsi ba Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo batangaza ko umuntu agira kabiri yanduye umugera w’indwara ya Ebola mu gisagara ca Goma yitavye Imana mu gitondo c’uno musi ku wa gatatu. Ni umusi umwe inyuma y’uko bitangajwe ko yanduye Ebola.
Uwo muntu ari mu myaka ya 40 yacukura ubutare yari yatahutse imuhira iwe avuye mu karere k’intara ya Ituri iri mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Kongo. Nta muntu yari azi ko afise Ebola muri ako karere.
Abategetsi b’ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, bavuga ko uwo muntu ashobora kuba yanduye Ebola hagati y’ahitwa Komanda n’igisagara ca Goma. Yafashe amapikipiki y’amatagisi mu kiringo c’imisi itari mike mu karere karimwo abantu benshi aho ikiza ca Ebola gikomeye cane.
Uwo muntu yashitse mu gisagara ca Goma kw’italiki 13 z’ukwezi kw’indwi. Yatanguye kwerekana ibimenyetso vya Ebola kuwa mbere w’indwi iheze yashizwe mu kibanza ciwe ca wenyene mu kibanza abantu bajejwe kuvurirwamwo Ebola ku musi wa kabiri. Yari yamaze imisi 5 avurirwa imuhira iwe, mu nyuma yaho aja mu kibanza c’ubuvuzi aho yiketswe ko afise Ebola.
Avurwa ko ashobora kuba atari azi ko yanduye Ebola. Abantu bamwegereye bariko bararonderwa kugira bahabwe urucandago rwa Ebola ruriko rurageragezwa muri iki gihe.
Abantu bashobora kwitiranya ibimenyetso vy’umuriro mwinshi mu mubiri uterwa na Ebola n’indwara ya Malariya. Akarere ko mu buseruko bwa Kongo ni akarere kasinzikajwe na Malariya.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5184986' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5184986.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Yemeje ko Abakozi Batatu Bayo Bishywe muri Kongo
Abategetsi mw’ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, bavuga ko abakozi batatu bishwe, kandi ko abandi benshi bakomerekeye mu gitero cyagabwe ku bigo by’abarwanya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Kongo.
OMS ivuga ko abo bakozi bahitanywe n’igitero, abarwanyi b’aba mai mai bagabye ku bigo by’ubuzima bya ONU kuri uyu wa kane i Biakato. Ni mu ntara ya Ituri aho abakozi bahanganye na Ebola baba. Umwe mu bantu bahatuye nawe yishwe. OMS isobanura ko igitero cyo mu mujyi wa Mangina mu ntara ya Ituri, cyasubijwe inyuma.
Mu butumwa ku rubuga rwa Twiter, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yumvikanishije akababaro gatewe n’abatakaje ubuzima. Yavuze ko icyo batinyaga kibaye. Avuga ko bagiye gushyira ingufu mu kwita ku bakomeretse no gukora ku buryo, abakozi bari mu bindi bice batekana.
Abantu barenga 2100 barapfuye kuva icyorezo cya Ebola cyadutse hashize umwaka urenga, mu ntara ya Kivu ya ruguru n’iy’epfo hamwe no mu ntara ya ituri. Ni muburasirazuba bwa Repuburika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2679836' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2679836.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Undi Murwayi wa Ebola Wakuwe muri Sierra Leone
Umukozi wo mu by'ubuvuzi w'umunyamerika wanduye Ebola muri Sierra Leone ubu aravurirwa mu bitaro by'ikigo k'igihugu kita ku ndwara muri leta ya Maryland. Ni mu nkengero z'umujyi wa Washington, DC.
Abategetsi bavuga ko uwo murwayi, wagiye kwita ku barwayi ba Ebola ku bushake bwe, yinjijwe ibyo bitaro ejo kuwa gatanu mu masaha ya kare. Yazanywe mu ndege yashyizwe mu kato.
Abaganga bamusuzumye bavuze ko arembye cyane akimara kuhagera.
Abayobozi b'icyo kigo kita ku ndwara, kizwi kw'izina rya NIH (National Institutes of Health) nta yandi makuru batanze ku mwirondoro w'uwo murwayi. Uyu ni umurwayi wa 11 uvuriwe Ebola muri Leta zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Abashinzwe iby'ubuzima muri Amerika bavuga ko undi munyamerika wa kabiri, ushobora kuba yarahuye n'abantu banduye Ebola muri Sierra Leone yashyizwe mu bitaro mu mujyi wa Atlanta, aho azaba ari hafi y'ibitaro bya kaminuza ya Emory. Ibi ni ibindi bitaro byazobereye mu kuvura indwara z'ibyaduka nka Ebola.
Ikigo CDC, gishinzwe ubugenzuzi bw'indwara, cyubatse mu mujyi wa Atlanta, kivuga ko uwo muntu ataragaragaza ibimenyetso by'uko yanduye Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4285504' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4285504.html' term='ebola'>
Sierra Leone Bararindiriye Ibizova mu Matora
Abanyagihugu muri Sierra Leone kur’uyu wa gatatu ni ho bagiye gutora umukuru w’igihugu mushasha bizigiye ko azorongora ico gihugu co muri Afrika y’uburengero casinzikaye mu vy’ubutunzi inyuma y’ikiza ca Ebola co mu mwaka wa 2014 cahitanye abatari bake.
Abakandida 16 nibo bahiganirwa gusubirira Perezida Ernest Bai Koroma, arangije ibiringo bibiri vy’imyaka itanu itanu yemererwa n’ibwirizwa shingiro. Abari imbere y’abandi mu majwi ni Samura Kamara wo mu mugambwe All People's Congress uri ku butegetsi, hamwe na Julius Maada Bio, arongoye umugambwe w’abanyagihugu “People's Party”.
Iyo migambwe ibiri niyo yagiye irakabukanya ku butegetsi kuva ico gihugu ciganzura intwaro y’ubukoroni y’Abongereza mu mwaka w’1961.
Ubwinshi bw’abitoza bushobora gutuma haba igice ca kabiri c’amatora mu gihe atawoshikana amajwi 55 kw’ijana.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4399887' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4399887.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ikiza Ebola muri RDC Giteye Amakenga Cane
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS ryamenyesheje kuri uyu wa gatanu ko ryihweje uko ivya Ebola vyifashe muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo rishize ico kiza ku rugero rwo hejuru cane mu gutera ubwoba ku rwego rw’igihugu.
Iyo ngingo ifashwe inyuma y’aho uwundi muntu umwe yagaragaye ko yanduye Ebola muri imwe mu ma zone y’ubuganga mu gisagara ca Mbandaka, ahaba abantu barenga umuriyoni, ni mu buraruko bushira uburengero bw’intara ya Equateur.
Igisagara ca Mbandaka kiri ku bilometero 150 uva mu mihana yo hagati mu gace ka Bikoro, aho ico kiza catanguye kugaragara mu ntango z’uku kwezi.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Dr. Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yavuze ko ivy’ico kiza biteye amakenga.
Iryo shirahamwe rimenyesha ko ryarungitse abahinga bashika kuri 30 gukurikiranira hafi ico kiza muri ico gisagara mugihe incanco 4000 zashitse ku murwa mukuru Kinshasa ku musi wa gatatu.
Abantu bashika 44 nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko boba baranduye kuva Ebola yongera kwaduka mu ndwi iheze, harimwo 23 bapfuye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5016957' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/oms-ivuga-ibibazo-bikiri-byinshi-mu-guhangana-na-ebola-muri-kongo/5016957.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ibibazo Biracyari Byinshi Mu Guhangana na Ebola Muri Kongo
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS, rivuga ko urukingo rwa Ebola rurimo kugeragezwa rumaze gukiza ubuzima bw’abantu benshi, runagabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo.
Icyakora mu gihe bazirikana umwaka Ebola yongeye kuboneka muri Kongo OMS ivuga ko bagihura n'ibibazo byinshi mu guhangana n'iyo ndwara.
Tariki ya mbere y’ukwezi kwa munani umwaka ushize ni bwo hamenyekanye bwa mbere ko indwara ya Ebola yageze mu ntara za Kivu ya ruguru na Ituri mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo.
Kuva icyo gihe, ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS, rimaze gutangaza ko abantu 1,756 bamaze gupfa bazize indwara ya Ebola, abandi 2,600 banduye iyo ndwara.
Ni ku nshuro ya kabiri icyorezo cya Ebola kibasira ibihugu byo ku mugabane w’Afurika. Mu mwaka wa 2014, iyo ndwara yahitanye abantu 11,000 mu bihugu byo mu burengerazuba bw’Afrika.
OMS ivuga ko mu duce twa Beni, umubare w’abandura ukomeje kwiyongera ku muvuduko udasanzwe ugereranyije nuko byari bimeze umwaka ushize. Amakuru OMS ivuga ko ifite, agaragaza ko mu bantu 242 bashya banduye iyo ndwara mu byumweru bitatu bishize, benshi ari abo mu gake ka Beni mu ntara ya Ituri. Ahandi hagaraga umubare munini w’abandura iyo ndwara ni mu duce twa Mandima, Mabalako na Katwa.
Mike Ryan ushinzwe ubutabazi bwihuse muri OMS, avuga ko nubwo umubare w’abandura ukomeje kwiyongera, bashimishwa n’ibimaze kugerwaho bijyanye no gukumira ikwirakwira ry’iyo ndwara.
Avuga ko ubufatanye buhari hagati y’imiryango mpuzamahanga n’ibihugu byatumye iyo ndwara itarenga intara za Kivu ya ruguru na Ituri. Avuga kandi ko iyo ndwara itararenga imipaka ngo igere mu bihugu bihana imbibi n’izo ntara.
Bwana Ryana avuga abantu 175,000 bamaze gukingirwa indwara ya Ebola nka kimwe mu buryo bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ryayo.
Yabwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika ko mu myaka amaze akurirana ibijyanye n’indwara ya Ebola ari bwo bwa mbere habayeho gukoresha uburyo bw’inkingo. Avuga ko izo nkingo zimaze gukiza ubuzima bw’abantu benshi.
Uyu muyobozi yongeyeho ko bateganya irindi gerageza ry’inkingo zikigira ebola rizatuma izo nkingo zigera ku bantu benshi. Avuga ko bizeye ko urwo rukingo ruzafasha cyane mu kurwanya no gukiza indwara ya Ebola.
Muri icyo kiganiro n’Ijwi ry’Amerika bwana Ryan yavuze ko mu bibazo bakomeje guhura nabyo mu kazi kabo muri Kongo, ikiza ku isonga ari ikibazo cy’umutekano muke.
Yagaragaje ko hari abakozi babo bamaze kwicwa n’abarwanyi. Yongeraho ko hari uduce tuvugwamo iyo ndwara badashobora kugeramo kubera ibibazo by’umutekano muke.
Uyu muyobozi yishimira kandi ko abaturage bakomeje kwemera gukingirwa no kuvurwa, ariko akagaragaza ko hakiri abanangira ngo kuko batizera izo nkingo.
Ikindi kibazo avuga bahura nacyo n’ikijyanye n’uburyo. Agaragaza ko nibura bakeneye amafranga agera kuri miliyoni 350 z’amadolari kugirango bashobore guhangana n’indwara ya Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4389303' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4389303.html' term='ebola'>
Abanyeshure Baziga ku Buntu muri Sierra Leone
Perezida mushasha wa Sierra Leone, Julius Maada Bio kuri uyu wa kane yatangaje ko abanyeshure bo mu mashure mato mato n’ayisumbuye bagiye kuzokwiga ku buntu, nk'uko yavyemereye abanyagihugu yiyamamariza amatora. Yavuze ko iyo ngingo izotangura gushirwa mu ngiro mu mwaka mushasha w’ishure uza, mu mwezi kw'icenda umwaka w'2018.
Ivyo yabitangaje ariko yugurura ibikorwa vy’inama nshingamateka, kandi avuga ko ari mu ntumbero yo guteza imbere inyigisho.
Perezida Bio yatangaje kandi ko muri kazoza ka hafi azogwiza kabiri amafaranga reta iha igisata c’indero, ave ku bice 11 aje kuri 20 kw’ijana.
Sierra Leone ni kimwe mu bihugu bikenye cane kw’isi. N'aho gifise ubutare bwinshi mu butaka bwaco, harimwo na diyama, ica kabiri c’Abanyagihugu ba Sierra Leone barenza imyaka 15 ntibashoboye kuja mu mashure, nkuko raporo ya UNESCO yo mu mwaka wa 2015 ivuga.
Ico gihugu kiriko kirava mu bikomere casigiwe n’intambara kandi giheruka guterwa n’ikiza ca Ebola mu myaka ya 2014 gushika 2016, ikiza cahitanye abantu ibihumbi bine.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5142485' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5142485.html' term='ebola'>
Babiri Bakekwaho Ebola Bagaragaye mu Buseruko bwa Kongo
Abantu babiri bashobora kuba bafise umugera wa Ebola bahagaritswe igihe bari bagiye mu gice kibamwo abantu barenga umuliyoni mu buseruko bwa Republika ya demokrasi ya Kongo.
Abo bantu babiri bafise imyaka 24 na 25 ntibicandagishije. Bahagaritswe mu kibanza c’ugusuzumiramwo abantu c’ahitwa Mboya mu karere ka Beni mu ntara ya Kivu yo mu buraruko.
Abo bantu bavurwa ko bari bavuye mu gisagara ca Kabasha bagana mu ca Butembo. Nta bimenyetso vy’indwara ya Ebola abo bantu bose uko ari babiri berekana igihe bahagarikwa.
Ikiza ca Ebola kiramaze guhitana abantu 2180 kuva gitangajwe muri Kongo mu kwezi kw’umunani umwaka w’i 2018. Ubwa mbere ico kiza ciyadukije ku butaka bwa Kongo hari mu mwaka w’i 1976.
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, ryatangaje ko ikiza ca Ebola kiriko cibonekeza muri Kongo ari ikibazo kijanye n’amagara y’abantu cihutirwa kw’isi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3146009' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3146009.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ebola Yaracitse muri Afurika y'Uburengerazuba
Ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, O-M-S ryatangaje irangira ry’ukwiyadukiza kw’umugera wa Ebola mu gihugu ca Liberiya. Ni ukuvuga kw’ibihugu bitatu vyo muri Afurika yo mu burengero vyasinzikajwe bikomeye na Ebola muri iki gihe iyo ndwara atayihari.
Ivyatangajwe n’ishirahamwe O-M-S, uno musi ku wa kane bibaye imisi 42 inyuma yuko ata bantu bashasha basanganywe Ebola muri Liberiya.
Yamara ishirahamwe O-M-S ryamenyesheje kw’uwo mugera ushobora gusubira kwiyadukiza, rikaba ryasavye kuba maso kugira Ebola ntisubire kwibonekeza.
Ishirahamwe O-M-S rimenyesha ko zizobandanya gufasha igihugu ca Liberiya mu twigoro twaco tw’ukwirinda, gusuzuma n’ukwishura ku bantu bashasha bashobora gusubira kwandura Ebola.
Ubu n’ubugira gatatu bivurwa ko ata Ebola irangwa muri Liberiya.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2528008' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2528008.html' term='ebola'>
Mali: Abategetsi Bahagurukiye Icyorezo cya Ebola
Igihugu cya Mali kirakurikiranira hafi abantu barenga 300 bahuye n'abarwayi wa Ebola.
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima muri Mali bavuga ko barimo gukirikiranira hafi abantu 338 bafite aho bahuriye n'abarwayi batandatu bahitanywe na Ebola muri icyo gihugu. Abenshi muri abo bakurikiranwa buri munsi.
Itangazo ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima OMS, ryashyize ahagaragara kuri uyu wa kane ryavuze ko abo bantu 118, bagize aho bahurira n'abantu bahitanywe na Ebola, barangije iminsi yabo 21 iyo ndwara igaragarizamo ibimenyetso.
Iryo tangazo ryavuze ko gushakisha abahuye n'abarwayi, hagamijwe kubuza iyo ndwara gukwirakwira, byagaragaje ko aribwo buryo bwo guhagarika iyo ndwara, nk'uko byigaragaje mu bihugu bituranye na Mali, aribyo Senegali na Nigeria.
OMS yatangaje imibare mishya ku byerekeye Ebola, yavuze ko, mu bantu ibihumbi 15,145 banduye Ebola, kugeza ubu 5,420 bamaze gupfa bazira icyo cyorezo. Cyakora OMS iburira ko umubare w'abandura n'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara, ukomeje kudatangazwa wose.
Habonetse abantu bake banduye mu bindi bice by'isi, nko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ariko ibihugu byo mu burengerazuba bw'Afurika, Gineya, Liberiya na Sierra Leone, nibyo bikomeje kwibasirwa n'icyo cyorezo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5318445' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5318445.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Yaba Iri Hafi Gucika Muri Kongo
Ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS riraburira abatuye isi gukomeza kwitwararika no gukurikiza amabwiriza yo kwirinda indwara ya Ebola nubwo iki cyorezo cyagaragaye muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo kiri bugufi kurangira.
Umurwayi wa Ebola wanyuma yasezerewe ku wa Kabiri w’iki cyumweru avuye mu bitaro bya Beni.
Niba iminsi 42 ishize nta wundi muntu uragaragarwaho n’iyi ndwara, taliki ya 12 z’ukwa kane OMS izatangaza ku mugaragaro ko Ebola Irangiye.
Gusa umuyobozi mukuru wungirije wa OMS aravuga ko igihe cyo kwishimira intsinzi kitaragera. Aravuga ko bishoboka ko yakongera kugira aho igaragara.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5063259' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/muri-congo-ebola-imaze-guhitana-abarenga-2000/5063259.html' term='ebola'>
Muri Congo Ebola Imaze Guhitana Abarenga 2000
Muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo, nta kimenyetso kigaragaza ko Ebola yaba igiye kuhacika. Ni umunsi umwe bucya umuyobozi mukuru muri ONU, ajyaga gusura icyo gihugu aho umubare w’abahitanywe n’iyo ndwara iterwa na virusi yandura cyane, umaze kurenga 2,000. Hari n’undi muntu wahitanywe n’iyo ndwara muri Uganda bituranye.
Uherutse guhitanwa n’iyo ndwara aho muri Uganda yari umwana w’umukobwa w’imyaka icyenda wari uvuye muri Congo. Byatumye hongera kuba ubwoba ko virusi ya Ebola ishobora kubona aho imenera ikambuka umupaka wa Repuburika ya Centrafurika aho yabonetse mu kwezi kwa munani kw’umwaka ushize.
Abayobozi bashinzwe ubuzima muri Congo, baraye bavuze ko abantu 2,006 bapfuye. Muri abo 1,901 byaremejwe neza ko bahitanywe na Ebola. Abandi 105 nta wabihamya ijana kw'ijana. Aho ni ukuva mu kwezi kwa munani umwaka ushize wa 2018.
Abategetsi banditse bagira bati: “Kuva icyorezo cyaduka, umubare w’abanduye ni 3,004. Barimo 2,899 bifitiwe gihamya na 105 bikekwa ko yaba ari Ebola. Bongeyeho ko 902 bavuwe bagakira.
Aya makuru atangajwe umunsi umwe mbere y’uko umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU Antonio Guterres ajya gusura Congo, kwirebera aho urugamba rwo kurwanya Ebola rugeze.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4548670' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4548670.html' term='ebola'>
Uruhara rwa Monusco mu Kurwanya Ebola muri Kongo
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu OMS ritangaza ko mu misi indwi gushika kw’icumi iri imbere izoba itoroshe mu gukurikirana igwirirana rya Ebola mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo.
Mu biharuro vya nyuma vyashikirijwe, OMS ivuga ko abantu 111 banduye Ebola, 75 barapfuye.
OMS ivuga ko izobandanya kuhangana na Ebola mu buraruko bw’intara ya Kivu na Ituri hamwe na Oicha, igisagara kigoye kwinjiramwo bivanye n’umutekano muke uharangwa.
Umuvugizi wa OMS, Christian Lindmeier avuga ko naho hari imihari irenga 100 irwanira mur’ubwo burere, abajejwe amagara y’abantu barashobora gushika mu bice bipfuza bafashijwe n’abasirikare ba MONUSCO.
Abantu barenga ibihumbi bine baramaze guhabwa urucanco rwa Ebola barimwo abakora mu gisata c’amagara y’abantu hamwe n’abana barenga amajana icenda.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4651809' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/amerika-ihangayikishijwe-na-ebola-muri-congo-/4651809.html' term='ebola'>
Amerika Ihangayikishijwe na Ebola muri Congo
Umutegetsi akorera ibiro vya Reta ya Amerika bijejwe iterambere mu makungu, USAID yatangaje ko reta ya Amerika itewe umutima uhagaze n’ikiza ca Ebola cadutse mu ntara yo mu buseruko bwa Congo irangwamwo ingwano, aho abantu 312 bamaze gufatwa n’ico kiza, mu gihe abandi 191 bamaze gupfa.
Nk’uko uyo mutegetsi abivuga, igiteye amakenga cane ni uko ivyo vyatumye abakozi bajejwe kwitaho amagara y’abantu bagira ingorane zo kwigiza kure abamaze gufatwa n’iyo ngwara. Ubwandu bw’ico kiza bwariyongeye cane mu misi iheze.
Igihugu ca Uganda kibanyi ca Congo kiramaze gutangaza ko catanguye guha urucandago abakozi bajejwe kwitaho amagara y’abantu mu mugambi wo kubakingira mu gihe ikiza ca Ebola cotandukira igihugu ca Uganda.
Umutegtsi akorera ibiro vya Reta ya Amerika bijejwje iterambere kw’isi USAID, yavuze ko kuva ico kiza cadutse mu kwezi kw’umunani, reta ya Amerika yarungitse abahinga barenga 20 mu gihugu ca Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Congo, bagiye gukorana n’ubushikirangaji bw’ico gihugu bujejwe amagara y’abantu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5025036' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/u-rwanda-rwafunze-imipaka-iruhuza-n-umugi-wa-goma-kubera-ebola/5025036.html' term='ebola'>
U Rwanda Rwafunze Gato Imipaka Iruhuza na Goma Kubera Ebola
U Rwanda rwafunze gato umupaka uruhuza na Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo kuri uyu wa kane, mu gihe abategetsi muvyo amagara y’abantu bariko barakora uko bashoboye kugira bahagarike ikiza ca Ebola kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 1,800.
Abavyiboneye babwiye Ijwi ry’Amerika ko abategetsi babujije abantu batari bake kujabuka umupaka hagati y’igisagara ca Gisenyi mu Rwanda na Goma amasaha make, inyuma y’aho hamenyekanye ko Ebola yamenyekanye i Goma. Abantu gusa bemerewe kujabuka ni abakongomani bari mu Rwanda bariko batahuka iwabo.
Umushikiranganji w’u Rwanda w’amagara y’abantu yahakanye ko ata mupaka wigeze wugarwa, ariko mu masaha y’inyuma ya sasite kuri uyu wa kane uruja n’uruza rw’abantu rwari rwasubiye kandi hagati y’ivyo bisagara bibiri.
Uko gufunga gato umupaka kwabaye igisata c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS isabiye ibihugu kutugara imbibe zavyo canke kubuza abaja muri Kongo.
Abategetsi ba Kongo b’amagara y’abantu baremeje ko umwana w’umukobwa avyarwa n’umugabo yishwe na Ebola mu ntango z’iyi ndwi afise ibimenyetso c’iyo ngwara.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5025988' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5025988.html' term='ebola'>
Amerika Yemeye Kurungika Abafasha Guhangana na Ebola i Goma
Ikigo co muri Reta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura no gukinga indwara, CDC mu mfunyafunyo y’icongereza, cashikirije kuri uyu wa kane ko abakozi baco 12 barungitswe i Goma muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gufasha abarwayi ba Ebola. Ico kiza kimaze umwaka, kimazi guhitana ubuzima bw’abantu barenga 1,800.
Ico kigo catangaje ko gishobora kuzorungika abandi bakozi baco mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Kongo ahazogaragara ko hari umutekano.
Umuyobozi w’ico kigo, Dr. Robert R. Redfield yashikirije ejo kuwa kane mu butumwa bwa Twitter ko intambara zahagaritse utwigoro tw’abajejwe amagara y’abantu guhangana n’ico kiza.
Ico kigo cashikirije kandi ko kiriko kirakorana n’ubushikiranganji bw’Amerika bw’imigenderanire n’amakungu kugira barabe ko umutekano ukwiye kugira barungike abandi bakozi b’Amerika muvy’amagara y’abantu mu bice biri hanze ya Goma.
Ikigo co muri Amerika gushinzwe kugenzura no gukinga indwara catangaje iyo ngingo, inyuma y’amasaha make reta y’u Rwanda yugaye umwanya muto urubibe basangiye na Kongo ku bwoba bw’uko iyo ngwara ishobora kwandukira abanyagihugu bayo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5097647' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5097647.html' term='ebola'>
Reta ya Tanzaniya na OMS Ntibumvikana kuri Ebola
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu, OMS, rihagaritswe umutima n’abategetsi ba Tanzaniya badashikiriza amakuru y’aboba baranduye Ebola kandi risaba ko haba ugukorera ahabona kuri ico kiza.
Mu ndwi zibiri ziheze, OMS yararonse, ico yise raporo zitavuye ku butegetsi z’urupfu rw’umuntu ku murwa mukuru wa Tanzaniya, Dar es Salaam, yoba akekwa kuba yishwe na Ebola.
Kuva ico gihe, OMS ivuga ko yaronse amakuru ko umuntu w’imyaka 27 akekwa kwandura Ebola yashizwe mu bitaro, ariko nta makuru yavuye mu bipimo, ko yoba yaranduye canke atanduye.
Mu kiganiro ku bamenyeshamakuru kw’itariki 14 z’ukwezi kw’icenda, abategetsi ba Tanzaniya batangaje ko ata kiza ca Ebola cateye mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5052255' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5052255.html' term='ebola'>
Guterres mu Rugendo muri Congo Kwirabira Ivya Ebola
Umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU mu ndwi iza azogendera igihugu ca Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo gihanzwe n’ikiza ca Ebola.
Antonió Guterres ategekanya kuzogendera ico gihugu imisi itatu, guhera kw’itariki 31 z’uku kwezi kwa munani. Umuvugizi wiwe, Stephane Dujarric, yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ko Guterres yipfuza kwirabira uko ivya Ebola vyifashe no guhamagarira abafasha kwongereza amafaranga kugira bahangane n’ico kiza.
Mu bo bazobonana muri urwo rugendo harimwo perezida Felix Tshisekedi ku murwa mukuru, Kinshasa.
Iyi nkuru Ijwi ry’Amerika riyikesha umumenyeshamakuru waryo ku cicaro ca ONU i New York, Margaret Besher.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2455434' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2455434.html' term='ebola'>
Burundi: Guverinoma Yahagurukiye Gukumira Ebola
WASHINGTON, DC —
Uburundi buhagurukiye gukumira indwara ya Ebola. Kuva hatangiye kuvugwa icyorezo cya Ebola muri Afrika y’uburengerazuba, ibihugu hafi ya byose birakora ibishoboka mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Mu kiganiro Ijwi ry'Amerika ryagiranye n’umuvugizi wa ministeri y’ubuzima no kurwanya icyorezo cya Sida, muganga Thaddee Ndikumana, yatubwiye ingamba zafashwe mu rwego rwo gukumira icyorezo cya ebola.
Izo zirimo guhugura abaganga, gutegura ibikoresho byakwifashishwa mu gihe haboneka icyo cyorezo, harimo no gupima abinjira mu gihugu cyane ababa baturuka muri Afrika yo mu burengerazuba.
Cyakora kugeza ubu ngo nta muntu wari wagaragaho ibyo bimenyetso. Muganga Ndikumana rero yahumurije abanyagihugu avuga ko badakwiye gukuka umutima, ariko kandi ko bagomba kwilinda icyatuma bandura Ebola, harimo kwirinda guhiga ibikoko cyangwa kurya inyamaswa zapfuye. Asaba kandi abanyagihugu kwihutira kujya kwa muganga igihe cyose baba bafite ikibazo cy’ubuzima.
Ibindi bisobanuro mubikurikire mu kiganiro umunyamakuru w'Ijwi ry'Amerika Eugenie Mukankusi yagiranye na Muganga Ndikumana.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2650536' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2650536.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Ntirogorora Muri Afrika Y’Uburengerazuba
Kurwanya Ebola muri Afrika y’uburengerazuba bicyagoranye kubera gushyingura nabi imirambo y’abo yica no kunanirwa gutahura vuba abayandura. Ni OMS ibitangaza.
Ubusanzwe, nk’uko abaganga babitangamo inama, kugirango Ebola ihagarare gukwirakwira ni uko imirambo y’abo yishe igomba gushyingurwa n’abantu bambaye bikwije imyenda yabugenewe, ibarinda kwandura. Nyamara rero, nk’uko OMS ibitangamo urugero, mu cyumweru cya kabili cy’uko kwezi honyine, imirambo y’abazize Ebola 39 muri Guinea na 45 bose muri Sierra Lone yashyinguwe bisanzwe, ntawambaye imyenda imurinda.
Naho ku ngorane zo gutahura vuba abanduye Ebola, OMS iragira, iti: “Muri kiriya cyumweru cya kabili cy’uko kwezi, abantu 40 bamenye ko ari yo yabahitanye bararangije gupfa. Kuba bitaramenyekanye ko bayanduye hakiri kare kugirango bashyirwe mu kato, ni ikibazo gikomeye kuko bashobora kuba barasize baranduje abandi bantu batabarika.”
Muri Guinea, Liberia, na Sierra Leone bafashe ingamba zihambaye zo gutahura abakekwaho Ebola hakiri kare cyane. Nyamara rubanda bo ntibitabira ingamba zo kujya mu kato no gufatanya n’abanganga uko bikwiye, nk’uko OMS ibivuga. Ni yo mpamvu guhashya Ebola bikiri mu nzira ndende. Muri biriya bihugu bitatu, hatahuwe abandi bantu bamaze kwandura Ebola 128 mu cyumweru gishize.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5007692' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5007692.html' term='ebola'>
U Rwanda Rukomeje Gukaza Imyiteguro yo Gukumira Ebola
Inzego z’ubutegetsi mu Rwanda zikomeje gukaza imyiteguro yo gukumira icyorezo cya Ebola ku mipaka na Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo.
Iyo myiteguro iragaragarira ku ngendo zikurikirana abategetsi bakuru mu rwego rw’ubuzima barimo umunyamabanga wa leta muri Ministeri y’Ubuzima Dr Patrick Ndimubanzi bakomeje kugirira ku mipaka yose y'u Rwanda ruhana na Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo, bagenzura aho imirimo yo gukaza ubugenzuzi bukorerwa abambutse baturutse hakurya igeze.
Nubwo uyu munyamabanga wa leta atashimye kuvugisha itangazamakuru, mu bikorwa yasuye bikomeje gukorerwa kuri iyo mipaka birimo za kamera zirimo kuhashyirwa zifite ubushobozi bwo gukurura ibipimo by’ubushyuhe nka kimwe mu bimenyetso bya Ebola.
Yanasuye n’inyubako zagenewe gukurikiraniramo ababa baketsweho icyo cyorezo zirimo kubakwa aho ku mipaka cyo kimwe no kureba aho ibitaro bya Gihundwe bigeze byitegura kwakira no gufata ibizamini ku bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya Ebola.
Dogiteri Ndimubanzi yasabye ko imirimo isigaye yakwihutishwa ikarangira mu gihe gito gishoboka byanaba ngombwa abarimo kuyikora bagakora amanywa n’ijoro ariko bikava mu nzira.
Mu gushaka kumenya niba uburyo bwari busanzwe bukoreshwa budahagije mu gusuzuma no kumenya ababa bafite ibimenyetso bya Ebola, bwana Malick Kayumba, umuvugizi wa ministeri y’ubuzima yabwiye Ijwi ry'Amerika ko ibirimo gukorwa ari ukongera ubushobozi hashingiwe ku mageragezwa aba yakorewe ku busanzwe buhari.
Uyu muvugizi wa Ministeri y’Ubuzima mu Rwanda kandi yabwiye Ijwi ry'Amerika ko nta muntu n'umwe wigeze agaragaraho ibimenyetso bya Ebola ku butaka bw’u Rwanda.
Ku rundi ruhande bamwe mu batuye akarere ka Rusizi baragaragaza impungenge ku babo bakorera imirimo itandukanye muri Congo cyane cyane abambukira ku bindi byambu bitari imipaka isanzwe imenyerewe.
Mu nama mpuzamahanga yabaye kuri uyu wa gatatu yigaga kuri iki cyorezo cya Ebola, u Rwanda rwashyizwe mu bihugu bifite ibyago byo kugerwamo vuba n’iki cyorezo; hanzurwa ko ishami ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS ryohereza itsinda ry’impugucye zarufasha guhangana nacyo.
Bwana Kayumba yabwiye Ijwi ry'Amerika ko amakuru y’ukuza kw’izo mpuguke ntacyo bayazi ho, ariko basanzwe bafitanye imikoranire.
Ingufu mu gukumira icyorezo cya Ebola ku ruhande rw’u Rwanda zongerewe nyuma y’uko mu mujyi wa Goma uhana imbibi n’u Rwanda ku ruhande rwa Kivu y’Amajyaruguru hagaragaye umurwayi wa Ebola bivugwa ko uwo yari yananyuze mu mujyi wa Bukavu ku ruhande rwa Kivu y’Amajyepfo ihana imbibi n'akarere ka Rusizi.
Nubwo OMS iheruka kugaragaza impungenge ko icyorezo cya Ebola kivugwa mu baturanyi gishobora gutuma u Rwanda rufunga imipaka, kugeza kuri uyu wa gatanu urujya n’uruza ni urusanzwe ku mipaka u Rwanda ruhana na Congo ku ruhande rw’akarere ka Rusizi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4837212' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4837212.html' term='ebola'>
ONU Isaba Tshisekedi Gushinga Reta Vyihuta
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU ryasavye perezida Felix Tshisekedi wa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo gushinga reta bidatevye, mu gihe ico gihugu kibandanya kuba mu mahoro inyuma y’ibisikanya ku butegetsi ryabaye mu mahoro kuva ico gihugu cikukiye hahareze imyaka ishika 60.
Leila Zerrougui arongoye ibikorwa vya ONU muri Congo yabibwiye akanama ka ONU kajejwe umutekano kuri uyu wa mbere.
Zerrougui yavuze ko ibiganiro bitumbereye gushinga reta nshasha biriko biraba hagati y’urunani Front Commun pour le Congo (FCC), rwatahukanye intebe nyinshi mu matora y’abashingamateka n’abarongoye intara, hamwe n’urunani Coalition pour le Changement rwashigikiye kandidatire ya Tshisekedi.
Hagat’aho, igihugu gihanzwe n’indyane hagati y’amoko hamwe n’ikiza ca Ebola mu ntara ya Beni.
Ambasaderi wa Congo muri ONU Ignace Gata Mavita wa Lufuta yabwiye ako kanama ko perezida arajwe ishinga n’umutekano uhungabana mu gihugu, agasaba ONU gufatanya n’abasirikare b’igihugu mu gutuza imihari yitwaje ibirwanisho.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5006163' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5006163.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Abajejwe Umutekano Bagiye Gufasha Kurwanya Ebola
Abategetsi muri Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo batangaza ko abasirikare n’abapolisi b’ico gihugu bazofasha gutuma ingingo zerekeye kwoza amaboko n’ugupima umuriro mu mubiri w’abantu vyubahirizwa muri iki gihe ikiza ca Ebola catangajwe ko ari ikibazo cihutirwa giteye impungenge amakungu.
Abasirikare ba Reta n’abapolisi b’igihugu bazotegeka abanyagihugu bagonanwa gufata ingingo zigenewe gutuma ikiza ca Ebola kitabandanya gukwiragira.
Ivyo Dr. Aruna Abedi yabitangaje mu kiganiro yahaye abamenyeshamakuru mu gisagara ca Goma kirimwo abantu barenga imiliyoni 2. Inkuru yerekeye umuntu wa mbere afise Ebola muri ico gisagara yatangajwe mu ntango z’iyi ndwi.
Igisagara ca Goma kiri hafi y’urubibe Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo ihana n’u Rwanda kandi gifise ikibuga c’indege mpuzamakungu.
Uruja n’uruza rw’abantu n’imodoka vyari nkuko bisanzwe muri ico gisagara uno musi ku wa kane. Ni inyuma yuko ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS ritangaje ku musi wa gatatu ku muhingamo ko ikibazo ca Ebola ari ikibazo cihutirwa giteye impungenge amakungu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4830192' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4830192.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Mu Mezi Atandatu nta Ebola Izovugwa muri RDC
Umuyobozi w’igisata c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU cita ku magara y’abantu, OMS, avuga ko ikiza ca Ebola mu buseruko bwa Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gishobora gusezererwa burundu mu mezi atandatu, mu gihe vyose vyogenda nkuko bitegekanijwe. Ibiharuro vya nyuma vyashikirijwe n’ubushikiranganji bw’amagara y’abantu vyavuga ko abantu 927 aribo banduye, muri bo 584 barapfa.
Amakuru Ijwi ry’Amerika rikesha umumenyeshamakuru waryo i Geneve ku cicaro ca OMS, Lisa Schlein avuga ko umuyobozi wa OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yemeza ko utwigoro twakozwe twerekana ko ico kiza kizoba carangiye mu mezi atandatu mu ntara za Kivu yo mu buraruko na Ituri.
Avuga kandi ko Ebola ata bantu bashasha icandukira mu bisagara vya Beni, Mangina, Komanda, na Oicha muri Kivu y’uburaruko.
Tedros ariko avuga ko umutekano ari co kintu ca mbere kigiteye amakenga, mu gihe imihari yitwaje ibirwanisho ikibandanya ihungabanya umutekano mu bisagara vya Katwa na Butembo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5086763' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/dr-ilunga-yagirizwa-kunyuruza-amahera-yo-kurwanya-ebola-muri-drc-/5086763.html' term='ebola'>
Dr Ilunga Yagirizwa Kunyuruza Amahera yo Kurwanya Ebola muri DRC
Uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo Oly Ilunga kuri uno wa kabiri yarungitswe kumvirizwa muri parike. Ni inyuma y’imisi itatu yari amaze mu minwe ya polisi yagirizwa kuba yaranyuruje amafaranga yari agenewe kurwanya Ebola.
Muri rusangi amafaranga muganga Oly Ilunga yagirizwa yababa imiliyoni zine n’inusu z’amadolari ya Amerika. Ivyagiriji abamuburanira bamirira kure basigura ko amafaranga yahawe kugira agwanye Ebola atarenga imiliyoni zibiri n’ibihumbi amajana ane z’amadolari.
Ababuranira Ilunga bavuga ko ayo mafaranga yakoreshejwe ivyo yari abwirizwa gukora. Bemanga ko muri dosiye y’uwo baburanira bashizemwo ivyemezo vyerekana uko igiceri kimwe kimwe cakoreshejwe mu kiringo c’amezi cumi na kumwe.
Agihagarikwa, muganga Ilunga yagirijwe kuba yariko agerageza gusohoka Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo kandi ubutungane bwamutegetse mu mpera z’ukwa munani kutarenga imbibe z’ico gihugu.
Oly Ilunga w’imyaka 59 yatanze imihoho mu mpera z’ukwezi kw’indwi, inyuma yaho Perezida Félix Tshisekedi yakiye ububasha ubushikiranganji yaramutswa bwo kuyobora umugambi wari ugamije kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola kimaze guhitana abarenga ibihumbi bibiri kuva mu kwa munani 2018.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3790956' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3790956.html' term='ebola'>
Ingaruka Mbi z'Inyama z'Ibikoko vyo mw'Ishamba
Igihe Ebola yaduka mu gihugu ca Sierra Leone, gufungura inyama z’ibikoko vyo mw’ishamba vyaragabanutse bikomeye cane.
Ivyatohojwe vyerekana kw’ivyo bizogira ingaruka nziza ku magara y’abantu n’ugukingira inyamaswa.
Igikorwa c’ugutanga inyigisho ku bibazo n’ingaruka z’ugufungura inyama z’ibikoko vyo mw’ishamba vyashimikiye ku banyagihugu baba hafi y’ibibanza bikingiwe birimwo inyamaswa.
Inyama z’ibikoko vyo mw’ishamba zirimwo i mbumbamubiri bita proteine ikenewe cane ku banyagihugu baba mu bice vyo hagati mu gihugu mu karere ko muri Afrika yo mu burengero. Yamara n’abantu baba mu bisagara barirukira inyama z’ibikoko vyo mw’ishamba.
Kubera abarondera izo nyama biyongeye, vyatumye mu bibanza bimwe bimwe ata gikoko kisubira kubazwa mu mashamba.
Inyama z’ibikoko vyo mw’ishamba zishobora kandi gukwiragiza indwara nka Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_1263934' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/a-18-a-2003-11-15-3-1-93011939/1263934.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Ivuga ko Ebola Yongeye Gutera muri Congo Brazaville - 2003-11-15
Ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, ryemeje ko indwara ya Ebola yongeye gutera ahitwa Mbomo, mu majyaruguru ya Congo Brazaville.  Abaganga 3 ba OMS ejo ni bwo bavuye i Brazaville bagiye kureba aho iyo ndwara yateye ituruka.  Minisiteri y’ubuzima muri Congo Brazaville ivuga ko hari abantu 13 bakekwaho kuba baranduye iyo ndwara ya Ebola. Abandi 11 ngo yarabahitanye.  Umuvugizi wa OMS, Fadela Chaib, avuga ko OMS yamenye ko Ebola yari yongeye gutera mu mpera z’ukwezi gushize. Ibizami by’amaraso by’abantu bari bafite ibimenyetso bya Ebola mu ntangiriro z’iki cyumweru ngo bimaze kugaragaza ko ari yo barwaye koko.  Muri ntangiriro z’uyu mwaka na none abantu 120 nibura bazize Ebola mu karere ka Mbomo n’ahitwa Kelle mu majyaruguru y’uburengerazuba bwa Congo Brazaville. Icyo gihe Ebola ngo yari yatewe n’uko abaturage bari bariye inyama z’inguge zari zanduye iyo ndwara.  Indwara ya Ebola irandura cyane, kandi ikandurira mu maraso, amacandwe cyangwa indi mirenda yo mu mubiri w’umuntu. Uwarwaye Ebola agira umuriro mwinshi, akagira umutwe n’isesemi, akanavira mu nda. Hagati ya 50 na 90% by’abanduye Ebola irabahitana.   Shakira izindi nkuru z'Afurika hano. Saba amakuru muri email yawe  hano.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5313067' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/oms-mu-nzira-yo-kwemeza-ko-ebola-yasezerewe-muri-kongo-/5313067.html' term='ebola'>
OMS mu Nzira yo Kwemeza ko Ebola Yasezerewe muri Kongo
OMS yatangaje uyu munsi ko muri iyi minsi 13 ishize nta muntu uheruka kwandura virusi ya Ebola muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo.
OMS ivuga ko igomba “gutegereza iminsi 42 ireba ko nta muntu n’umwe wongeye kwandura mbere yo kwemeza ko Ebola yatsinzwe."
Ebola yatangiye gukora ibara muri Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo mu kwezi kwa munani 2018, cyane cyane mu burasirazuba bw’igihugu.
Ni inshuro ya cumi Ebola muri iki gihugu kuva mu 1976. Yahitanye abantu ibihumbi bibili na 264.
Ni iya kabili mu mateka yishe abantu benshi nyuma y’iyatsembye imbaga y’abantu barenga ibihumbi 11 mu 2014 muri Afrika y’uburengerazuba, cyane cyane mu bihugu bya Liberia, Guinea, na Sierra Leone.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3280218' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3280218.html' term='ebola'>
Zika: Ibivuye mu Bushakashatsi Biteye Impungenge Kurushiriza
Abategetsi bajejwe amagara y’abantu bameneysha ko uko abashakashatsi bamenya vyinshi kurishiriza ku mugera wa Zika, ariko bagira impungenge kurushiriza, ku nkurikizi zayo mu bwonko. n’ibibazo vy’uwo mugera mu kiringo kirekire kiri kiri imbere.
Icegera c’umuyobozi b’ibiro bijejwe kurwanya n’ukwirinda indwara ziterwa n’imigera muri Amerika, Dr. Anne Schuchat, avuga ko ibintu vyose ubushakashatsi bumenya ku mugera wa Zika bitera ubwoba kurusha uko bavyiyumvira.
Amenyesha kw’ubushakashatsi bwerekana ko umugera wa Zika ugeramira ubwonko bw’umwana akiri mu nda.
Abategetsi bajejwe ubuvuzi bafise impungenge ku vyerekeye ikwiragira ry’umugera wa Zika. Basaba inama nshingamateka ya Amerika kwemeza idatevye umuliyaridi n’imiliyoni amajana icenda y’amadolari yihutirwa, yasabwe mu rugamba rw’ukurwanya Zika.
Bamenyesha ko nibatoronka amafranga basaba batazoshobora gushika kuvyo bakeneye gukora.
Mu ndwi iheze, ibiro vya prezida wa Amerika, Maison Blanche, vyatangaje ko bizoshira amafranga agera ku miliyoni amajana atandatu y’amadolari mu kigega kigenewe kurwanya umugera wa Zika.
Menshi muri ayo mafranga azoba avuye mu yasanzwe ahari ku bijanye na Ebola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2494323' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/2494323.html' term='ebola'>
Rwanda: Guverinoma Yivuguruje ku byo Gusuzuma Ebola
Mu Rwanda, Ministeri y'Ubuzima yisubiyeho ku cyemezo yari yafashe cy’uko abagenzi bose baturutse muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika na Espagne bazajya bapimwa Ebola.
Ku rubuga rwe rwa Twitter, Ministiri ushinzwe ubuzima mu Rwanda Dr. Agnes Binagwaho yanditse ko icyo cyemezo yagifashe ku giti cye ko ntaho gihuriye na Guverinoma y’u Rwanda, ariyo mpamvu gisheshwe. Umunyamakuru w'Ijwi ry'Amerika Eddie Rwema adufitiye inkuru irambuye.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4547020' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4547020.html' term='ebola'>
RDC: Ebola Imaze Kwica 75
Ibitigiri vy’abamaze guhitanwa n’ikiza ca Ebola muri Republika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo bimaze gushika ku bantu 75, nkuko vyashikirijwe kuri uyu wa mbere n’umushikirianganji w’amagara y’abantu mur’ico gihugu.
Uwo mushikiranganji amenyesha ko ata wafashwe n’ico kiza aramenyekana kuva ku musi w’Imana.
Ikindi gice Ebola iheruka gutandukira ni mu buraruko bw’intara ka Kivu ya ruguru, aharwiriye imihari y’abarwanyi.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5049104' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5049104.html' term='ebola'>
Ibihugu Bihana Urubibe na Congo Bisabwa Gufasha Kurwanya Ebola
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu (OMS) ryasavye ibihugu bihurikiye mur’iryo shirahamwe, cane cane ibihugu icenda bihana urubibe na Republika iharanira demokarasi ya Kongo gukorera hamwe mu kurwanya ikiza ca Ebola.
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyessus yabivugiye i Brazzaville kuri uyu wa mbere mu nama ya 69 ya komiye ya OMS mu karere ka Afrika, aho bategekanya gutora umuyobozi mushasha wa OMS Afrika, isanzwe ifise icicaro ku murwa mukuru wa Congo Brazzaville.
Intumwa 400, zigizwe n’abashikiranganji b’amagara y’abantu ku mugabane w’Afrika zitavye iyo nama, hamwe na perezida Denis Sassou Nguesso. Iyi nkuru Ijwi ry’Amerika riyikesha itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Abafaransa, AFP.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_5048187' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/abanyarwanda-bakomeje-kubuzwa-kwambuka-muri-congo-/5048187.html' term='ebola'>
Abanyarwanda Bakomeje Kubuzwa Kwambuka muri Congo
Iminsi ine irarumanye Abanyarwanda bakoreshaga imipaka ya Rusizi ya 1 n’iya 2 bajya muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo batemererwa kwambuka ku ruhande rwa Congo.
Ukigera kuri iyi mipaka uko ari ibiri urasanganirwa n’abaturage biremye mu matsinda mato mato ku ruhande rw’u Rwanda, ubona ko bashobewe.
Iki kibazo kigitangura ku wa kane w’icyumweru gishize haherewe ku bambukaga bakoresheje indangamuntu, ariko kuri ubu icyangombwa cy’inzira cyose waba ukoresha, upfa kuba uri Umunyarwanda, gutambuka ku ruhande rwa Congo ntibishoboka.
Ku rundi ruhande ariko Abanyekongo bava iwabo bajya i Rusizi cyangwa bava i Rusizi bataha bo baratambuka ku mipaka yombi nta nkomyi; igikomeje gutera urujijo abaturanyi babo bo ku ruhande rw’u Rwanda bamaze iminsi ine bakumirwa.
Kugeza ubu imvano y’uku gufunga imipaka ku baturage b’uruhande rumwe iracyari urujijo; inzego z’ubutegetsi ku rwego rw’akarere ka Rusizi zabwiye Ijwi ry'Amerika ko nazo iki kibazo cyarenze ubushobozi bwazo, uretse kugitangira raporo mu nzego nkuru z’igihugu nta kindi zarenzaho.
Nubwo iki kibazo kimaze iminsi igera kuri 4 gihari, ubuyobozi bukuru bw’urwego rushinzwe abinjira n’abasohoka mu Rwanda bwabwiye Ijwi rya Amerika ko ntacyo burakimenyaho.
Ihungabana ry’urujya n’uruza ku mipaka ya Rusizi ya 1 n’iya 2 u Rwanda ruhana na Congo ku ruhande rw’intara ya Kivu y’Amajyepfo rije rikurikira igabanuka rikabije ry’Abanyarwanda bambuka imipaka u Rwanda ruhana n’icyo gihugu ku ruhande rw’akarere ka Rubavu biturutse ku cyorezo cya Ebola cyagaragaye mu mujyi wa Goma.
Amakuru twamenyeye kuri iyi mipaka yombi ni ay’uko kuri ubu Abanyekongo bafite ibyangombwa bigaragaza ko baturuka muri Teritwari ya Mwenga, nayo iheruka kugaragaramo abarwayi 2 ba Ebola ku ruhande rwa Kivu y’Amajyepfo batarimo kwemererwa kwinjira mu Rwanda.
Icyakora biragoye kwemeza niba iyo yaba ari yo mvano yo gukumira abanyarwanda kwinjira ku butaka bwa Kongo.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2482024' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/umuntu-wa-mbere-wanduriye-ebola-muri-amerika/2482024.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Umuntu wa Mbere Yandurijwe Ebola muri Leta ya Texas
Muri Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika habonetse umuntu wa mbere wanduye Ebola ari imbere mu gihugu. Uyu ni umuforomokazi wo mu mujyi wa Dallas wavuraga umurwayi Thomas Eric Duncan wari wavuye muri Liberiya yarayanduye. Uwo Thomas Duncan yitabye Imana mu cyumweru gishize.
Uwo muntu mushya wanduye avugwa kuba afite imyaka iri muri za 20 n'indi. Abashinzwe iby'ubuzima muri Amerika barakora ibishoboka byose kugirango bakumira icyo cyorezo.
Abakozi bazobereye mu byo gukoresha ibintu bishobora kwanduza barimo gusukura inzu uwo muforomokazi yabagamo mu mujyi wa Dallas. Ibi kandi byatumye abaturanyi na bo bagira ubwoba cyane.
Dr. Thomas Frieden, ushinzwe ikigo CDC cy'Amerika, kita ku bugenzuzi no kubuza indwara kwandura, yavuze ko hagomba gufatwa izindi ngamba zikaze zo gukumira Ebola. Ku kibazo cy'umuforomokazi wanduye Ebola, Dr. Drieden avuga ko haahobora kuba hari amabwiriza yo kwikingira atarakurikijwe.
Hagati aho, gusuzuma abantu binjira muri Amerika bavuye mu bihugu by'Afurika byiganjemo Ebola byatangiye gukorwa ku bibuga by'indege byo muri Amerika. Ubu muri Afurika haravugwa abantu barenga bihumbi umunani banduye virusi ya Ebola, mu gihe imaze guhitana abarenga ibihumbi bine.
Nyamara, mu gihe ubwoba bwo kwandura Ebola bwihuta cyane mu batuye isi kurusha uko virusi ubwayo yihuta, hari inkuru nziza yaturutse mu Burusiya. Abashinzwe iby'ubuzima muri icyo gihugu batangaje ko bakoze inkigo za Ebola zishobora gutangira kugeragezwa ku bantu.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_3015286' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/3015286.html' term='ebola'>
OMS: Ingamba Nshya zo Kurwanya Ebola
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryitaho amagara kw’isi rigiye gutunganya ibintu gushasha mu ntumbero yo gusezerera ubutagaruka ikiza c’ingwara ya Ebola.
Margaret Chan, umuyobozi mukuru w’iryo shirahamwe amenyesha ko baronse ivyigwa igihe ico kiza kirigita abantu mu gace ka Afrika y’Uburengero. Agira ati, ivyo nivyo iryo shirahamwe rigiye gufatirako kugira rifate umukenyuro musha mu rugamba rwo kurwanya ico kiza.
Mu bigiye guhinduka, OMS, ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita ku magara y’abantu rigiye gushiraho abaganga mu bice bitandukanye vy’isi bazokwama bagavye mugihe ico kiza cokwongera kwibonekeza mugihugu ic’arico cose.
Nkuko Marguaret Chan abandanya abivuga, ati Kera iyo tuvuze ivyo kwitaho amagara y’abantu, abantu bahita bumva kuvura, ariko ubu dukwiye kwama tugavye twiteguriye icokwaduka kandi tukama tugira ubushakashatsi.
Ati ikindi gikomeye n’ugukomeza imigenderanire myiza hagati y’abita ku magara y’abantu n’abanyagihugu.
Aho ni mugihe abanyagihugu bamwe bahisha ibiziga vy’ababo baba bahitanywe n’ico kiza bigatuma ibikorwa vy’iryo shirahamwe bitagenda neza nkuko bikwiye.
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryita kumagara y’abantu rimenyesha ko ata murwayi wa Ebola acibonekeza muri Sierra Leone. Asobanura ko ariko ntaworyama umukondorazosi kuko mugihugu kibanyi ca Gineya hashobora kuba har’abantu batatu boba baheruka kwandura ico kiza.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4978894' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4978894.html' term='ebola'>
Imirwano Muri Kongo Ibangamiye Abagerageza Guhoshya Ebola
Umukozi mukuru w’Ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS aratangaza ko imbaraga zishyirwa mu bikorwa byo gukumira icyorezo cy’indwara ya Ebola muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo zishobora kutagira icyo zitanga, igihe cyose ako karere kazaba karangwamo imirwano.
Imibare y’abanduye iyo ndwara iheruka gushyirwa ahagaragara yazamutse kugera ku bantu 2,284 barimo 1,540 bahitanywe na yo, hamwe n’abandi 637 bayikize. Mu cyumweru gishize abantu 79 bashya barayanduye.
Ibrahima Soce Fall, umuyobozi wungirije ushinzwe ibikorwa by’ubutabazi bw’ingoboka wa OMS aravuga ko nubwo ibikorwa byo gukumira iki cyorezo byagendaga neza, ubu bitangiye kubangamirwa cyane ahitwa Mabalako na Mandima kubera urujya n’uruza rw’abantu bahunga imvururu ziterwa n’abarwanyi b’inyeshyamba za Mai-Mai na ADF muri Kivu y’amajyaruguru na Ituri.
Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo irimo imvururu kuva mu mwaka w’ 1998. Abantu barenga million 4.5 imbere mu gihugu bavanywe mu byabo. Umuryango w’Abimbumbye uvuga ko uyu mubare ukomeje kwiyongera cyane mu ntara za Kivu zombi na Ituri, ahabarurwa imitwe y’abarwanyi itandukanye irenga 100.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_4618953' type='mono' source_url='https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/4618953.html' term='ebola'>
OMS Ihangayikishijwe n'Uko Ebola Yakwambuka mu Rwanda
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, rimenyesha ko ikiza ca Ebola ciyadukije muri Repubulika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo atari ikiza gikwiriye gufatirwa ingingo zihutirwa kw’isi. Yamara ishirahamwe OMS ritangaza ko atari ukuvuga ko abaganga badafise impungenge zikomeye cane ku vyerekeye ico kiza.
Ku bw’ishirahamwe OMS, ikiza gitegerezwa gufatirwa ingingo zihuta kw’isi ni ikiza gishobora gukwiragira hanze y’imbibe mu vyotuma amakungu afata ingingo zihutirwa.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, avuga ko iryo shirahamwe ayoboye rikibona ko ukugene ibintu vyifashe muri Republika iharanira demokrasi ya Kongo ku bijanye na Ebola bigiteye impungenge zikomeye cane.
Ghebreyesus avuga ko bagifise abakozi barenga 250 bariko bakorera muri Kongo kugira bahagarike Ebola, kandi ko ico kiza gishobora gutandukira ibihugu bibanyi vya Kongo. Amenyesha ko bazoguma bari magabo kandi ko bazokomeza uburyo bw’ukwishura kuri ico kiza. Ghebreyesus asigura ko batazogoheka gushika urugamba rw’ukurwanya Ebola rurangiye.
Ishirahamwe OMS rimenyesha ko abategetsi b’u Rwanda na Uganda biteguye hamwe Ebola yotandukira ibihugu vyabo.
</doc>
